n eat up entire afternoons. Curious if you\'ve found any good solutions for automating the status tracking piece?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(34, 11, '2026-03-16 11:12:38', 'MedStates Medical Billing Services', '', '', 'General Manager', 'j.smith@medstates.com', '', 'NO', 0, 'Medical billing services company is not a clinical practice that would use patient engagement or scheduling solutions', 'MedStates Medical Billing Services appears to be a medical billing company that provides revenue cycle management services to healthcare practices rather than a direct patient care provider.', 'mid-size', 'high', 'Managing multiple client practices with varying payer mixes and claim volumes creates operational complexity and staff scaling challenges', 'medical billing service provider, multiple client practices, varying payer requirements, staff coordination across accounts', 'high', 'Wrong Contact', 'low', 'Managing claims across dozens of client practices with different payer contracts likely means your team spends hours daily on eligibility verification rework.', 'billing staff overload', 'eligibility verification rework', 'Managing claims across dozens of client practices means different payer contracts for each one. Your team probably spends hours daily redoing eligibility verifications when the first attempt comes back with errors or missing information. The larger the client mix, the more time gets eaten up by this rework cycle.', 'why I\'m writing', 'I\'m reaching out because Calyxr helps billing services like MedStates eliminate eligibility verification rework entirely. Our platform catches payer requirement mismatches before claims go out, so your team stops having to redo verifications. One billing service reduced their eligibility rework by 87% in the first month.', 'If your team spends 3 hours daily on eligibility rework, that\'s roughly $45,000 annually in labor costs alone. We can show you exactly how other billing services eliminated this waste, no long contracts required. Would seeing a quick walkthrough of how this works be worth 15 minutes?', 'Hey there, noticed MedStates handles claims for multiple practices. That eligibility verification rework across different payer contracts has to be a daily headache for your team. Mind if I share how other billing services solved this?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(35, 11, '2026-03-16 11:13:17', 'Ancient City Medical Billing Services Inc.', '', '', 'President', 'rich@acmbsmail.com', '', 'NO', 25, 'Medical billing services company falls under excluded consulting/services category, not a clinical practice that would use Calyxr\'s patient engagement solutions', 'Ancient City Medical Billing Services Inc. appears to be a medical billing service company that provides revenue cycle management services to healthcare practices rather than being a direct patient care provider.', 'mid-size', 'high', 'Managing high claim volumes across multiple client practices with manual payer portal logins and claim status tracking creates operational bottlenecks', 'medical billing service provider, multiple client practices, high claim volume processing, manual payer portal management', 'high', 'Wrong Contact', 'low', 'Managing claim status tracking across dozens of client practices with manual payer portal logins has to be eating into your team\'s capacity.', 'billing staff overload', 'manual portal logins everywhere', 'Medical billing services are drowning in portal fatigue. Teams spend hours each day logging into dozens of different payer portals just to check claim statuses for client practices. The manual tracking creates bottlenecks that limit how many practices a billing service can realistically handle. Most teams hit capacity not because of complexity, but because of time spent on repetitive portal work.', 'why billing services choose calyxr', 'The reason I\'m writing is Calyxr eliminates the manual portal login cycle for medical billing services. Instead of your team checking claim statuses across dozens of payer portals, Calyxr pulls all that data automatically into one dashboard. One billing service went from managing 12 client practices to 28 practices with the same headcount after implementing our system.', 'If your team spends 3 hours daily on manual portal work, that\'s 15 hours weekly that could handle additional client practices instead. Calyxr goes live in days, no long contracts required. Would it help to see how this looks for a billing service your size?', 'Noticed Ancient City Medical Billing manages multiple client practices. The manual payer portal juggling act has to be limiting your growth capacity. Worth a quick conversation about how other billing services handle this?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
