tead of phone tag. One practice similar to Cross Timbers freed up 15 hours weekly for their coordinators within the first month.', 'If your team spends 25+ hours weekly on appointment calls, that\'s roughly $35,000 annually in coordinator time just for scheduling tasks. Most practices see ROI within 90 days, and we get you live in days, not months, with no long-term contracts. Would it make sense to see how this would work specifically for Cross Timbers?', 'Hey there, noticed Cross Timbers likely handles 150+ appointment calls weekly. Most primary care practices this size find their coordinators overwhelmed by scheduling coordination. Mind if I share how similar practices have reduced this workload by 40%?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
