(53, 22, '2026-03-17 11:05:40', 'Paoli Family Medicine', '', '', 'Office Manager', 'connie.legge@paolifamilymedicine.com', '', 'YES', 52, 'Healthcare practice with 27 employees fits basic firmographic criteria but lacks key signals like named EHR, decision-maker identification, and operational pain indicators.', 'Paoli Family Medicine is likely a primary care family practice serving patients of all ages with comprehensive family medicine services. Based on the name, it appears to be a community-based practice focused on continuity of care for families.', 'small', 'medium', 'High patient communication burden with manual appointment scheduling and reminder processes across a 27-person team serving diverse family medicine patient population', 'family medicine specialty, 27 employees indicating significant patient volume, primary care typically has high appointment frequency, community-based practice likely serves mixed insurance types including Medicare/Medicaid', 'medium', 'Gatekeeper', 'medium', 'Managing appointment coordination and patient reminders across 27 staff members for multi-generational families creates significant communication bottlenecks.', 'staff coordination overload', '27 people, endless appointment calls', 'Managing appointment coordination across 27 staff members creates a communication maze that never ends. Family medicine practices are drowning in manual scheduling calls, missed reminder follow-ups, and constant patient check-ins. The larger the team, the more disconnected the patient experience becomes. Multi-generational families especially feel the chaos when different staff members handle different family members.', 'why I\'m reaching out', 'I\'m writing because Calyxr helps family medicine practices eliminate the manual appointment coordination burden across large teams. Instead of 27 people juggling different systems and processes, everything flows through one streamlined patient communication hub. One practice reduced their daily scheduling calls by 78% in the first month while improving patient satisfaction scores.', 'A 27-person team spending just 30 minutes daily on manual appointment tasks costs roughly $180,000 annually in staff time. Most practices see that time cut in half within weeks, no long contracts required. Would it make sense to see how this looks for your patient volume?', 'Managing patient communication across 27 staff members at Paoli Family Medicine must create endless coordination challenges. I help family practices streamline this exact bottleneck. Worth a quick conversation about your current setup?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(54, 23, '2026-03-17 11:16:05', '', 'http://www.phs.org', '', 'Manager Clinical Operations Presbyterian Health Plan', 'sleger@phs.org', '', 'NO', 0, 'Insufficient company information provided to conduct proper ICP evaluation. Missing critical data points including employee count, revenue, location, and contact persona details.', 'Presbyterian Healthcare Services is a large integrated healthcare system in New Mexico offering comprehensive medical services, health insurance plans, and multi-location care delivery including virtual care options.', 'large', 'high', 'Large integrated healthcare system with multiple locations likely struggles with coordinating insurance eligibility verification and denial management across different service lines and facilities', 'integrated healthcare system, multi-location operations, comprehensive medical services, health insurance plans, large scale operations', 'high', 'Champion', 'high', 'Managing eligibility verification across Presbyterian\'s dozen+ facilities and multiple service lines creates significant rework when patients move between locations.', 'cross-facility coordination inefficiency', 'eligibility checks at 12 locations', 'Most integrated health systems run eligibility verification at each facility separately. When patients move between locations, staff often repeat the same checks multiple times. Presbyterian\'s dozen+ facilities probably see this daily, especially with patients accessing different service lines across locations. The rework adds up quickly when the same patient data gets verified three or four times in a week.', 'why we built calyxr', 'Built Calyxr specifically for integrated systems like Presbyterian dealing with cross-facility eligibility chaos. Our platform centralizes eligibility verification so when a patient is verified at one location, all facilities instantly see that status. One health system cut their eligibility rework by 67% in the first month. Worth exploring how this applies to Presbyterian\'s multi-location setup?', 'Quick math: if Presbyterian staff spend 20 minutes per duplicate eligibility check across 12 facilities, that\'s roughly $180,000 annually in wasted labor costs. Calyxr goes live in days, no long contracts required. Would a brief overview of how we eliminate duplicate verification work make sense for your team?', 'Hi there, noticed Presbyterian manages eligibility verification across multiple facilities. Built something specifically for integrated systems facing that cross-location coordination challenge. Worth a quick conversation about what we\'re seeing work?', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(55, 23, '2026-03-17 11:16:49', '', 'https://bonsecours.com', '', 'Director of Radiology Operations ... Richmond-East', 'valerie_szalay@bshsi.org', '', 'NO', 0, 'Bon Secours is a large health system with 10,000+ employees operating across multiple states, requiring enterprise sales motion that doesn\'t align with Calyxr\'s current GTM strategy for mid-market practices.', 'Bon Secours is a large healthcare system offering comprehensive medical services across multiple specialties with extensive community health initiatives. They operate a multi-location network with integrated patient portal technology and online scheduling systems.', 'large', 'high', 'Managing patient communication and workflow coordination across multiple locations with high patient volume creates operational inefficiencies and missed touchpoints', 'large healthcare system, multi-location network, comprehensive medical services, multiple specialties, high patient volume, complex coordination needs', 'high', 'Champion', 'high', 'Managing radiology scheduling and pre-procedure communications across Bon Secours\' Richmond-East network likely creates coordination gaps between locations.', 'multi-location workflow coordination gaps', 'coordination gaps across locations', 'Most radiology networks with multiple locations face the same challenge: patient communications and scheduling coordination become fragmented between sites. Pre-procedure instructions get missed, scheduling conflicts arise, and staff spend hours manually coordinating instead of focusing on patient care. The higher the volume, the more these gaps compound into real operational friction.', 'why I\'m reaching out', 'I\'m writing because Calyxr helps radiology operations eliminate coordination gaps between multiple locations. Our platform centralizes patient communications and workflow coordination, so pre-procedure instructions reach patients consistently and scheduling conflicts get resolved automatically. Houston Methodist reduced their