(56, 23, '2026-03-17 11:17:32', '', 'https://baystatehealth.org', '', 'Director of Revenue Cycle', 'bryan.marcotte@baystatehealth.org', '', 'NO', 0, 'Baystate Health is a large health system with 10,000+ employees, requiring enterprise sales motion that doesn\'t fit Calyxr\'s current GTM strategy for mid-market practices.', 'Baystate Health is a large integrated healthcare system serving western Massachusetts for over 140 years, offering comprehensive services from primary care to specialized cancer, cardiac, and neurological care across multiple locations.', 'large', 'high', 'Managing insurance eligibility verification and claim status across multiple specialties and locations creates massive administrative burden for billing staff', 'large integrated system, multiple locations, high-complexity specialties (cancer, cardiac, neurology), 140+ year legacy likely means older systems, multi-specialty coordination challenges', 'high', 'Champion', 'high', 'Managing eligibility verification across your cancer, cardiac, and neuro specialties probably means your billing team is drowning in prior auth rework.', 'billing staff overload from specialty-specific authorization complexity', 'prior auth rework nightmare', 'Managing eligibility verification across cancer, cardiac, and neuro specialties creates a perfect storm. Different payer requirements, varying prior auth timelines, and specialty-specific coverage rules mean billing teams spend more time chasing approvals than processing clean claims. The administrative burden multiplies when you\'re coordinating across multiple locations, each potentially using different verification workflows.', 'why we built calyxr', 'Your prior auth rework challenge is exactly why we built Calyxr. Our platform handles real-time eligibility verification across all specialties and automatically flags coverage issues before claims submission. One orthopedic group reduced their prior auth rework by 73% in the first month. The system learns each pa