, quality patient care, patient satisfaction, crnas', 'U.S. Anesthesia Partners (USAP) is a leading provider of anesthesia services in the United States, founded in 2012 by anesthesiologists. Headquartered in Dallas, Texas, the company operates in over 700 facilities nationwide, serving more than 2 million patients each year with a team of over 5,000 clinicians, including more than 4,500 physicians and certified registered nurse anesthetists (CRNAs). USAP is majority-owned and governed by approximately 1,500 practicing anesthesiologist shareholders,', 'Dallas', '2012', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
