(101, 29, '2026-03-17 14:33:53', 'GULFSHORE CONCIERGE MEDICINE', 'https://gulfshoreconciergemedicine.com', 'Mary Aufderheide', 'Practice Administrator', 'mary@gcmedicine.com', '', 'YES', 42, 'Small concierge practice in Florida with Practice Administrator contact shows operational fit but limited scale with only 9 employees. Concierge model suggests premium patient experience focus that aligns with Calyxr\'s communication capabilities.', 'Gulfshore Concierge Medicine is a premium concierge medical practice offering personalized healthcare with board-certified physicians across multiple locations in the Naples, Florida area. They focus on providing unhurried, comprehensive care with extended patient visits and 24/7 access.', 'small', 'low', 'Small 9-person team managing premium concierge patients across multiple Naples locations likely struggles with manual scheduling coordination and patient communication workflows', 'multi-location practice, small team size, concierge model requiring high-touch service, premium patient expectations, 24/7 access promise', 'medium', 'Gatekeeper', 'medium', 'Nine-person team coordinating premium concierge care across multiple Naples locations probably spends significant time on manual patient scheduling and communication workflows.', 'staff bandwidth strain', 'nine people, three locations', 'Most concierge practices with multiple locations hit the same wall around 8-10 team members. The manual coordination between sites starts breaking down. Patient scheduling becomes a juggling act between locations, and communication workflows that worked fine with one office suddenly require constant back-and-forth calls and texts. The premium experience patients expect gets harder to deliver when your team is spending half their day coordinating instead of caring.', 'why we built calyxr', 'Mary, we built Calyxr specifically for multi-location practices like yours that got tired of manual coordination eating up their day. It connects your scheduling and patient communication across all Naples locations in one system, so your nine-person team stops playing phone tag and starts delivering seamless concierge care. Palm Beach Concierge cut their coordination time by 60% in the first month. Does the constant back-and-forth between your locations sound familiar?', 'Quick math on coordination time: if your team spends just 2 hours daily on scheduling calls and location coordination, that\'s 60 hours monthly at $25/hour, or $18K annually just on coordination overhead. Calyxr typically pays for itself in the first quarter through time savings alone, plus you\'re live in days with no long-term contracts. Would it make sense to see how this looks with your specific Naples setup?', 'Mary, noticed Gulfshore runs concierge care across multiple Naples locations with a lean team. The coordination challenges between sites are probably familiar. Mind if I share how similar practices solved this?', 'sixty hours per month', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://gulfshoreconciergemedicine.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'GULFSHORE CONCIERGE MEDICINE, LLC', '', '9', '', '', 'Florida', 'United States', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://gulfshoreconciergemedicine.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation 