(103, 29, '2026-03-17 14:35:30', 'Heart and Vascular Group', 'https://heartvasc.com', 'Lyanna Banda', 'Practice Manager', 'l.banda@heartvasc.com', '', 'YES', 47, 'Strong specialty fit in cardiology with 30+ years experience and cardiology-specific pain signals, but limited by small size (12 employees) and Practice Manager role which is lower decision-making authority than ideal C-suite targets.', 'The Heart and Vascular Group is an established cardiology and vascular medicine practice serving Virginia Beach & Hampton Roads with over 30 years of experience, offering comprehensive cardiovascular care including interventional procedures.', 'small', 'high', 'Manual insurance eligibility verification and prior authorization processes are overwhelming their 12-person staff with high-volume interventional cardiology procedures requiring complex approvals', 'interventional cardiology specialty, complex procedures like Watchman device, preoperative evaluations, small 12-person team, 30+ years established practice, cardiology high-denial specialty', 'high', 'Gatekeeper', 'medium', 'Running high-volume Watchman procedures with a 12-person team means your staff likely burns hours daily on complex device approvals.', 'prior authorization bottleneck for specialized procedures', 'watchman approvals eating your day', 'Running high-volume Watchman procedures with a 12-person team means your staff likely burns hours daily on complex device approvals. Most interventional cardiology practices find their teams spending 3-4 hours per case just navigating insurance requirements and prior auth paperwork. The volume creates a bottleneck that pushes procedures out weeks, sometimes months. Sound familiar?', 'why calyxr built for cardiology', 'The reason I\'m reaching out is because Calyxr handles the entire insurance verification and prior authorization workflow for interventional procedures like Watchman implants. Instead of your staff burning hours on each case, our system processes eligibility checks and submits prior auths automatically. One cardiology group in Texas cut their pre-procedure admin time from 4 hours to 20 minutes per case. How much time does your team currently spend on each Watchman approval?', 'If your team spends 4 hours on pre-auth per Watchman case, that\'s roughly $800 in labor costs before the procedure even happens. Multiply that by your monthly volume and the numbers add up quickly. Calyxr typically pays for itself within the first month, no long contracts required. Would it make sense to see how this works for a few of your upcoming cases?', 'Saw you\'re managing ops at Heart and Vascular Group. Running Watchman procedures with a 12-person team, your staff probably spends hours daily on device approvals. Built something that might help, mind if I share how other cardiology practices handle this?', '4 hours vs 20 minutes', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://heartvasc.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Heart and Vascular Group', '', '12', '', '', 'Virginia', 'United States', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://heartvasc.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'http://www.li