(104, 29, '2026-03-17 14:36:18', 'Rosetta Radiology', 'https://rosettaradiology.com', 'Sharon Graham', 'Practice Manager', 'sgraham@rosettaradiology.com', '', 'YES', 42, 'Small radiology practice in high-value NYC market with Practice Manager contact, but limited size and revenue constrain immediate fit. Specialty imaging practices often have complex scheduling needs.', 'Rosetta Radiology is a boutique radiology practice on Manhattan\'s Upper East Side, established in 1949, offering personalized diagnostic imaging with direct radiologist consultation for every patient.', 'small', 'high', 'Small boutique practice with high-touch service model likely drowning in manual insurance authorizations for expensive imaging procedures', 'radiology specialty, authorizations keyword, concierge medicine model, expensive imaging procedures (PET/CT), small team of 10 handling complex prior auth requirements', 'high', 'Gatekeeper', 'medium', 'Running direct radiologist consultations for every patient with only 10 staff means your authorization team is probably buried in pre-cert requests for high-end imaging.', 'authorization bottleneck crushing boutique service model', 'pre-cert requests piling up', 'Most boutique radiology practices hit a ceiling around $2M revenue because their authorization workflow can\'t scale. With direct radiologist consultations and high-end imaging, the pre-cert volume becomes overwhelming for small teams. Every MRI, CT scan, and specialty procedure requires manual insurance verification, and most practices with 10-person teams find their staff spending 60% of their time chasing approvals instead of serving patients.', 'how rosetta could clear the backlog', 'The reason I\'m reaching out is that Calyxr built something specifically for this problem. Instead of your team manually tracking every pre-authorization, our system handles the insurance verification and approval process automatically. One radiology group in Texas went from 3 days average approval time to same-day clearance for 90% of their imaging orders. Does this sound like something that could help Rosetta\'s workflow?', 'Quick math: if delayed pre-auths are pushing out just 5 imaging appointments per week, that\'s roughly $125K in annual revenue sitting in limbo. Most practices see ROI within 30 days, and we can get you live without any long-term contracts. Would it make sense to see exactly how this would work with Rosetta\'s current authorization volume?', 'Sharon, noticed Rosetta\'s direct consultation model is unique for radiology practices. Curious how you\'re managing the pre-authorization volume with such a boutique approach, especially for high-end imaging procedures?', 'what delayed approvals actually cost', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://rosettaradiology.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Rosetta Radiology', '1.7M', '10', '', '', 'New York', 'United States', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://rosettaradiology.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'http://www.linkedin.com/company/rosettaradiology', '+1 212-744-5538', '', '', '', 'rosettaradiology.com', 'medical practice', 'sonography, xray, authorizations, diagnostic imaging, radiation oncology, biopsy, concierge medicine, mammography, womens imaging, radiology, pet scans, cat scans', 'WELCOME TO ROSETTA RADIOLOGY, WHERE EVERY PATIENT SEES A RADIOLOGIST TO DISCUSS THEIR CASE. \n\nLocated on the Upper East Side of Manhattan, our radiologists provide the most personalized diagnostic imaging care available. Since its inception in 1949, Rosetta Radiology has aimed to deliver the highest quality diagnostic radiology and radiation oncology care with warmth and compassion.\nWe remain the exceptional choice for high quality diagnostic radiology, advanced imaging, women\'s imaging and radi', 'New York', '1949', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
