40+ verification calls per day, that\'s roughly 20 hours of staff time that could go toward patient care instead. Most mobile practices see ROI within 60 days, no long contracts required. Would you be open to a 15-minute screen share to see how the verification process works for other NYC mobile teams?', 'Kenneth, noticed Care2U\'s 24/7 mobile operations across NYC. Most teams your size are hitting dispatch delays from insurance verification calls. Worth a quick conversation about how others are handling this bottleneck?', '22 minutes per response', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://care2u.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '38', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://care2u.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'khickey@care2u.com', '', '', '', 'hospital & health care', '', '', '', '', '', 'Assistant Director of Operations and Training', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(106, 30, '2026-03-18 14:40:45', 'Langdon Prairie Health', 'https://lph.hospital', 'Leilani Bryan', 'Business Office Manager', 'leilani.bryan@lph.hospital', '', 'YES', 42, 'Small healthcare facility with 32 employees fits basic size criteria, but Business Office Manager represents lower-tier persona. Missing critical signals like EHR system, pain points, and geographic data limit scoring potential.', 'Langdon Prairie Health is a rural critical access hospital and clinic serving the Langdon and Walhalla communities since 1939, providing comprehensive healthcare from emergency services to primary care with 24/7 availability.', 'small', 'high', 'Managing 24/7 emergency services and comprehensive care with limited staff creates overwhelming administrative burden and patient communication gaps', 'rural critical access hospital, 24/7 operations, small staff (32 employees), comprehensive services, emergency care, serving multiple communities', 'high', 'Gatekeeper', 'medium', 'Running 24/7 emergency services with just 32 staff means your business office is probably drowning in insurance eligibility checks at 2AM.', 'billing staff overload', '2am insurance eligibility checks', 'Emergency departments never sleep, but insurance verification systems seem to. Many rural hospitals with 24/7 services find their business office staff fielding eligibility checks and prior auth requests at all hours. The administrative burden just multiplies when you\'re managing comprehensive care around the clock with a lean team.', 'why we built calyxr', 'Watching business office teams at rural hospitals juggle insurance verifications at 2AM is exactly why we created Calyxr. We handle the insurance eligibility checks, prior authorizations, and patient communication workflows that eat up your team\'s time. Prairie Lakes Healthcare reduced their administrative workload by 40% within the first month of using our platform.', 'A single denied claim from missed eligibility verification costs $200-400 in