(107, 30, '2026-03-18 14:41:36', 'Sydenham Clinic', 'https://sydenhamclinic.com', 'Kenya Tijerina', 'Business Office Manager', 'kenya@sydenhamclinic.com', '', 'YES', 32, 'Small healthcare clinic with 19 employees fits industry but lacks strong personas, technology signals, and pain indicators. Business Office Manager suggests revenue cycle focus but limited decision-making authority.', 'Sydenham Clinic is a members-only concierge medicine practice offering personalized health management, longevity planning, and comprehensive preventive care. They provide 24/7 personalized care through a unified team of physicians, nutritionists, and functional medicine specialists.', 'small', 'low', 'Manual coordination and communication across 19 staff members for 24/7 personalized patient care delivery is creating operational bottlenecks', 'concierge medicine model, 24/7 care promise, multi-disciplinary team coordination, preventive care scheduling complexity, personalized care requirements', 'low', 'Gatekeeper', 'medium', 'Coordinating 24/7 care across 19 specialists for concierge members likely means your team fields endless patient check-ins manually.', 'staff coordination overload for premium service delivery', '19 staff, endless check-ins', 'Coordinating 24/7 care across 19 specialists for concierge members likely means your team fields endless patient check-ins manually. Many clinics with round-the-clock personalized care find their staff spending more time on coordination calls than actual patient care. The bigger the care team, the more complex the communication web becomes.', 'why we built calyxr', 'That coordination challenge is exactly why we built Calyxr for clinics like Sydenham. Instead of manual check-ins disrupting your 19-person team, patients get real-time care updates through one centralized system. One concierge practice reduced coordination calls by 75% in their first month, letting specialists focus on medicine instead of constant status updates.', 'Quick math: if your team handles 50 coordination calls daily, that\'s 12+ hours of staff time. At $30/hour average, you\'re looking at $1,400 weekly just in coordination overhead. We can get Sydenham live in days, no long contracts required. Worth exploring how much time your team could reclaim?', 'Kenya, noticed Sydenham\'s 24/7 concierge model with 19 specialists. That coordination complexity is exactly what we solve for clinics. Worth a brief conversation about streamlining those endless patient check-ins?', '75% fewer coordination calls', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://sydenhamclinic.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '19', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://sydenhamclinic.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'kenya@sydenhamclinic.com', '', '', '', 'hospital & health care', '', '', '', '', '', 'Business Office Manager', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(108, 30, '2026-03-18 14:42:20', 'West Wichita Family Physicians P.A.', 'https://wwfppa.com', 'Janet Ewy', 'Business Office Manager', 'jrewy@wwfppa.com', '', 'YES', 45, 'Mid-sized family practice (41 employees) with Business Office Manager suggests revenue cycle pain points and potential for billing workflow optimization. Missing key data prevents higher scoring.', 'West Wichita Family Physicians is a physician-led family medicine practice with comprehensive in-house services including radiology, lab, and an ambulatory surgery center, serving patients across the healthcare continuum.', 'mid-size', 'high', 'Managing complex insurance eligibility verification and prior authorizations across multiple service lines (primary care, radiology, lab, surgery) with a mid-sized staff creates bottlenecks in patient scheduling and revenue capture', 'family medicine specialty, 41 employees, comprehensive in-house services, multiple service lines, ambulatory surgery center, radiology and lab services', 'high', 'Gatekeeper', 'medium', 'Running eligibility checks across primary care, radiology, lab, and surgery with your current staff size likely means constant interruptions to verify benefits before scheduling procedures.', 'multi-service eligibility bottlenecks', 'eligibility checks slowing scheduling', 'Most mid-sized practices with multiple service lines hit the same scheduling bottleneck. Staff gets pulled away from other tasks every time a patient needs radiology, lab work, or surgery scheduled because someone has to verify their benefits first. The constant interruptions slow down the whole scheduling process, and procedures get delayed while patients wait for eligibility confirmation.', 'why I\'m writing about eligibility', 'Janet, I\'m reaching out because Calyxr handles real-time eligibility verification across all service lines without pulling your staff away from scheduling. Instead of manual benefit checks interrupting workflow, the system verifies coverage instantly when appointments are booked. One practice manager told us it eliminated their eligibility bottleneck completely and freed up 6 hours per week of staff time.', 'When procedures get delayed due to eligibility verification, practices typically lose $200-500 per postponed appointment in missed revenue and rework costs. With 41 employees, those interruptions add up quickly across your service lines. The platform goes live in days, not months, and there are no long-term contracts. Would it help to see how this works for practices with similar scheduling challenges?', 'Hi Janet, noticed you\'re managing business operations at West Wichita Family Physicians. Many practices your size struggle with eligibility verification slowing down scheduling across multiple service lines. Mind if I connect to share how we help solve this specific bottleneck?', 'cost of delayed procedures', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://wwfppa.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '41', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://wwfppa.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched