(111, 30, '2026-03-18 14:44:28', 'Logan County Health Services', 'https://logancountyhospital.org', 'Robert Mangold', 'Chief Nursing & Operations Officer', 'rmangold@lchoakley.com', '', 'YES', 49, 'Small rural healthcare facility with strong C-suite operations contact, but limited signals around pain points, technology stack, or growth initiatives to drive immediate urgency.', 'Logan County Health Services appears to be a small regional hospital system with 31 employees serving a rural community healthcare market.', 'small', 'medium', 'Rural hospital with limited billing staff likely struggling with manual insurance verification and payer portal logins across multiple insurance types including high Medicare/Medicaid volume', 'rural hospital system, small staff size (31 employees), likely high Medicare/Medicaid mix, limited billing resources, manual payer portal management', 'high', 'Champion', 'high', 'With 31 staff covering rural Logan County, your billing team is probably drowning in Medicare/Medicaid eligibility checks across dozens of payer portals daily.', 'billing staff overload', '31 staff, dozens of portals', 'Rural hospitals with 31 staff typically face a brutal reality. Your billing team logs into 15-20 different payer portals daily just to verify Medicare and Medicaid eligibility. Each portal has different passwords, different layouts, different timeout periods. What should take 2 minutes per patient stretches to 8-10 minutes when you factor in login failures and system slowdowns. Many rural facilities lose 3-4 hours daily to this portal juggling act.', 'why I\'m writing about portals', 'Robert, I\'m reaching out because Calyxr eliminates the payer portal nightmare for rural hospitals. Instead of your team logging into 20 different insurance portals, our platform pulls eligibility data directly through API connections in under 30 seconds per patient. Genesis Medical Center reduced their eligibility verification time from 4 hours daily to 45 minutes after switching from manual portal checks. Does this portal switching sound familiar at Logan County Health Services?', 'If your billing team spends 4 hours daily on eligibility checks, that\'s costing Logan County roughly $52,000 annually in staff time alone. Plus the revenue delays from verification bottlenecks. Calyxr typically pays for itself within 60 days, no long contracts required, and most rural hospitals go live within a week. Worth exploring what 3+ hours of recovered staff time daily could mean for your operations?', 'Robert, noticed Logan County has 31 staff handling rural healthcare operations. Curious how your billing team manages eligibility verification across all those Medicare/Medicaid payers without losing hours to portal logins daily?', '4 hours vs 45 minutes', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://logancountyhospital.org) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '31', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://logancountyhospital.org) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'rmangold@lchoak