(121, 30, '2026-03-18 14:51:17', 'CareForceMD', 'https://careforcemd.com', 'Edward White', 'COO', 'ewhite@careportmd.com', '', 'YES', 24, 'Small healthcare practice with strong C-Suite persona (COO) but missing critical data points. Industry match and senior decision-maker are positive, but lack of geographic, revenue, and technology signals limits scoring potential.', 'CareForceMD is a mobile healthcare service providing urgent care, COVID-19 testing/vaccination, and chronic disease management through house calls and telemedicine in Delaware. They operate as a concierge-style service bringing healthcare directly to patients\' homes or workplaces.', 'small', 'medium', 'Mobile healthcare team spending excessive time on manual insurance verification and payer portal logins while managing patients across multiple locations', 'mobile/field operations, multiple service locations, small team managing diverse patient populations, urgent care complexity, insurance verification challenges in field', 'high', 'Champion', 'high', 'Managing insurance eligibility across 11 mobile providers hitting different payers daily has to create serious portal fatigue for your operations team.', 'billing staff overload', 'portal fatigue is real', 'Most mobile healthcare teams burn 2-3 hours daily just logging into different payer portals to verify insurance eligibility. With 11 providers hitting different locations and payers, that portal switching adds up fast. The constant username juggling and verification delays slow down patient care when speed matters most.', 'why i\'m writing', 'Writing because Calyxr eliminates the payer portal maze for mobile teams like yours. Instead of your 11 providers manually checking eligibility across multiple portals, our platform pulls real-time verification data directly. One client reduced their daily verification time from 3 hours to 15 minutes.', 'If your team spends 2 hours daily on portal logins, that\'s 520 hours yearly just on verification tasks. Most mobile practices see ROI within 30 days, no long contracts required. Worth exploring how this works for your 11-provider operation?', 'Edward, noticed CareForceMD manages mobile teams across multiple locations. The insurance verification workflow for mobile providers is brutal, especially with constant payer portal switching. Worth a quick conversation about how other teams handle this?', 'the math on portal time', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://careforcemd.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '11', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://careforcemd.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'ewhite@careportmd.com', '', '', '', 'hospital & health care', '', '', '', '', '', 'COO', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(122, 30, '2026-03-18 14:51:59', 'Harlan County Health System (HCHS)', 'https://harlancountyhealth.com', 'Chad Jay', 'COO', 'cjay@harlancohealth.org', '', 'YES', 24, 'Small rural health system with strong persona match (COO) but limited scale with only 11 employees. Healthcare industry fit but size constraints limit immediate viability.', 'Harlan County Health System is a rural critical access hospital in Alma, NE providing comprehensive healthcare services including inpatient, outpatient, and specialty care to the local community.', 'small', 'high', 'Critical access hospital with 11 staff handling multiple service lines faces overwhelming administrative burden with manual insurance verification, claim processing, and patient communication across inpatient and outpatient care.', 'critical access hospital, rural location, small staff (11 employees), comprehensive services (inpatient/outpatient/specialty), limited resources, Medicare/Medicaid heavy payer mix typical of rural hospitals', 'high', 'Champion', 'high', 'With 11 staff managing both inpatient and outpatient services, your team likely spends hours daily on insurance eligibility checks across multiple payers.', 'billing staff overload', '11 staff, endless verifications', 'Critical access hospitals with small teams face an impossible math problem. Eleven staff members handling both inpatient and outpatient services means someone is constantly stuck on hold with insurance companies, checking eligibility for every patient that walks through the door. The verification calls alone can consume 3-4 hours daily across multiple payers. Meanwhile, patients wait longer and staff burnout accelerates.', 'why we built calyxr', 'The verification bottleneck at critical access hospitals is exactly why we built Calyxr. Instead of your team spending hours on hold with payers, our platform handles real-time insurance eligibility checks automatically across all major carriers. One rural hospital with 12 staff cut their verification time from 4 hours daily to 20 minutes. What could your team accomplish with those extra hours back?', 'Four hours of daily verification work costs a critical access hospital roughly $85,000 annually in staff time. Most hospitals see that time cut by 80% within the first week of going live with Calyxr, no long contracts required. Would 15 minutes be worth exploring how three other rural hospitals eliminated their verification backlog?', 'Chad, noticed HCHS manages both inpatient and outpatient with just 11 staff. Most critical access hospitals tell us insurance verification calls are eating up 3-4 hours daily. Curious if that rings true for your team?', '4 hours daily adds up', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://harlancountyhealth.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '11', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://harlancountyhealth.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'cjay@harlancohealth.org', '', '', '', 'hospital & health care', '', '', '', '', '', 'COO', '', '', '', '', '', NULL,