(123, 30, '2026-03-18 14:52:37', 'WellcomeMD', 'https://wellcomemd.com', 'Lori Kardos', 'Director of Clinic Operations', 'lori.kardos@wellcomemd.com', '', 'YES', 39, 'Strong persona match with Director of Clinic Operations in healthcare industry, but limited by small size (20 employees) and lack of visible technology/pain signals. Concierge medicine model may have different workflow needs.', 'WellcomeMD is a concierge medicine practice operating in Virginia and North Carolina, offering membership-based personalized healthcare with lower patient-to-doctor ratios and integrative/functional medicine approaches. They serve patients seeking premium, unhurried healthcare experiences with same-day appointments and comprehensive wellness services.', 'small', 'low', 'Concierge medicine practice managing premium patient experiences while coordinating complex wellness services and maintaining high-touch communication across multiple states', 'multi-state operations, concierge/membership model, integrative medicine complexity, premium service expectations, same-day scheduling demands, small staff relative to service complexity', 'medium', 'Champion', 'high', 'Managing same-day appointment coordination and wellness service follow-ups across Virginia and North Carolina locations with only 20 staff creates communication bottlenecks.', 'premium patient experience degradation', 'same day coordination bottlenecks', 'Managing same-day appointments across Virginia and North Carolina locations creates interesting coordination challenges for concierge practices. When premium patients expect immediate availability, but communication has to flow through multiple states with limited staff, bottlenecks form quickly. The expectation gap widens when wellness service follow-ups get delayed because teams can\'t stay synchronized in real-time.', 'why calyxr built this', 'This coordination challenge across multiple states is exactly why we built Calyxr. Most concierge practices lose 2-3 hours daily to communication gaps between locations when managing same-day requests and wellness follow-ups. Our operations platform connects your Virginia and North Carolina teams instantly, so premium patient requests flow seamlessly regardless of location. One practice reduced coordination time by 65% within their first month.', 'Those 2-3 lost coordination hours daily cost roughly $180,000 annually in operational inefficiency for a 20-person team. Most practices see the difference within days of implementation, no long contracts required. Would a 15-minute conversation about streamlining your multi-state coordination make sense this week?', 'Managing same-day coordination across Virginia and North Carolina with 20 staff creates interesting bottlenecks for concierge practices. Built something specifically for this challenge at Calyxr. Worth a brief conversation about streamlining multi-state operations?', '3 hours daily adds up', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://wellcomemd.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '20', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://wellcomemd.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'lori.kardos@wellcomemd.com', '', '', '', 'hospital & health care', '', '', '', '', '', 'Director of Clinic Operations', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(124, 30, '2026-03-18 14:53:21', 'Serviam Care Network', 'https://serviam.org', 'Cheryl Christie', 'Director of Laboratory Operations', 'cheryl.christie@serviamdiagnostics.com', '', 'YES', 19, 'Small healthcare organization with 31 employees in hospital & health care industry, but Director of Laboratory Operations is not a core decision-maker persona for patient communication platforms. Lacks key signals around patient access pain, technology stack, or operational overwhelm.', 'Serviam Care Network operates as a healthcare services enterprise focused on senior living communities, providing diagnostics, pharmacy, and hospice services through partnerships with senior living operators across the country.', 'small', 'high', 'Managing complex billing across multiple service lines (diagnostics, pharmacy, hospice) with different payer requirements and authorization workflows', 'multi-service healthcare enterprise, senior care focus, Medicare/Medicaid heavy patient base, complex prior authorization requirements, 31 employees managing diverse revenue streams', 'high', 'Wrong Contact', 'low', 'Managing lab billing across multiple senior living communities while coordinating with hospice and pharmacy claims creates serious eligibility verification bottlenecks.', 'billing staff overload', 'eligibility bottlenecks across service lines', 'Managing lab billing across senior living communities while coordinating hospice and pharmacy claims creates serious bottlenecks. Each service line has different payer requirements, and eligibility verification becomes a maze when claims cross between diagnostics, pharmacy, and hospice workflows. The manual coordination between these systems often delays reimbursement and creates compliance gaps that most mid-size healthcare operations struggle to close efficiently.', 'why calyxr handles multi-service billing', 'Writing because Calyxr specifically handles the complex billing coordination you\'re managing across diagnostics, pharmacy, and hospice services. Our platform connects these different payer workflows into one eligibility verification system, eliminating the bottlenecks between service lines. One lab network reduced their cross-service claim delays by 67% within their first month. Instead of juggling separate authorization processes, everything runs through unified workflows that understand each payer\'s specific requirements.', 'Each day of eligibility delays typically costs lab operations $200-400 per claim in extended A/R cycles. With multiple service lines, that compounds quickly across your communities. Calyxr goes live in days, not months, with no long-term contracts required. Would you be curious to see how the unified workflow handles your specific payer mix across diagnostics, pharmacy, and hospice?', 'Hi Cheryl, noticed Serviam manages lab operations across multiple senior communities. The eligibility verification bottlenecks between diagnostics, pharmacy, and hospice billing seem particularly challenging at your scale. Worth a brief conversation about how similar networks handle this coordination?', 'cost of eligibility delays', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://serviam.org) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '31', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://serviam.org) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'cheryl.christie@serviamdiagnostics.com', '', '', '', 'hospital & health care', '', '', '', '', '', 'Director of Laboratory Operations', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(125, 30, '2026-03-18 14:54:00', 'Adomo Health', 'https://adomohealth.com', 'Tina Raisifard', 'Director of Operations', 'tina@adomohealth.com', '', 'YES', 39, 'Strong persona fit with Director of Operations and healthcare industry match, but very small team size (10 employees) limits contract potential and operational complexity needs.', 'Adomo Health is a small healthcare technology company with 10 employees, led by a physician founder (Dr. Benjamin Stein) and VP of Technology, suggesting a tech-forward healthcare organization focused on physician partnerships.', 'small', 'medium', 'Small healthcare technology company likely struggling to scale automated patient communication and workflow processes with limited staff resources', 'small team size (10 employees), physician founder, tech-forward organization, likely high patient-to-staff ratio', 'medium', 'Champion', 'high', 'With only 10 staff supporting physician partnerships, your operations team is likely drowning in manual patient communication workflows.', 'small team operational overload', '10 people, endless workflows', 'Most healthcare tech companies with small teams hit the same wall around 10 employees. Patient communication workflows that worked at 3-5 people suddenly become impossible to manage manually. Every new physician partnership adds exponential complexity, but the operations team stays the same size. The bottleneck isn\'t technology or talent, it\'s that manual processes don\'t scale.', 'why I\'m writing about workflows', 'I\'m reaching out because Calyxr helps small healthcare operations teams like yours handle patient communication workflows without adding headcount. Instead of your team manually coordinating every touchpoint, practices see their patient engagement run automatically while staff focus on growth. One 12-person healthcare company went from 40 hours weekly on patient follow-ups to under 5 hours.', 'Quick math: if your team spends 30 hours weekly on manual patient communications, that\'s $75k annually in operational costs. Most practices using Calyxr recover that investment in under 90 days, with no long contracts or complex integrations. Worth a quick conversation about your current workflow challenges?', 'Noticed Adomo Health\'s growth with physician partnerships. With a 10-person operations team, curious how you\'re handling the patient communication workflows that typically break at this scale?', 'the math on manual workflows', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://adomohealth.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '10', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://adomohealth.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'tina@adomohealth.com', '', '', '', 'hospital & health care', '', '', '', '', '', 'Director of Operations', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(126, 30, '2026-03-18 14:54:39', 'Advanced Family Medicine + Wellness Center', 'https://advfamilymed.com', 'Matthew Holloway', 'Director of Operations', 'matt@advfamilymed.com', '', 'YES', 39, 'Small family medicine practice with operations director but very limited employee count (8) puts them at minimum viable size. Missing key data on location, revenue, and technology stack limits scoring potential.', 'Advanced Family Medicine + Wellness Center is an independent osteopathic family practice in Joplin, MO offering comprehensive primary care, immediate care, pediatrics, and wellness services including a med spa with IV hydration and aesthetic treatments.', 'small', 'medium', 'Small 8-person team manually handling high-volume patient communications and appointment scheduling across primary care, pediatrics, immediate care, and wellness services', 'multi-service offerings, small staff size, primary care scheduling complexity, pediatric appointments, immediate care unpredictability, wellness service coordination', 'medium', 'Champion', 'high', 'With 8 staff juggling primary care, pediatrics, immediate care, AND med spa bookings, your team\'s probably drowning in appointment coordination across those service lines.', 'operational overwhelm from multi-service scheduling complexity', '8 staff, 4 service lines', 'Most practices with your mix of services hit a breaking point around 8 staff members. Primary care appointments bleed into pediatric slots, immediate care creates scheduling chaos, and wellness bookings somehow end up double-booked. The manual juggling act works until it doesn\'t. Then one missed appointment coordination crashes the whole day.', 'why I\'m writing', 'I\'m reaching out because Calyxr helps practices like Advanced Family Medicine eliminate the manual scheduling chaos across multiple service lines. Instead of your 8-person team playing appointment tetris, our platform coordinates everything automatically. One family practice reduced scheduling errors by 89% in their first month.', 'A missed appointment costs $200 on average, but scheduling conflicts across four service lines? That\'s easily $2,000+ weekly in lost revenue. Calyxr typically pays for itself in the first month, no long contracts required, live within days. Would it help to see exactly how this works for a practice your size?', 'Hey Matthew, noticed Advanced Family Medicine handles quite the service mix with just 8 staff. Curious how you\'re managing the scheduling coordination across primary care, pediatrics, immediate care, and wellness without everything colliding?', 'the real cost', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://advfamilymed.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '8', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://advfamilymed.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'matt@advfamilymed.com', '', '', '', 'hospital & health care', '', '', '', '', '', 'Director of Operations', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(127, 30, '2026-03-18 14:55:20', 'Care2U', 'https://care2u.com', 'Rich Straub', 'Director of Operations', 'rich@care2u.com', '', 'YES', 39, 'Strong persona fit with Director of Operations and healthcare industry match, but limited data prevents higher scoring. Small team size (38 employees) suggests potential for operational efficiency gains.', 'Care2U is a mobile urgent care service providing physician-led, hospital-level medical care directly to patients\' homes in New York with 24/7 coverage and 2-4 hour response times. They serve high-acuity patients who would otherwise need emergency room or hospital care.', 'small', 'high', 'Mobile urgent care with 24/7 operations likely struggles with real-time insurance eligibility verification and claim status tracking across multiple payers while coordinating care between field providers and billing staff', 'mobile/field operations, 24/7 coverage, high-acuity patients, urgent care billing complexity, coordination between field staff and billing, real-time eligibility needs', 'high', 'Champion', 'high', 'Managing eligibility verification for 38 staff across mobile units while maintaining 2-4 hour response times creates billing bottlenecks.', 'operational efficiency bottleneck', 'eligibility checks killing response times', 'Mobile urgent care operations face a brutal reality. Field providers need instant insurance eligibility answers, but manual verification creates 15-30 minute delays per patient. When response times stretch beyond 2 hours, patient satisfaction drops and referral sources start looking elsewhere. Most practices with 30+ mobile staff report eligibility bottlenecks as their biggest operational headache.', 'why calyxr built real-time eligibility', 'Rich, writing because Calyxr solves the eligibility verification bottleneck that mobile urgent care faces. Our platform gives field providers instant eligibility results in under 10 seconds, eliminating the back-and-forth with billing staff. One mobile urgent care group reduced their average response time from 3.2 hours to 45 minutes after implementing real-time eligibility checks.', 'Quick math: if each of your 38 providers handles 8 patients daily and 60% need eligibility verification, that\'s 182 potential delays. At 20 minutes per manual check, your team loses 60+ hours weekly to eligibility bottlenecks. Calyxr goes live in days with no long contracts. Worth exploring how much faster your response times could be?', 'Rich, noticed Care2U\'s impressive 24/7 mobile coverage. Managing real-time eligibility verification across 38 field staff must be challenging. Mind if I share how similar mobile urgent care operations handle this bottleneck?', '38 staff, how many eligibility delays daily', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://care2u.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '38', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://care2u.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'rich@care2u.com', '', '', '', 'hospital & health care', '', '', '', '', '', 'Director of O