(128, 30, '2026-03-18 14:56:29', 'Crucial Care (acquired by GuideWell)', 'https://gemd.com', 'Cari Gravley', 'Director of Operations', 'cari.gravley@gemd.com', '', 'YES', 54, 'Director of Operations at 40-employee healthcare organization shows strong persona fit but limited firmographic signals. Missing geographic, revenue, and technology data prevents higher scoring despite ideal decision-maker role.', 'Crucial Care is a healthcare organization with 40 employees that was acquired by GuideWell, a major health insurance company. The practice operates in the hospital and health care sector with moderate operational complexity.', 'mid-size', 'medium', 'Post-acquisition integration challenges with 40 employees managing increased claim volumes and workflow standardization across GuideWell\'s expanded network', 'recent acquisition, 40 employees, GuideWell integration, healthcare organization scale, operational complexity', 'high', 'Champion', 'high', 'Post-GuideWell acquisition, your 40-person operation likely sees claim status inquiries spiking across the expanded network footprint.', 'billing staff overload', 'claim inquiries after guidewell', 'Post-acquisition integrations often create a perfect storm for operations teams. When networks expand overnight, claim status inquiries typically double or triple while staff scramble to learn new systems and processes. The 40-person operations team suddenly finds themselves managing volume designed for a much larger infrastructure. Most practices see this spike last 6-12 months before finding their rhythm.', 'why we built calyxr', 'Cari, post-acquisition claim volume spikes are exactly why we built Calyxr. Our healthcare operations platform handles the repetitive claim status work that\'s overwhelming teams like yours right now. Instead of your 40 staff members fielding these inquiries manually, Calyxr processes them automatically and routes only exceptions to your team. One recent post-merger practice reduced claim inquiry handling time by 78% in their first month.', 'Every manual claim status inquiry costs roughly $12 in staff time, and post-acquisition practices typically see 200-400% increases in these requests. For a 40-person operation, that math gets expensive quickly. Calyxr typically pays for itself within weeks, and there are no long contracts or lengthy implementations. Worth exploring what your current claim inquiry volume might be costing?', 'Hi Cari, noticed Crucial Care\'s recent GuideWell acquisition. Post-merger claim volume spikes are brutal for operations teams. Built something specifically for this challenge, curious if it\'s hitting your team too?', 'the cost of manual processing', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://gemd.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '40', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://gemd.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'cari.gravley@gemd.com', '', '', '', 'hospital & health care', '', '', '', '', '', 'Director of Operations', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL