(132, 30, '2026-03-18 14:59:00', 'Kyle ER & Hospital', 'https://kyleer.com', 'Alicia Bodony', 'Director of Operations', 'abodony@kyleer.com', '', 'YES', 45, 'Strong persona match with Director of Operations and emergency care creates urgency for patient flow optimization, but missing technology and pain signals limit qualification confidence.', 'Kyle ER & Hospital is a standalone emergency room and hospital facility in Kyle providing 24/7 emergency medical care with advanced diagnostic capabilities and inpatient services including medical detox.', 'small', 'high', 'Emergency department operations with 24/7 staffing and high patient turnover create massive claim volume and insurance verification challenges that overwhelm a 21-person team', 'emergency department specialty, 24/7 operations, high patient turnover, small staff relative to ED volume, urgent care billing complexity, insurance verification bottlenecks', 'high', 'Champion', 'high', 'Managing insurance eligibility for medical detox admissions at 3am with a 21-person team means your overnight staff are probably burning hours on hold with payers.', 'overnight staffing inefficiency', '3am insurance verifications', 'Managing insurance eligibility for medical detox admissions at 3am with a 21-person team means overnight staff are probably burning hours on hold with payers. Emergency departments with high patient turnover face this constantly, especially when detox beds need immediate clearance. The verification bottleneck hits hardest during peak overnight hours when payer phone lines have the longest hold times.', 'real-time eligibility checks', 'I\'m reaching out because Calyxr handles real-time insurance eligibility verification, which is why I thought of Kyle ER. Instead of staff spending hours on hold at 3am, the platform runs instant checks and populates coverage details automatically. One 18-bed detox facility cut their overnight verification time from 45 minutes per patient to under 2 minutes.', 'If your overnight team spends even 30 minutes per patient on insurance calls, that\'s roughly $180,000 annually in staff time for a facility your size. Calyxr typically pays for itself within 60 days, goes live without long contracts, and works with your existing systems. Would you be curious to see how the real-time verification looks for detox admissions?', 'Hi Alicia, noticed Kyle ER handles medical detox admissions. Managing insurance eligibility at 3am with a 21-person team has to create some interesting operational challenges. Would be curious to hear your perspective on overnight verification processes.', 'cost of 3am phone calls', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://kyleer.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '21', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://kyleer.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'abodony@kyleer.com', '', '', '', 'hospital & health care', '', '', '', '', '', 'Director of Operations', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(133, 30, '2026-03-18 14:59:37', 'Life', 'https://lifehealthgroup.com', 'Randy Coste', 'Director of Operations', 'randy.coste@homecare.life', '', 'YES', 20, 'Strong persona fit with Director of Operations in healthcare industry, but very small team size (11 employees) limits scalability and revenue potential for our typical engagement model.', 'Life Health Group is a comprehensive healthcare organization offering multiple service lines including home care, hospice, mobile healthcare, DME, transportation, and a multi-specialty medical practice with 50+ providers across various locations.', 'large', 'high', 'Managing insurance eligibility and claims across 50+ providers and multiple service lines creates massive coordination complexity and claim denial risk', 'multi-specialty practice, 50+ providers, multiple locations, diverse service lines (home care, hospice, DME, transportation), small staff relative to provider volume, complex billing requirements across different service types', 'high', 'Champion', 'high', 'With 50+ providers spanning home care to multi-specialty practice, your eligibility verification workload must be crushing your operations team of 11.', 'eligibility verification workload overwhelming small ops team', '50+ providers, endless eligibility checks', 'Most multi-specialty operations with 50+ providers hit the same wall. Eligibility verification becomes this endless cycle of calls, portal checks, and manual coordination across service lines. The operations team ends up spending 60% of their day on verification tasks instead of actual patient care coordination. Claims get denied because someone missed an eligibility change or coverage limitation.', 'why calyxr built eligibility automation', 'That eligibility coordination nightmare across multiple service lines is exactly why Calyxr exists. Instead of your 11-person operations team manually checking eligibility for each provider and service line, our platform automates real-time verification across all payers and instantly flags coverage changes. One multi-specialty group reduced their eligibility workload by 75% in the first month.', 'Operations teams managing 50+ providers typically spend 3+ hours daily on eligibility tasks. With automated verification, that drops to about 45 minutes of exception handling. That\'s 2+ hours per day your team could redirect to patient care coordination instead of insurance paperwork. Worth exploring if there\'s no long commitment required?', 'Randy, noticed Life manages 50+ providers across multiple service lines. The eligibility verification coordination must be intense with your operations team of 11. Curious how you\'re currently handling the workload across all those different specialties?', '3 hours daily vs 45 minutes', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://lifehealthgroup.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '11', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://lifehealthgroup.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'randy.coste@homecare.life', '', '',