-shows to 6% within their first month. Providers see their actual schedule, patients get accurate wait times, and your team stops playing phone tag between locations.', 'Quick math on those coordination calls. If your team spends even 2 hours daily managing schedules between locations, that\'s $50k annually in just coordination overhead. We typically get practices live within days, no long contracts required. Would it make sense to see how this looks with your specific setup across those four locations?', 'Hey Tyler, noticed Maniya Health\'s growth across multiple NJ locations. Managing same-day scheduling with 20+ providers across sites creates some interesting operational challenges. Worth a quick conversation about how similar urgent care groups handle the coordination complexity?', '15 minutes vs 15 hours weekly', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://maniyahealth.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '23', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://maniyahealth.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-2025051