(135, 30, '2026-03-18 15:00:58', 'NOVA MEDICAL SERVICES', 'https://novamedicalcare.com', 'Rosalia Prado', 'Director of Operations', 'rosalia.prado@novamedicalcare.com', '', 'YES', 44, 'Director of Operations at a 23-employee healthcare practice shows strong persona fit but limited firmographic signals due to missing geography, revenue, and technology data.', 'Nova Medical Services is a multi-specialty physician group serving Florida with 23 employees, providing comprehensive care across multiple specialties and care settings including residential homes, skilled nursing facilities, and telehealth.', 'small', 'high', 'Multi-specialty practice with 23 employees likely struggling with complex insurance verification and payer portal management across different specialties and care settings', 'multi-specialty group, 23 employees, multiple care settings, residential homes, skilled nursing facilities, telehealth', 'high', 'Champion', 'high', 'With 23 staff managing insurance verifications across multiple specialties plus skilled nursing facilities, your team\'s probably drowning in payer portal logins.', 'billing staff overload', '23 staff, endless portal logins', 'Multi-specialty practices with skilled nursing components face a unique challenge that single-specialty clinics never encounter. Each payer portal requires different credentials, different workflows, different verification steps. When you\'re managing insurance verification across multiple specialties plus SNF services, staff spend more time logging into portals than actually verifying coverage. The complexity multiplies with every new specialty you add.', 'why I\'m writing about nova', 'Rosalia, I\'m reaching out because Calyxr specifically built our platform for multi-specialty operations like Nova Medical Services. Instead of your team juggling dozens of payer portal logins, our system centralizes insurance verification across all specialties and care settings into one workflow. One of our multi-specialty grou