(136, 30, '2026-03-18 15:01:37', 'REACH Medical', 'https://reachprojectinc.org', 'Samantha Stevenson', 'Director of Operations', 'sstevenson@reachmed.org', '', 'YES', 39, 'Director of Operations at a small healthcare practice (29 employees) fits the target persona but lacks clear pain signals and technology stack details. Small size and missing firmographic data limit scoring potential.', 'REACH Medical appears to be a community-focused healthcare organization with 29 employees, likely providing primary care or multi-specialty services with emphasis on patient accessibility and community outreach.', 'small', 'medium', 'Multi-specialty community practice with 29 employees likely struggling with manual insurance eligibility verification and payer portal logins across multiple specialties and insurance types', '29 employees suggesting multi-specialty practice, community focus indicating Medicare/Medicaid patients, likely managing multiple payer relationships, staff coordination across specialties', 'medium', 'Champion', 'high', 'With 29 staff managing multi-specialty eligibility checks, your team\'s probably logging into 8+ payer portals daily just for verification.', 'billing staff overload', '8+ payer portals daily', 'Multi-specialty practices with 29+ staff often find themselves juggling 8+ different payer portals just for insurance eligibility checks. Each specialty brings its own set of insurance types, and staff end up spending hours daily logging in, checking coverage, and manually updating patient records. The bigger the practice, the more portals pile up.', 'why I\'m writing today', 'That payer portal juggling act is exactly why I\'m reaching out about Calyxr. We handle real-time eligibility verification across all major payers in one place, so your team stops logging into multiple portals throughout the day. One of our multi-specialty groups went from 6 hours of daily portal work down to 30 minutes.', 'When 29 staff members spend even 15 minutes per day on payer portals, that\'s over 7 hours of daily admin time. At $25/hour, portal juggling costs about $45,000 annually in labor alone. Calyxr typically goes live within days, no long contracts required. Worth exploring how much time your team\'s really spending on this?', 'Hi Samantha, noticed REACH Medical\'s multi-specialty setup likely means your team\'s logging into quite a few payer portals daily for eligibility checks. Been working with similar practices on streamlining this process, curious about your current workflow?', '6 hours to 30 minutes', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://reachprojectinc.org) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '29', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://reachprojectinc.org) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'sstevenson@reachmed.org', '', '', '', 'hospital & health care', '', '', '', '', '', 'Director of Operations', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(137, 30, '2026-03-18 15:02:22', 'Sydenham Clinic', 'https://sydenhamclinic.com', 'Ashvath Bhatia', 'Director of Operations', 'ashvath@sydenhamclinic.com', '', 'YES', 44, 'Strong persona match with Director of Operations and healthcare industry fit, but small employee count (19) and missing geographic/technology signals limit upside potential.', 'Sydenham Clinic is a members-only concierge medicine practice offering personalized health management, longevity planning, and comprehensive preventive care with 24/7 access and advanced diagnostics.', 'small', 'low', 'Concierge medicine practice with 19 employees likely struggles with high-touch patient communication expectations and manual coordination of personalized care workflows', 'concierge medicine model, 24/7 access expectations, personalized care coordination, comprehensive preventive care, 19 employees managing high-touch services', 'low', 'Champion', 'high', 'With 19 staff managing concierge members expecting 24/7 access, your team\'s likely drowning in after-hours communication coordination.', 'staff burnout from premium service expectations', 'concierge members calling at 9pm', 'Most concierge practices with 15-25 staff hit the same wall around patient communication. Members pay premium fees expecting immediate responses, but coordinating after-hours calls across your team creates bottlenecks. Your staff ends up juggling personal phones for patient calls, losing track of who spoke with whom. The bigger the member base grows, the messier communication coordination becomes.', 'why we built calyxr', 'Built Calyxr specifically for concierge practices drowning in communication chaos. Our platform routes patient calls intelligently across your team, tracks all interactions automatically, and ensures no member request falls through cracks. One concierge practice in Miami reduced after-hours coordination time by 60% in their first month. The system handles the logistics so your 19 staff can focus on delivering care, not managing communication workflows.', 'Quick math: if each of your 19 team members handles 25 patient touches daily, that\'s 475+ coordination points where communication can break down. Each missed handoff costs member satisfaction and staff overtime. Calyxr eliminates the coordination overhead completely, no long contracts required. Goes live in days, not months. Worth exploring how this applies to Sydenham\'s member communication flow?', 'Noticed Sydenham\'s concierge model with 19 staff. Most practices that size struggle with after-hours patient communication coordination. Built something specifically for this challenge. Worth a brief conversation about your current communication workflow?', '19 staff, 500+ daily touches', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://sydenhamclinic.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '19', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://sydenhamclinic.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'ashvath@sydenhamclinic.com', '', '', '', 'hospital & health care', '', '', 