(140, 30, '2026-03-18 15:04:24', 'Wells Infusion', 'https://wellsinfusion.com', 'Menachem Goldfarb', 'Director of Operations', 'menachem@wellsinfusion.com', '', 'YES', 29, 'Strong Operations persona match (Director level) and healthcare industry fit, but very small size (6 employees) and lack of confirmatory signals limit the score significantly.', 'Wells Infusion Centers is a specialty infusion clinic providing premium infusion and injection services with dedicated prior authorization and benefits investigation teams to support both providers and patients.', 'small', 'high', 'High-complexity prior authorization processes for infusion treatments create significant administrative burden for your dedicated benefits investigation team', 'infusion specialty, dedicated prior auth team, benefits investigation focus, small 6-person team, premium service model requiring extensive insurance verification', 'high', 'Champion', 'high', 'With specialty infusion treatments requiring complex prior auths, your 6-person team likely spends significant time on manual insurance eligibility verification.', 'billing staff overload', 'prior auth bottlenecks', 'Most infusion centers with 6-person teams face the same challenge. Complex prior authorizations for specialty treatments can consume 3-4 hours per case, turning what should be clinical time into administrative marathon sessions. The benefits investigation workload often creates a cascade where patient start dates get pushed back while your team juggles insurance requirements, medical necessity documentation, and appeals processes.', 'streamlining infusion prior auths', 'That prior auth complexity is exactly why I wanted to reach out about Calyxr. We help infusion centers automate the insurance verification and prior authorization workflow, cutting that 3-4 hour manual process down to minutes. One similar center reduced their benefits investigation team\'s admin time by 75% while improving approval turnaround. The system handles the insurance calls, documentation tracking, and follow-ups automatically.', 'Quick math on those prior auth delays: if each case takes 3 hours of admin time at $25/hour, that\'s $75 in labor per patient before you factor in delayed starts and rework. Most centers see ROI within 30 days, and we can have you live within a week with no long-term contracts. Would it help to see how this works for a center with similar patient volume?', 'Hi Menachem, noticed Wells Infusion handles complex specialty treatments. Most infusion centers struggle with the prior auth burden on their benefits teams. We help automate that entire workflow. Worth a quick conversation about how other 6-person operations teams handle this?', 'cost of manual prior auths', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://wellsinfusion.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '6', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://wellsinfusion.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'menachem@wellsinfusion.com', '', '', '', 'hospital & health care', '', 