rst month.', 'Quick math: if your team handles 200 eligibility verifications weekly at 15 minutes each, that\'s 50 hours of admin work per week. At $20/hour, you\'re spending $52k annually just on verification calls. Most practices see ROI within 60 days, and there are no long-term contracts. Worth exploring what this could look like for your MLTC workflow?', 'Hey Eric, saw you\'re handling DOH assessments at Welltel with 34 staff. Most telehealth operations are drowning in Medicaid verification calls. We help practices like yours automate that entire process. Worth a quick conversation about your current workflow?', '15 minutes per verification', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://welltel.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '34', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://welltel.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'ehagerman@welltel.com', '', '', '', 'hospital & health care', '', '', '', '', '', 'Director of Operations', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(142, 30, '2026-03-18 15:05:49', 'Winner Regional Health', 'https://winnerregional.org', 'Deb Davis', 'Director of Operations', 'debra.k.davis@sanfordhealth.org', '', 'YES', 39, 'Strong persona match with Director of Operations and correct industry, but small size (44 employees) and missing key signals limit fit. Neutral scores on geography, revenue, and technology due to missing data.', 'Winner Regional Health is a comprehensive rural healthcare system in South Dakota providing primary care, emergency services, surgery, rehabilitation, hospital care, long-term care, and specialty outreach services. They operate as a multi-service healthcare campus with 44 employees serving the Winner, SD community.', 'mid-size', 'high', 'Rural multi-service healthcare system with 44 employees likely struggling with manual insurance verification and claim status tracking across multiple service lines', 'rural location, multi-specialty services, comprehensive care model, small staff relative to service breadth, emergency services, surgery center, long-term care mix', 'high', 'Champion', 'high', 'Managing insurance eligibility across your emergency, surgical, and outpatient services with 44 staff likely creates significant verification bottlenecks.', 'multi-service eligibility verification bottlenecks', '44 staff, endless verification delays', 'Most rural health systems with multiple service lines hit the same wall around 40-50 employees. Insurance verification starts taking longer when you\'re juggling emergency, surgical, and outpatient services with limited staff. Each department ends up calling the same payers, patients wait longer for answers, and your team spends more time on phones than patient care. The verification bottleneck only gets worse as patient volume grows.', 'why I\'m reaching out', 'Deb, I\'m writing because Calyxr helps rural health systems like Winner Regional eliminate insurance verification delays across multiple service lines. Instead of your 44 staff making individual calls to payers, our platform verifies eligibility and tracks claim status in real-time for all departments. One health system in Montana cut their verification time by 70% in the first month. Does Winner Regional currently handle verification manually across your different services?', 'Rural systems typically lose 3+ staff hours daily to verification hold times, costing around $180,000 annually in productivity alone. A health system in Wyoming recovered those hours within 60 days using Calyxr, with no long-term contracts required. The platform goes live in days, not months. What does your current verification process look like during your busiest patient intake periods?', 'Hi Deb, I work with rural health systems facing verification bottlenecks across multiple service lines. Winner Regional\'s setup with 44 staff managing emergency, surgical, and outpatient likely creates similar challenges. Worth a quick conversation about how other systems handle this?', '3 hours daily on hold', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://winnerregional.org) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '44', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://winnerregional.org) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-