(145, 30, '2026-03-18 15:07:43', 'MyTown Health Partners', 'https://mytownhealthpartners.com', 'Brenda Myers', 'Executive Director of Operations', 'bmyers@mytownhealthpartners.com', '', 'YES', 48, 'Small healthcare practice with ideal ops decision-maker title, but limited by small size (23 employees) and lack of clear pain/technology signals to boost score higher.', 'MyTown Health Partners is a healthcare organization focused on providing comprehensive care to medically underserved communities in rural, urban, and de-industrialized areas through partnerships with local providers.', 'small', 'high', 'Managing complex insurance eligibility and prior authorizations across multiple underserved patient populations with limited billing staff resources', 'medically underserved populations, small 23-person team, comprehensive care model, multiple community partnerships, likely high Medicaid/Medicare mix', 'high', 'Champion', 'high', 'With 23 staff serving underserved populations, your billing team likely burns hours daily on Medicaid eligibility verification and prior auth workflows.', 'billing staff overload', 'medicaid eligibility verification bottleneck', 'Most practices serving underserved populations spend 3-4 hours daily just on Medicaid eligibility verification. The manual back-and-forth with state systems creates bottlenecks that delay patient care and eat up precious billing staff time. With limited resources, every hour spent on verification is an hour not spent on revenue-generating activities.', 'why we built calyxr', 'That Medicaid verification bottleneck is exactly why we built Calyxr for healthcare operations teams. Our platform handles eligibility verification and prior auth workflows automatically, so your billing staff can focus on higher-value work instead of chasing down coverage details. One practice with 25 staff reduced their verification time from 4 hours to 30 minutes daily.', 'Quick math: 4 hours of daily verification work costs about $52,000 annually in staff time. Most practices see ROI within 60 days with Calyxr, and we go live in days, not months, with no long contracts. Would it make sense to see how this works for underserved populations like yours?', 'Hi Brenda, noticed MyTown Health Partners serves underserved populations. Most practices your size spend hours daily on Medicaid eligibility verification. We help operations teams automate this completely. Worth a brief conversation about how it works?', '4 hours daily adds up', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://mytownhealthpartners.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '23', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://mytownhealthpartners.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'bmyers@mytownhealthpartners.com', '', '', '', 'hospital & health care', '', '', '', '', '', 'Executive Director of Operations', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
