(146, 30, '2026-03-18 15:08:23', 'Forefront Concierge Medicine', 'https://forefrontconciergemedicine.com', 'Brad Andrews', 'Interim President and Head of Operations (following Chief of Staff Engagement)', 'brad@forefrontconciergemedicine.com', '', 'YES', 33, 'Small concierge medicine practice with operations leader title fit, but very small team size (5 employees) and concierge model may not align with high-volume patient communication needs that Calyxr optimizes for.', 'Forefront Concierge Medicine is a luxury concierge primary care practice in Southwest Florida focused on optimization and longevity medicine for high-achieving individuals. They operate a proactive, prevention-based medical model with personalized wellness strategies targeting affluent patients who want to maintain vitality and longevity.', 'small', 'low', 'Small 5-person team likely overwhelmed with manual patient communication and scheduling coordination for high-touch concierge services', 'small team size, high-touch concierge model, personalized service expectations, luxury patient demographic', 'low', 'Champion', 'high', 'With a 5-person team managing high-touch concierge patient communications, your manual coordination workload must be intense for optimization consultations and follow-ups.', 'small team operational overload', '5-person concierge teams', 'Concierge practices with small teams often face an interesting challenge. The same high-touch service that attracts patients creates a coordination nightmare behind the scenes. Manual scheduling for optimization consultations, follow-up communications, and care coordination can consume most of a 5-person team\'s day. The irony is that exceptional patient care requires so much manual work that it limits how many patients can actually receive that care.', 'about Forefront\'s coordination', 'The coordination workload at Forefront caught my attention, which is why I\'m writing. Calyxr handles the patient communication and scheduling coordination that typically overwhelms small concierge teams. Instead of your team manually managing consultation bookings and follow-ups, the platform handles these workflows automatically. One 4-person concierge practice freed up 15 hours weekly for actual patient care after implementation.', 'That 4-person practice calculated they were spending $2,400 weekly on coordination tasks that Calyxr now handles automatically, no long contracts required. For Forefront\'s team size, the math is similar. The platform goes live in days, not months. Would seeing how other 5-person concierge teams structure their patient communication workflows be useful?', 'Brad, noticed Forefront\'s 5-person team likely handles significant manual patient coordination for concierge services. Calyxr automates these workflows for similar practices. Worth a quick conversation about your current communication processes?', '15 hours weekly', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://forefrontconciergemedicine.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '5', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://forefrontconciergemedicine.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain +