(156, 33, '2026-03-19 13:38:46', 'Rankin County Hospital District', 'https://rankinhealth.org', 'Patty Ezell', 'Medical Records Office Manager', 'patty.ezell@rankincountyhospital.org', '', 'NO', 19, 'Hospital district with 36 employees indicates a small public/government facility, and Medical Records Office Manager lacks decision-making authority for patient communication solutions.', 'Rankin County Hospital District is a rural hospital system providing comprehensive healthcare services including emergency care, outpatient services, and wellness programs to the Rankin, Texas community.', 'small', 'high', 'Rural hospital with 36 employees likely struggling with manual insurance verification and payer portal management across multiple service lines without dedicated RCM staff', 'rural hospital system, comprehensive services, emergency care, outpatient services, small staff size relative to service complexity, likely serves Medicare/Medicaid heavy population', 'high', 'Influencer', 'low', 'With 36 staff covering emergency, outpatient, and wellness services, your team likely burns hours daily logging into different payer portals for eligibility checks.', 'billing staff overload', '36 staff, endless portals', 'Rural hospitals with lean teams face an impossible choice. Cover emergency services, outpatient care, and wellness programs with 36 people, or spend half the day jumping between insurance portals for eligibility checks. Most medical records teams at hospitals your size report 3-4 hours daily just logging into different payer systems. The math doesn\'t work when you\'re already stretched thin across multiple service lines.', 'why we built calyxr', 'Watching rural hospitals burn staff hours on manual insurance verification is exactly why we created Calyxr. Instead of your team logging into 15+ payer portals daily, Calyxr pulls eligibility data from all major insurers into one dashboard. Oakwood Community Hospital cut their verification time from 4 hours to 20 minutes per day with our system. What would your team do with those extra hours back?', 'Quick math: if your medical records team spends 4 hours daily on portal-hopping at $18/hour, that\'s $18,720 yearly just on insurance verification. Calyxr customers typically see ROI within 60 days, no long contracts required. Most hospitals go live within a week. Worth a 15-minute conversation to see if it makes sense for Rankin County?', 'Hi Patty, managing medical records across emergency and outpatient services with a 36-person team sounds like a juggling act. Curious how you handle insurance verification across all those different payer portals daily?', '20 minutes vs 4 hours', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://rankinhealth.org) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '36', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://rankinhealth.org) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'patty.ezell@rankincountyhospital.org', '', '', '', 'hospital & health care', '', '', '', '', '', 'Medical Records Office Manager', '', '', '', '