(157, 33, '2026-03-19 13:39:22', 'CARE CENTRAL URGENT CARE', 'https://carecentralurgentcare.com', 'Joseph Weekes', 'Office Manager', 'jweekes@carecentralurgentcare.com', '', 'YES', 26, 'Strong industry match for urgent care but limited by small team size and Office Manager persona. Could benefit from automation given typical urgent care operational challenges.', 'CARE CENTRAL URGENT CARE operates 4 urgent care locations across Southern Massachusetts, providing walk-in medical services for minor injuries, illnesses, and routine health needs including lab testing, X-rays, and specialized asthma/allergy care.', 'small', 'medium', 'Managing high patient volume across 4 locations with only 11 staff creates scheduling chaos and communication breakdowns for walk-in urgent care', 'urgent care specialty, 4 locations, only 11 employees, walk-in patients, high volume unpredictable scheduling', 'high', 'Gatekeeper', 'medium', 'Managing walk-in flow across 4 Southern Massachusetts locations with 11 staff means your front desk is constantly juggling patient intake, insurance verification, and location capacity.', 'operational overwhelm from understaffing', '11 staff, 4 locations', 'Managing walk-in urgent care across multiple locations with a lean team creates an impossible juggling act. Front desk staff bounce between patient intake, insurance verification, and tracking capacity at each site. Meanwhile, patients wait longer and staff burn out from the constant coordination chaos. Most urgent care groups this size hit the same wall around 4 locations.', 'why I\'m reaching out', 'I\'m writing because Calyxr specifically helps urgent care groups manage patient flow across multiple locations without adding staff. Our platform handles intake coordination, real-time capacity tracking, and insurance verification in one place. One group in Texas went from 45-minute average waits to 12 minutes across their 5 locations with the same team size.', 'Every extra 10 minutes of patient wait time costs about $32 in lost satisfaction scores and potential walkouts. Across 4 locations seeing 200+ patients daily, that adds up fast. We can show you exactly how other urgent care groups cut their coordination time in half. Would seeing a quick walkthrough of how this works for multi-location setups be useful?', 'Joseph, noticed Care Central runs 4 locations with 11 staff. Most urgent care groups hit coordination chaos at that scale. Worth a quick conversation about how others solved this without hiring more people?', 'the math on wait times', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://carecentralurgentcare.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '11', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://carecentralurgentcare.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'jweekes@carecentralurgentcare.com', '', '', '', 'hospital & health care', '', '', '', '', '', 'Office Manager', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(158, 33, '2026-03-19 13:39:57', 'Coastal Plus Medical Center', 'https://coastalcareplus.com', 'Joanna Gensch', 'Office Manager', 'joanna@coastalcareplus.com', '', 'YES', 20, 'Healthcare industry match with small practice size (9 employees) and Office Manager contact, but lacks technology signals, pain indicators, and senior decision-maker authority.', 'Coastal Plus Medical Center is a family medicine and chiropractic practice in Jacksonville serving patients since 1989, offering primary care, urgent care, and specialized auto accident injury treatment.', 'small', 'medium', 'Small 9-person team managing primary care, urgent care, and auto accident cases likely struggles with insurance verification and claim management across multiple specialties and payer types', 'multi-specialty practice, auto accident treatment (complex insurance), urgent care (high patient volume), small team size, established practice likely has legacy processes', 'high', 'Gatekeeper', 'medium', 'Managing insurance verification for auto accident cases alongside regular primary care patients with just 9 staff creates serious bottlenecks.', 'billing staff overload', '9 people, 3 specialties', 'Small teams handling primary care, urgent care, and auto accident cases face an impossible math problem. Insurance verification for auto accidents requires completely different workflows than standard primary care visits. Most 9-person practices spend 3-4 hours daily just on verification calls, leaving patients waiting and staff overwhelmed. The specialty mix creates constant workflow interruptions.', 'why I\'m writing', 'I\'m reaching out because Calyxr helps practices like Coastal Plus Medical Center streamline insurance verification across multiple specialties. Our platform handles the different verification requirements for primary care, urgent care, and auto accident cases in one unified workflow. One practice with similar specialty mix reduced their verification time from 4 hours to 45 minutes daily.', 'Verification delays cost practices an average of $847 per day in denied claims and rework. For multi-specialty practices, that number jumps to over $1,200 daily. Calyxr typically pays for itself within the first month, with no long contracts or lengthy implementations. Most practices are live within days. Curious how much time your team currently spends on daily verification calls?', 'Hi Joanna, noticed Coastal Plus handles primary care, urgent care, and auto accidents with just 9 staff. Managing insurance verification across those specialties must create constant workflow challenges. Worth a quick conversation about streamlining that process?', 'cost of verification delays', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://coastalcareplus.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '9', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://coastalcareplus.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'joanna@coastalcareplus.com', '', '', '', 'hospital & health care', '', '', '', '', '', 'Office Manager', '', '', '', '', '',