(163, 33, '2026-03-19 13:43:05', 'Milan Medical Group', 'https://milanmedicalgroupqc.com', 'Rebecca Kline', 'Office Manager', 'rkline@milanmedicalgroupqc.com', '', 'YES', 29, 'Small healthcare practice with 14 employees fits industry criteria but limited scale. Office Manager persona indicates operations focus but lacks senior decision-making authority for significant software investments.', 'Milan Medical Group is a multi-disciplinary family practice offering primary care, chiropractic, mental health, walk-in care, and diagnostic services with same-day appointments and walk-ins welcome.', 'small', 'high', 'Multi-disciplinary practice with 14 staff managing diverse appointment types, walk-ins, and same-day scheduling likely struggles with complex patient communication and workflow coordination across different service lines', 'multi-specialty practice, walk-in appointments, same-day scheduling, small staff for diverse services, complex appointment coordination', 'medium', 'Gatekeeper', 'medium', 'Coordinating same-day slots across primary care, chiropractic, and mental health with 14 staff must create constant scheduling conflicts and patient confusion.', 'multi-service scheduling chaos', '14 staff, same scheduling system', 'Multi-disciplinary practices with primary care, chiropractic, and mental health under one roof face a unique challenge. When 14 staff members are juggling same-day appointments across different service lines, patients often get double-booked or sent to the wrong provider. The constant back-and-forth between departments to confirm availability creates bottlenecks that frustrated patients notice immediately.', 'how Milan Medical could fix this', 'Rebecca, I\'m writing because Calyxr specifically handles the coordination mess that multi-specialty practices like Milan Medical Group deal with daily. Our platform automatically routes patients to the right provider based on their needs and real-time availability across all your service lines. One practice with 12 staff reduced scheduling conflicts by 78% in their first month.', 'Practices similar to Milan Medical Group typically waste 5-7 hours weekly on scheduling conflicts and patient redirects. That\'s roughly $200-300 in lost staff productivity per week, or $12,000+ annually. We can show you exactly how this works for multi-specialty practices, no long contracts required. Worth a quick look at how other 14-person teams handle this?', 'Rebecca, noticed Milan Medical Group manages multiple specialties with same-day scheduling. Multi-disciplinary practices often struggle with patient routing across service lines. Worth comparing notes on how other similar practices handle this coordination challenge?', '30 min weekly of scheduling fixes', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://milanmedicalgroupqc.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '14', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://milanmedicalgroupqc.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'rkline@milanmedicalgroupqc.com', '', '', '', 'hos