(179, 33, '2026-03-19 13:53:29', 'Internal Medicine of Milford', 'https://immct.com', 'Lorri Brown-Ominsky', 'Practice Administrator', 'lbrown-ominsky@immct.com', '', 'YES', 43, 'Internal medicine practice with 14 employees has strong industry fit and ideal Practice Administrator persona, but limited data on pain signals, technology stack, or growth indicators to support higher scoring.', 'Internal Medicine of Milford is a primary care practice in Connecticut offering comprehensive internal medicine services with same-day appointments and extended hours including Saturdays.', 'small', 'medium', 'Primary care practice with 14 employees likely struggling with high patient volume communication, missed appointment follow-ups, and manual insurance verification workflows across their extended hours operation', 'primary care specialty, 14 employees, same-day appointments, extended hours including Saturdays, high patient turnover typical of internal medicine', 'medium', 'Gatekeeper', 'medium', 'With 14 staff managing same-day appointments plus Saturday hours, your team\'s probably drowning in eligibility checks and appointment confirmations.', 'staff overload from extended hours operations', '14 staff, endless eligibility checks', 'Primary care practices running same-day appointments plus Saturday hours face a brutal reality. Staff spend hours daily on insurance eligibility verification, calling carriers while patients wait. The manual checking, the hold times, the denials discovered after care delivery. Most practices this size lose 8-12 hours weekly just on verification workflows that could happen automatically.', 'why I\'m writing about eligibility', 'I\'m reaching out because Calyxr eliminates manual insurance verification for primary care practices. Real-time eligibility checks happen automatically before appointments, no staff time required. Internal Medicine Associates reduced their verification workload by 85% in the first month. Does automatic eligibility verification sound like something worth exploring for your Saturday appointment schedule?', 'Practices similar to Internal Medicine of Milford typically waste $2,400 monthly on manual eligibility workflows. That\'s staff time that could go to patient care instead of carrier hold music. Calyxr goes live in days, no long contracts required. Would you be curious to see how automatic verification could work with your current appointment system?', 'Hi Lorri, noticed Internal Medicine of Milford runs Saturday hours with same-day appointments. Most practices that size spend way too much time on manual insurance verification. Worth a quick conversation about streamlining that workflow?', '12 hours weekly back to patient care', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://immct.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '14', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://immct.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'lbrown-ominsky@immct.com', '', '', '', 'hospital & health care', '', '', '', '', '', 'Practice Administrator',