 in their first month. Does your current system verify coverage before appointments, or is your team still making those calls manually?', 'If verification callbacks are taking 3 hours of staff time daily, that\'s $45,000 yearly in labor costs just for insurance checks. Most practices our size see verification drop to under 30 minutes per day within two weeks, no long contracts required. Would it help to see how this works with a 15-minute walkthrough of your current verification process?', 'Hi Yadira, noticed Internal Medicine of Milford offers same-day appointments with 14 staff. Most practices that size get buried in insurance verification callbacks. Worth a quick conversation about how some are handling this differently?', '3 hours daily vs 30 minutes', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://immct.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '14', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://immct.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'yriddle@immct.com', '', '', '', 'hospital & health care', '', '