(181, 33, '2026-03-19 13:54:43', 'Medical Associates of Marlboro', 'https://maomhealth.com', 'Ellen Walter', 'Practice Administrator', 'ellenw@maomhealth.com', '', 'YES', 37, 'Practice Administrator at 36-employee healthcare practice shows strong persona fit, but missing geographic, revenue, and technology signals limit scoring potential.', 'Medical Associates of Marlboro is a leading multi-specialty healthcare practice in New Jersey with 7 locations offering internal medicine, cardiology, gastroenterology, and hematology/oncology services. With 36 employees and multiple board-certified physicians, they provide comprehensive care including on-site diagnostic testing.', 'mid-size', 'high', 'Managing insurance eligibility verification and prior authorizations across 4 high-complexity specialties at 7 locations is overwhelming your billing team with manual portal logins and coordination', 'multi-specialty practice, 7 locations, cardiology/oncology/gastroenterology specialties, high prior auth requirements, 36 employees managing complex insurance workflows', 'high', 'Gatekeeper', 'medium', 'With hematology/oncology and cardiology across 7 locations, your billing team is probably drowning in prior auth requests and eligibility checks.', 'billing staff overload from high-complexity specialty requirements', '36 staff, 7 locations, endless prior auths', 'Managing prior authorizations for hematology/oncology and cardiology across multiple locations creates a perfect storm. Each specialty has different requirements, each location operates slightly differently, and insurance portals don\'t talk to each other. The result is billing staff spending hours every day on manual eligibility checks and prior auth coordination instead of revenue-generating activities. Many multi-location practices with complex specialties find their teams overwhelmed by this administrative burden.', 'why I\'m writing about prior auths', 'I\'m reaching out because Calyxr helps multi-specialty practices streamline insurance verification and prior authorization workflows across all locations. Instead of your team logging into multiple portals throughout the day, everything runs through one system that handles eligibility checks and tracks prior auth status in real-time. One practice with 5 locations reduced their prior auth processing time by 60% in the first month.', 'If your billing team spends 3 hours daily on manual prior auths and eligibility checks, that\'s roughly $45,000 in labor costs annually, plus delayed treatments and frustrated patients. Most practices see ROI within 90 days, with no long contracts and systems live in days not months. Would it help to see how this works with a practice similar to yours?', 'Hi Ellen, noticed Medical Associates manages complex prior auths across 7 locations. Most multi-specialty practices struggle with the manual coordination between hematology/oncology and cardiology requirements. Worth a quick conversation about streamlining this?', 'the prior auth math', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://maomhealth.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '36', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://maomhealth.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'ellenw@maomhealth.com', '', '', '', 'hospital & health care', '', '', '', '', '', 'Practice Administrator', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(182, 33, '2026-03-19 13:55:17', 'Sabal Direct Primary Care', 'https://sabaldpc.com', 'Tyler Emmons', 'Practice Administrator', 'tyler@sabaldpc.com', '', 'YES', 39, 'Direct primary care practice with Practice Administrator contact shows industry fit but very small size (4 employees) limits automation needs. Missing key data points reduce overall scoring potential.', 'Sabal Direct Primary Care is a small family-focused direct primary care practice in Ocala, Florida operating on a membership-based model that bypasses traditional insurance billing. They emphasize affordable upfront pricing and direct patient-doctor relationships with mobile app access.', 'small', 'low', 'Direct primary care practice likely struggles with patient communication and scheduling coordination across their membership base with minimal administrative staff', '4 employees total, direct primary care model, family practice, membership-based model, mobile app mentioned', 'low', 'Gatekeeper', 'medium', 'Running a membership-based DPC practice with just 4 staff means your administrator is likely juggling member onboarding, scheduling, and payment coordination manually.', 'administrative bottleneck with small team', 'membership coordination chaos', 'Direct primary care practices with small teams often find themselves drowning in member coordination tasks. Between onboarding new patients, managing recurring appointments, and handling payment coordination, practice administrators end up juggling multiple systems just to keep the membership base organized. The challenge gets worse as membership grows, but adding full-time staff isn\'t always financially viable for smaller DPC practices.', 'why calyxr built for dpc', 'Hi Tyler, I\'m reaching out because Calyxr helps DPC practices like Sabal streamline member coordination without adding headcount. Our platform handles patient onboarding workflows, appointment scheduling, and payment coordination in one system designed specifically for membership-based practices. Desert Bloom Family Medicine reduced their administrative time by 60% while growing their membership base with the same staff size.', 'Most DPC administrators spend 15+ hours weekly on manual coordination tasks that could run automatically. That\'s essentially losing a part-time employee\'s worth of productivity each week. Calyxr typically goes live within days, no long contracts required. Would you be curious to see how the member coordination flows work for other 4-person DPC teams?', 'Hi Tyler, noticed Sabal DPC has stayed lean with just 4 staff. Most DPC practices your size struggle with member coordination workflows. Mind if I share how similar practices handle this without adding headcount?', '15 hours back per week', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://sabaldpc.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '4', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://sabaldpc.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'tyler@sabaldpc.com', '', '', '', 'hospital & health care', '', '', '', '', '', 'Pra