(183, 33, '2026-03-19 13:55:54', 'ZoeRVA Health', 'https://zoerva.com', 'Kearby Chen', 'Practice Administrator, Zoe Primary Care', 'kchen@zoerva.com', '', 'YES', 39, 'Small healthcare practice (28 employees) with strong persona fit (Practice Administrator) but lacks key technology signals and pain indicators needed for higher scoring.', 'ZoeRVA Health is an integrated mental health and primary care practice offering counseling, psychiatric medication management, and lifestyle medicine services. They combine therapy services with primary care in a holistic mind-body approach to wellness.', 'mid-size', 'high', 'Managing complex scheduling for both therapy appointments and primary care visits with dual-provider coordination creates scheduling bottlenecks and patient communication gaps.', 'integrated mental health and primary care, dual-provider coordination, 28 employees, complex appointment types, holistic care model requiring coordination', 'medium', 'Gatekeeper', 'medium', 'Managing dual-provider coordination between your therapy and primary care teams likely creates scheduling conflicts when patients need both services within tight timeframes.', 'scheduling bottlenecks and coordination complexity', 'dual provider scheduling chaos', 'Most integrated practices with therapy and primary care struggle with the same coordination nightmare. When patients need both services within days of each other, the scheduling dance between providers creates bottlenecks that ripple through the entire day. The back-and-forth between teams, double-booked slots, and patients caught in communication gaps turn what should be seamless care into operational chaos.', 'why calyxr built this', 'That dual-provider scheduling challenge is exactly why Calyxr exists. Our platform eliminates the coordination chaos by giving both your therapy and primary care teams real-time visibility into each other\'s schedules, so patients get seamless booking without the administrative ping-pong. One integrated practice reduced their scheduling conflicts by 78% in the first month.', 'With 28 team members coordinating dual services, those scheduling bottlenecks probably cost ZoeRVA 15-20 hours weekly in pure administrative overhead. Calyxr typically pays for itself within 60 days through eliminated coordination time alone, no long contracts required. Would it help to see how this looks for a practice your size?', 'Hi Kearby, noticed ZoeRVA integrates therapy and primary care. That dual-provider scheduling coordination must create some interesting operational challenges. Worth a quick conversation about how similar practices handle it?', '28 staff, endless scheduling loops', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://zoerva.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '28', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://zoerva.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'kchen@zoerva.com', '', '', '', 'hospital & health care', '', '', '', '', '', 'Practice Administrator, Zoe Primary Care', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, 