(192, 33, '2026-03-19 14:02:43', 'Sevi Health', 'https://sevihealth.com', 'Anna Remillard', 'Practice Manager', 'anna@sevihealth.com', '', 'YES', 34, 'Small healthcare practice with Practice Manager contact but very limited data points. Industry match provides base fit, but missing geography, revenue, and technology signals prevent higher scoring.', 'Sevi Health is a physician-founded wellness-focused healthcare organization offering holistic health services including yoga, nutritional advice, and emotional support through their clinics and Sevi Life programs.', 'small', 'medium', 'Small 15-person wellness practice likely struggles with manual patient communication and appointment scheduling across holistic services requiring different prep and follow-up', 'small team size, wellness specialty requiring complex scheduling, holistic services needing varied patient prep, physician-founded practice likely lacking operational systems', 'low', 'Gatekeeper', 'medium', 'Managing appointment prep and follow-up communications for yoga sessions, nutrition consults, and wellness programs across 15 staff must create significant coordination overhead.', 'multi-service coordination complexity', 'coordination overhead at 15-person practices', 'Most wellness practices with 15+ staff hit the same wall around patient communications. Yoga sessions need different prep instructions than nutrition consults, wellness programs require unique follow-ups, and someone has to coordinate it all. The manual juggling act between appointment types, staff schedules, and patient touchpoints becomes a full-time coordination job. Many practice managers find themselves spending more time organizing communications than actually improving patient care.', 'why calyxr built patient communication workflows', 'That coordination overhead is exactly why we built Calyxr. Instead of manually managing different prep instructions for yoga sessions versus nutrition consults, practices automate the entire patient communication flow by service type. Each appointment automatically triggers the right prep materials, follow-up sequences, and staff notifications. One wellness practice reduced their coordination time by 12 hours per week while improving patient preparation rates.', 'Quick math on coordination time: 12 hours weekly at $25/hour manager time equals $15,600 annually just in coordination overhead. Most wellness practices see their patient communication workflows live within days, no long contracts required. Worth exploring how much coordination time your 15-person practice could reclaim?', 'Anna, noticed Sevi Health manages holistic services across 15 staff. Most wellness practices that size hit coordination walls around patient communications between different service types. Worth a quick conversation about streamlined workflows?', '12 hours weekly versus current coordination', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://sevihealth.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '15', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://sevihealth.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'anna@sevihealth.com', '', '', '', 'hospital & health care', '', '', '', '', '', 'Practice Manager', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
