(193, 33, '2026-03-19 14:03:21', 'TrueMedicine PA', 'https://truemedicinepa.com', 'Felice Botiller', 'Practice Manager', 'felice@truemedicinepa.com', '', 'YES', 29, 'Small healthcare practice with 9 employees and Practice Manager contact fits basic profile, but lacks key signals like named EHR, geographic data, pain indicators, and technology stack details needed for higher scoring.', 'TrueMedicine PA is a direct primary care practice offering internal medicine services with a concierge model that eliminates traditional insurance billing. The practice focuses on creating direct patient-physician relationships through membership plans and 24/7 access including telemedicine.', 'small', 'low', 'Patient communication and scheduling coordination across 24/7 access model with only 9 staff members creates operational bottlenecks', 'direct primary care model, 24/7 patient access, telemedicine offering, small 9-person team, concierge service expectations', 'low', 'Gatekeeper', 'low', 'Running 24/7 patient access with just 9 staff means your team is juggling membership inquiries, urgent care scheduling, and telemedicine coordination around the clock.', 'staff overload from always-on patient access model', '24/7 access with 9 staff', 'Running 24/7 patient access with just 9 staff means your team is juggling membership inquiries, urgent care scheduling, and telemedicine coordination around the clock. Many practices with similar models find their staff stretched across too many communication channels, creating bottlenecks that slow down patient response times. The constant switching between membership calls, urgent scheduling requests, and telehealth coordination can leave even the most organized teams feeling overwhelmed.', 'why I\'m writing about TrueMedicine', 'I\'m reaching out because Calyxr helps practices like TrueMedicine streamline patient communications across all access points from one central hub. Instead of your 9 staff members juggling separate systems for membership, urgent care, and telehealth scheduling, everything flows through unified workflows. One practice manager told us it eliminated the constant channel switching that was burning out her small team.', 'Most practices with 24/7 access models see 40% faster patient response times when they consolidate their communication workflows, which directly impacts member satisfaction and retention. Calyxr typically goes live within days, no long contracts required. Would faster patient communication coordination make a meaningful difference for your team\'s daily workload?', 'Hi Felice, managing 24/7 patient access with 9 staff has to create some interesting operational challenges. I work with practices dealing with similar communication bottlenecks and thought you might find our approach helpful. Worth a quick conversation?', 'quick question about response times', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://truemedicinepa.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '9', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://truemedicinepa.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriche