(197, 33, '2026-03-19 14:06:16', 'ZoeRVA Health', 'https://zoerva.com', 'Jaclyn Vaseleck', 'Practice Manager', 'jvaseleck@zoerva.com', '', 'YES', 42, 'Strong industry match and Practice Manager title but small team size limits growth potential. Missing key data on EHR, location, and pain signals reduces overall scoring.', 'ZoeRVA Health is an integrated mental health and primary care practice that combines therapy services, psychiatric medication management, and lifestyle medicine under one roof. They serve patients seeking comprehensive mind-body wellness solutions with a focus on understanding root causes of health issues.', 'small', 'high', 'Managing complex scheduling coordination between mental health providers and primary care staff while handling insurance verification for dual-specialty services', 'integrated dual-specialty practice, mental health + primary care coordination, 28 employees indicating complex staffing, insurance complexity across specialties, appointment scheduling complexity', 'medium', 'Gatekeeper', 'medium', 'With 28 staff coordinating dual-specialty appointments between therapy and primary care, your team likely spends hours daily on insurance eligibility checks across different provider networks.', 'staff coordination overload with dual-specialty insurance verification', 'dual specialty scheduling chaos', 'Most practices with both mental health and primary care find their staff drowning in coordination calls. Between verifying insurance eligibility across different provider networks and syncing therapist availability with medical appointments, teams often spend 3-4 hours daily just on scheduling logistics. The complexity multiplies when patients need both services, creating bottlenecks that frustrate staff and delay patient care.', 'why I\'m writing about ZoeRVA', 'Your 28-person team handling dual-specialty coordination is exactly why I reached out about Calyxr. We help integrated practices streamline insurance verification and provider scheduling from one platform instead of juggling multiple systems. One practice manager told us it cut their daily coordination time from 4 hours to 45 minutes. Worth exploring how this applies to ZoeRVA\'s setup?', 'If your team spends 4 hours daily on scheduling coordination, that\'s roughly $40,000 annually in staff time just managing logistics. Most practices see this drop by 75% within the first month with Calyxr, no long contracts required. We can show you exactly how this would work with your dual-specialty model in about 15 minutes. What would free up that much daily admin time mean for your patient flow?', 'Managing scheduling between mental health and primary care with 28 staff sounds like a coordination nightmare. We help practices like ZoeRVA streamline this exact challenge. Mind if I share how similar integrated practices cut their daily admin time by 75%?', 'the 4 hour daily cost', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://zoerva.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '28', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://zoerva.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV