(198, 33, '2026-03-19 14:07:00', 'Emergence Health Holdings', 'https://emergencehealth.com', 'Kevin Spring', 'President and Chief Operating Officer', 'kspring@ccmdcenters.com', '', 'YES', 54, 'Strong persona fit with President/COO at small healthcare organization (24 employees), but limited signals for technology stack, pain points, or growth indicators. Missing geographic and revenue data limits scoring potential.', 'Emergence Health Holdings is a parent company operating two urgent care brands (CareWell and ClearChoiceMD) across New England with 24+ locations providing on-demand healthcare services. Established in 2021 as a holding company for brands founded in 2012-2014, indicating rapid expansion and consolidation strategy.', 'large', 'high', 'Managing patient communication and scheduling across 24+ urgent care locations with only 24 employees creates massive operational bottlenecks and missed revenue opportunities', 'multi-location urgent care, 24+ locations with lean staffing, on-demand healthcare model, rapid expansion since 2021, urgent care specialty requires high patient turnover', 'high', 'Champion', 'high', 'Operating 24+ urgent care locations with just 24 employees means your intake staff are drowning in eligibility verifications during peak walk-in hours.', 'billing staff overload', '24 locations, 24 employees', 'Most urgent care chains hit a breaking point around 20+ locations where patient intake becomes chaos. Walk-ins pile up during peak hours while staff scramble between eligibility checks, scheduling conflicts, and basic triage. The math just doesn\'t work when you\'re running lean across that many sites.', 'why we built calyxr', 'Kevin, urgent care operators kept telling us the same story about intake bottlenecks, so we built Calyxr to handle the heavy lifting. Our platform manages eligibility verification, patient flow, and scheduling coordination across multiple locations from one dashboard. Genesis Health saw 40% faster patient processing within their first month.', 'Every minute a patient waits past the 15-minute mark, you lose 12% chance they\'ll return. Across 24+ locations, those delays add up to serious revenue leakage. Calyxr typically pays for itself in recovered patient volume within 60 days, no long contracts required. Worth exploring what your current intake delays might be costing?', 'Kevin, noticed you\'re scaling 24+ urgent care locations with a tight team. The patient intake juggle across that many sites has to be brutal during peak hours. Mind if I share how similar operators are solving this?', 'the 3pm rush problem', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://emergencehealth.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '24', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://emergencehealth.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'kspring@ccmdcenters.com', '', '', '', 'hospital & health care', '', '', '', '', '', 'President and Chief Operating Officer', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(199, 33, '2026-03-19 14:07:56', 'MyTown Health', 'https://mytownhealthpartners.com', 'Brittany Frost', 'Regional Director of Operations', 'bfrost@mytownhealthpartners.com', '', 'YES', 39, 'Strong persona fit with Regional Director of Operations and healthcare industry match, but small employee count (23) and lack of key signals limit overall qualification score.', 'MyTown Health Partners is a healthcare organization focused on providing comprehensive care to medically underserved communities in rural, urban, and de-industrialized areas. They appear to be a partnership-based organization that works with local providers to expand access and integrate value-based care models.', 'small', 'high', 'Multi-location coordination across underserved communities creates significant administrative burden with manual insurance verification and claim management workflows', 'medically underserved populations, partnership-based model, value-based care focus, small team for multi-location operations, likely high Medicare/Medicaid volume', 'high', 'Champion', 'high', 'Managing insurance eligibility across 23 staff serving multiple underserved communities likely means your team spends hours daily on manual verification calls.', 'staff time drain on repetitive verification tasks', '23 staff, endless verification calls', 'Managing insurance eligibility across multiple underserved communities means someone on your team is constantly on hold with insurance companies. Between 23 staff members serving different locations, the manual verification calls add up fast. Most regional operations directors tell us their teams spend 2-3 hours daily just confirming patient coverage before appointments. The administrative burden keeps growing as patient volumes increase.', 'why we built calyxr', 'Built Calyxr specifically for multi-location healthcare operations struggling with manual insurance workflows. Instead of your team making dozens of verification calls daily, Calyxr handles eligibility checks automatically across all your locations. One regional director reduced their verification time from 3 hours to 15 minutes daily after going live. The system works seamlessly whether you\'re coordinating 2 locations or 20.', 'Quick math on those manual verification workflows: 3 hours daily at $20/hour equals $15,600 annually just in staff time. That doesn\'t count the missed appointments from verification delays or the patient experience impact. Most practices see ROI within 60 days, and we can have you live in under a week with no long contracts required. Worth exploring how much time your team could reclaim?', 'Noticed MyTown Health serves multiple underserved communities with 23 staff. Managing insurance verification across all those locations must create quite the daily workload. Built something that might help streamline that process significantly.', '3 hours daily adds up quickly', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://mytownhealthpartners.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '23', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://mytownhealthpartners.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'bfrost@mytownhealthpartners.com', '', '', '', 'hospital & health care', '', '', '', '', '', 'Regional Director of Operations', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(200, 33, '2026-03-19 14:08:49', 'MyTown Health', 'https://mytownhealthpartners.com', 'Courtney Walsh', 'Vice President of Operations', 'cwalsh@mytownhealthpartners.com', '', 'YES', 44, 'VP of Operations at a small healthcare practice (23 employees) is a strong persona match scoring 16/20 pts, but limited company data and small size reduce overall fit to partial match territory.', 'MyTown Health Partners is a healthcare organization focused on providing comprehensive care to medically underserved communities in rural, urban, and de-industrialized areas. They operate as a partnership model, working with local providers to expand access and integrate value-based care models.', 'small', 'high', 'Managing complex value-based care contracts across multiple underserved communities with limited administrative staff creates operational inefficiencies and potential revenue leakage', 'underserved patient populations, partnership model complexity, small staff size relative to multi-location operations, value-based care contracts, rural/urban mixed patient base', 'high', 'Champion', 'high', 'Managing value-based contracts across underserved communities with 23 staff likely means your team spends hours manually tracking patient engagement metrics.', 'administrative burden of value-based care reporting', 'value-based contract tracking', 'Many health systems serving underserved communities are drowning in manual patient engagement tracking for value-based contracts. Teams spend hours each week pulling data from different systems, creating reports, and calculating metrics that determine contract payments. With smaller administrative teams, this burden often falls on operations leaders who end up managing spreadsheets instead of focusing on patient outcomes. The manual work creates delays in identifying at-risk patients and reporting to payers.', 'why I\'m reaching out', 'Your role managing operations at MyTown Health caught my attention, especially given the complexity of tracking value-based metrics across underserved populations. Calyxr helps health systems like yours eliminate manual contract tracking by automatically pulling patient data, calculating engagement metrics, and generating payer reports. One of our clients reduced their contract reporting time from 15 hours per week to under 2 hours. Curious how your team currently handles the patient engagement tracking for your value-based contracts?', 'A 23-person team spending even 10 hours weekly on manual contract tracking costs roughly $15,000 per month in labor. That\'s $180,000 annually that could go toward patient care instead of administrative work. Our health system clients typically see their contract reporting burden drop by 80% within the first month, with no long contracts or lengthy implementations. Worth exploring what those time savings could mean for MyTown Health\'s operations?', 'Hi Courtney, noticed MyTown Health\'s focus on underserved communities. Many operations leaders in similar settings tell us they\'re drowning in manual value-based contract tracking. Curious if that resonates with your experience managing metrics across multiple communities?', '15 hours weekly savings', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://mytownhealthpartners.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '23', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://mytownhealthpartners.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'cwalsh@mytownhealthpartners.com', '', '', '', 'hospital & health care', '', '', '', '', '', 'Vice President of Operations', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(201, 33, '2026-03-19 14:09:36', 'WellcomeMD', 'https://wellcomemd.com', 'Jessica Parnell', 'Vice President of Operations', 'jessie.parnell@wellcomemd.com', '', 'YES', 48, 'VP of Operations at healthcare practice with 20 employees fits persona perfectly, but small size and missing technology/pain signals limit score to partial fit territory.', 'WellcomeMD is a concierge medicine practice operating in Virginia and North Carolina, offering personalized integrative membership-based healthcare with lower patient ratios and comprehensive wellness services. They focus on functional medicine approaches with same-day appointments and extended consultation times.', 'small', 'low', 'High-touch concierge model creates massive communication overhead with membership renewals, appointment coordination, and wellness program follow-ups that don\'t scale efficiently with current staffing', 'concierge/membership model, personalized care requirements, same-day scheduling complexity, wellness program coordination, extended consultation times, multi-state operations', 'medium', 'Champion', 'high', 'With 20 staff managing concierge membership communications across Virginia and North Carolina, your team\'s probably drowning in renewal calls and wellness follow-ups.', 'communication overhead scaling challenge', 'concierge communication burnout', 'Most concierge practices hit a wall around 20 staff members. The personal touch that makes membership valuable becomes the bottleneck that breaks operations. Renewal calls, wellness program coordination, and appointment follow-ups start consuming entire days. The math stops working when your team spends more time on communication overhead than actual patient care.', 'why I\'m reaching out', 'I\'m writing because Calyxr helps concierge practices like WellcomeMD scale high-touch communication without losing the personal feel. Instead of your Virginia and North Carolina teams drowning in renewal calls and wellness follow-ups, our platform handles the coordination while keeping everything feeling boutique. One practice reduced communication overhead by 60% while improving member satisfaction scores.', 'Peak renewal season with 20 staff doing manual outreach probably costs 200+ hours monthly in communication overhead alone. That\'s $15K+ in operational drag every month. Most practices see ROI within 30 days, no long contracts required. Would it make sense to see how this works for a practice your size?', 'Hey Jessica, noticed WellcomeMD\'s expansion across Virginia and North Carolina. The concierge communication challenge at your scale is real. Mind if I share how similar practices handle the overhead without losing that boutique feel?', 'the renewal season reality', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://wellcomemd.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '20', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://wellcomemd.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'jessie.parnell@wellcomemd.com', '', '', '', 'hospital & health care', '', '', '', '', '', 