(204, 33, '2026-03-19 14:11:45', 'RemoteFocus', 'https://remotefocus.com', 'Ethan Baraff', 'Vice President Operations', 'ebaraff@remotefocus.com', '', 'YES', 38, 'Strong VP Operations persona match but extremely limited data and small team size (14 employees) suggests minimal patient volume and limited revenue potential below ICP thresholds.', 'RemoteFocus is a virtual chronic care management platform serving 25k+ patients through telehealth services, remote patient monitoring, and care coordination for homecare agencies, payers, physicians, and patients.', 'mid-size', 'high', 'Managing insurance eligibility verification and claims processing for 25,000+ virtual chronic care patients across multiple payers with only 14 staff members creates massive administrative bottlenecks', '25k+ patient volume, 14-person team, virtual care model, chronic care management, multiple payer types, telehealth billing complexity', 'high', 'Champion', 'high', 'With 14 staff managing eligibility verification for 25,000+ chronic care patients across multiple payers, your team likely spends entire days just on insurance lookups.', 'billing staff overload', '14 staff, 25k patients', 'Most chronic care platforms hit a wall around 15,000 patients when it comes to insurance verification. The math just stops working. With 25,000+ virtual patients spread across multiple payers, even the most efficient teams find themselves drowning in eligibility lookups. The administrative load grows exponentially while staff count stays linear.', 'why I\'m writing', 'The insurance verification bottleneck is exactly why I\'m reaching out. Calyxr handles real-time eligibility verification and claims processing for virtual care platforms like RemoteFocus. One chronic care network reduced their verification time from 4 hours per patient to 12 minutes while managing 40,000+ patients with the same staff size.', 'Quick calculation: if your team spends 6 hours daily on insurance lookups, that\'s roughly $180,000 annua