(205, 33, '2026-03-19 14:12:35', 'Seniority Healthcare', 'https://seniorityhealthcare.com', 'Rachel Taylor', 'Vice President Operations', 'rachelt@seniorityhealthcare.com', '', 'YES', 49, 'Strong VP Operations persona fit and healthcare industry match, but limited signals available. Employee count in sweet spot range but missing key technology and pain indicators.', 'Seniority Healthcare is an in-home medical care provider serving seniors in private homes and senior living communities, focusing on preventing hospitalizations through frequent visits, telemedicine, and comprehensive care coordination.', 'small', 'high', 'Managing insurance eligibility verification and prior authorizations across multiple senior living locations with complex Medicare/Medicaid billing requirements', 'in-home care model, senior population, Medicare/Medicaid heavy, 41 employees across multiple locations, complex care coordination, frequent visits requiring ongoing eligibility checks', 'high', 'Champion', 'high', 'Managing eligibility verification across 40+ senior living facilities while coordinating Medicare Advantage and dual-eligible plans creates serious billing bottlenecks.', 'eligibility rework across complex Medicare/Medicaid billing', 'medicare verification bottlenecks', 'Most senior living operators with 40+ facilities hit the same wall with Medicare Advantage and dual-eligible plan verifications. Each location runs eligibility checks differently, creating billing delays that compound across properties. The manual coordination between facilities means verification bottlenecks pile up just when census is climbing. These delays turn into serious cash flow issues during peak admission periods.', 'why calyxr built this', 'Rachel, this Medicare verification chaos across multiple senior living locations is exactly why Calyxr exists. Our platform centralizes eligibility verification for Medicare Advantage and dual-eligible plans, letting your 40+ facilities run consistent checks from one system. One of our senior living clients cut their verification time by 60% in the first month after going live.', 'Senior living operators typically lose $80K annually per facility on delayed Medicare verifications and prior auth bottlenecks. Across 40+ locations, that compounds fast. Calyxr goes live in days, no long contracts required. Would it make sense to see how this works for facilities like yours?', 'Hi Rachel, noticed Seniority Healthcare manages 40+ senior living facilities. The Medicare verification coordination across that many locations has to create some serious bottlenecks. Mind if I share how similar operators handle this challenge?', 'cost of verification delays', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://seniorityhealthcare.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '41', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://seniorityhealthcare.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'rachelt@seniorityhealthcare.com', '', '', '', 'hospital & health care', '', '', '', '', '', 'Vice President O