(206, 33, '2026-03-19 14:13:23', 'Castle Connolly Top Doctors & Top Hospitals', 'https://castleconnolly.com', 'Caroline Baron', 'Vice President, Strategy, Marketing & Operations', 'cbaron@castleconnolly.com', '', 'NO', 0, 'Castle Connolly is a physician rating and hospital directory service, not a healthcare practice that treats patients directly, making them outside our target market of actual medical practices.', 'Castle Connolly is a healthcare directory and recognition service that identifies and ranks top doctors and hospitals nationwide, serving as a referral platform rather than a direct care provider.', 'small', 'low', 'As a healthcare directory service, Castle Connolly faces complex workflow coordination challenges managing referral communications and provider network validation across their 28-person team.', '28-person team coordination, healthcare directory operations, provider network management, referral platform complexity', 'low', 'Wrong Contact', 'low', 'Managing referral coordination and provider verification workflows across your 28-person team likely creates significant communication bottlenecks between directory operations and network partners.', 'workflow coordination overload', 'directory coordination bottlenecks', 'Most healthcare directory services with 25+ team members hit the same wall around referral coordination. Information gets trapped in email chains between operations staff and network partners. Provider verification requests bounce between departments, and status updates disappear into communication gaps. The bigger the directory network grows, the more these workflow bottlenecks compound.', 'workflow coordination for directories', 'Caroline, I\'m reaching out because Calyxr helps healthcare directory services streamline referral coordination across distributed teams. Instead of email chains and manual handoffs, everything flows through structured workflows that keep provider verification and network communication organized. One directory service reduced their coordination time by 60% within the first month. How are you currently managing workflow visibility across your 28-person team?', 'Directory services typically lose 8-12 hours per week to coordination delays and duplicate work across departments. That\'s roughly $15,000 in productivity costs monthly for a team your size. Calyxr gets directory operations running smoothly in days, not months, with no long-term contracts required. What would reclaiming those lost hours mean for your network expansion goals?', 'Hi Caroline, noticed Castle Connolly\'s growth and wondered how you\'re handling referral coordination across your expanding team. Most directory services hit workflow bottlenecks around your size. Worth a quick conversation about what\'s working for you?', 'coordination costs add up', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://castleconnolly.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '28', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://castleconnolly.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250