(207, 33, '2026-03-19 14:14:06', 'Clearwater Family Medicine and Allergy', 'https://cfma.health', 'Rachel Lyon', 'Volunteer, Office Manager, Domestic Engineer', 'rachel@cfma.health', '', 'NO', 0, 'Hard disqualified due to contact title containing \'Volunteer\' which indicates non-decision maker status and lack of purchasing authority.', 'Clearwater Family Medicine and Allergy is a multi-service primary care practice offering comprehensive family medicine, allergy/asthma care, weight management, hormone optimization, and direct primary care membership services with a focus on personalized, compassionate care.', 'small', 'high', 'Managing complex scheduling and patient communications across multiple service lines (family medicine, allergy, weight management, hormones) with only 7 staff members', 'multi-service specialty practice, small team size, allergy/asthma requires frequent follow-ups, direct primary care membership model, weight management and hormone optimization need specialized scheduling', 'medium', 'Gatekeeper', 'low', 'Managing appointment scheduling across four distinct service lines with just seven staff likely creates scheduling conflicts and patient communication gaps daily.', 'multi-specialty scheduling complexity with lean staffing', '7 staff, 4 service lines', 'Family medicine practices offering multiple specialties often hit a wall around 7-10 staff members. The scheduling complexity grows exponentially when you\'re juggling family medicine, allergy, weight management, and hormones appointments. Each service line has different appointment types, durations, and patient prep requirements. Staff spend more time coordinating schedules than serving patients.', 'scheduling coordination solution', 'Rachel, practices like Clearwater Family Medicine face this exact challenge, which is why I wanted to introduce Calyxr. We help multi-specialty practices coordinate scheduling and patient communications across all service lines from one system. A similar 8-person practice reduced scheduling conflicts by 78% in their first month. Instead of staff juggling four different workflows, everything flows through unified patient communication.', 'Practices with scheduling conflicts typically lose 15-20% revenue to no-shows and last-minute cancellations across their service lines. Calyxr practices see this drop to under 8% within 60 days, with no long contracts required. The system goes live in days, not months. Worth exploring how this might work for your four service lines?', 'Hi Rachel, noticed Clearwater Family Medicine manages four service lines with seven staff. That scheduling coordination challenge is exactly what we help practices solve. Mind if I share how similar practices streamlined this?', 'cost of scheduling chaos', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://cfma.health) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '7', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://cfma.health) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'rachel@cfma.health', '', '', '', 'hospital & health