(208, 33, '2026-03-19 14:14:52', 'Anovia Health', 'https://anoviahealth.com', 'Ken Strmiska', 'VP & COO', 'kstrmiska@anoviahealth.com', '', 'YES', 46, 'Strong persona fit with VP & COO title in healthcare industry, but limited by small team size (22 employees) and lack of visible technology or pain signals to drive higher scoring.', 'Anovia Health is a Wisconsin-based direct primary care (DPC) practice serving individual patients, employers, and brokers with a relationship-focused healthcare model. They won the DPC Innovation Award 2024 and emphasize proactive, personalized primary care.', 'small', 'low', 'Direct primary care model likely struggles with mixed payer communications and workflow coordination across individual patients, employers, and brokers requiring different engagement strategies', 'direct primary care model, serves multiple customer types (individuals/employers/brokers), relationship-focused care model, 22 employees suggesting moderate operational complexity', 'medium', 'Champion', 'high', 'Managing communication workflows across individual DPC members, employer groups, and broker partnerships with 22 staff likely creates coordination gaps.', 'workflow fragmentation across diverse stakeholder types', 'dpc coordination gaps', 'Direct primary care models face a unique challenge that traditional practices don\'t. When you\'re managing individual DPC members, employer groups, and broker partnerships simultaneously, communication workflows often create coordination gaps. Each stakeholder group needs different engagement strategies, but most systems treat them the same way. The result is staff juggling multiple processes for what should be streamlined patient care.', 'why I\'m writing', 'I\'m reaching out because Calyxr helps DPC practices like yours coordinate communication workflows across different stakeholder groups. Instead of your 22 staff members managing separate processes for individual members, employers, and brokers, everything runs through unified workflows designed for mixed payer models. One of our DPC clients reduced coordination time by 40% within their first month.', 'When coordination gaps persist, DPC practices typically see 15-20% more administrative overhead per patient relationship. That adds up quickly across employer groups and individual members. Calyxr goes live in days, not months, with no long contracts required. Worth exploring how this might work for Anovia\'s specific setup?', 'Hi Ken, noticed Anovia\'s growth in the DPC space. Managing communication workflows across individual members, employer groups, and brokers with 22 staff likely creates some interesting coordination challenges. Worth a quick conversation about how other DPC practices are solving this?', 'cost of coordination gaps', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://anoviahealth.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '22', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://anoviahealth.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'kstrmiska@anoviahealth.com', '', ''