(209, 33, '2026-03-19 14:15:39', 'NOVA MEDICAL SERVICES', 'https://novamedicalcare.com', 'Masiel Feito', 'VP of Clinical Operations', 'masiel.romero@novamedicalcare.com', '', 'YES', 34, 'Small healthcare practice with strong ops leadership fit (VP of Clinical Operations) but limited firmographic data and employee count below optimal range. Tier D due to insufficient qualifying signals.', 'Nova Medical Services is a multi-specialty physician group serving Florida with comprehensive care across multiple settings including residential homes, skilled nursing facilities, and hospitals. They operate with 23 employees and offer services ranging from family medicine to specialized care like cardiology, neurology, and pain management.', 'small', 'high', 'Multi-specialty practice across multiple care settings is drowning in manual insurance eligibility verification and payer portal logins for 23+ employees managing diverse patient populations', 'multi-specialty practice, multiple care settings (homes, SNFs, hospitals), 23 employees managing complex patient mix, cardiology/neurology/pain management specialties with high prior auth requirements, Florida market with diverse payer mix', 'high', 'Champion', 'high', 'Managing eligibility checks across skilled nursing facilities, residential homes, and hospitals with 23 staff juggling multiple payer portals daily.', 'multi-setting eligibility complexity', '23 employees, 50+ portal logins', 'Most multi-specialty practices with 20+ staff end up with someone logging into insurance portals every 15 minutes. Skilled nursing, residential care, hospitals, each with different payer requirements. The average clinical team member at a practice like yours juggles 8-12 different portal logins daily just for eligibility checks. It\'s become the hidden time sink that nobody talks about in operations meetings.', 'why we built calyxr', 'The portal juggling act is exactly why we built Calyxr for multi-specialty practices. Instead of 23 people logging into dozens of payer portals, our platform handles eligibility verification across all your care settings from one place. One of our clients went from 40+ daily portal logins across their team to zero, freeing up 6 hours daily for actual patient care.', 'Quick math on portal time: if your 23-person team spends even 15 minutes daily on eligibility logins, that\'s 29 hours weekly, $60k+ annually in staff time. Most practices see results within days, no long contracts required. Would it help to see exactly how this works for a practice managing your mix of care settings?', 'Hey Masiel, noticed NOVA manages patients across multiple care settings. The eligibility portal juggling act with 23+ staff has to be brutal. Built something specifically for this problem, curious if you\'d want to see how it works?', '6 hours daily vs 15 minutes', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://novamedicalcare.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '23', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://novamedicalcare.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (c