(230, 34, '2026-03-20 09:31:34', 'Salud Pediatrics', 'Salud Pediatrics', 'Deyci Rico', 'Billing Manager', 'deycimaria@spediatrics.com', '', 'YES', 56, 'Pediatric specialty with Billing Manager persona indicates strong claim status pain potential, but limited data prevents higher scoring.', 'Salud Pediatrics is a mid-size pediatric practice with 34 employees, likely serving a diverse patient population with significant Spanish-speaking families based on the \'Salud\' name, suggesting substantial Medicaid/CHIP billing complexity.', 'mid-size', 'high', 'Mid-size pediatric practice with 34 employees likely has 3-5 billers managing high Medicaid/CHIP volume serving Spanish-speaking families, creating significant manual claim status follow-up burden and extended hold times with government payers', '34 employees indicating mid-size practice, Salud name suggesting Spanish-speaking patient base, pediatric specialty with high Medicaid/CHIP enrollment rates, likely diverse patient population requiring complex payer mix management', 'high', 'Champion', 'high', 'With 34 staff serving a bilingual patient base, your billers likely spend 2+ hours daily on Medicaid hold times alone.', 'Medicaid hold time cost multiplied by bilingual patient complexity', 'medicaid hold times', 'Billing teams at mid-size pediatric practices are spending 2+ hours daily on hold with Medicaid and CHIP just chasing claim status. The government payers have the longest hold times in healthcare, and pediatric practices carry the highest volume of these slow-moving claims. Many billing managers are watching their teams lose entire afternoons to payer phone trees instead of working denials or processing new claims.', 'claim status without phone calls', 'That\'s exactly why Calyxr built our Claim Status Agent specifically for pediatric billing teams. Instead of your billers spending hours on Medicaid hold, our system runs automated 276/277 transactions and surfaces real-time claim status with zero phone calls to payers. One pediatric practice reduced their manual billing tasks by 70% in the first month. Is claim status follow-up still a manual process at your practice?', 'If your billing team spends 2+ hours daily on Medicaid hold times, that\'s roughly $25,000 annually in lost productivity per biller just chasing claim status. Most pediatric practices have this backwards, with experienced billers stuck on hold instead of working denials and collections. Worth seeing how other pediatric practices eliminated payer hold time entirely with no long contracts, live in days, no IT lift required. Is this still eating up your team\'s time?', 'Billing teams at pediatric practices spend hours daily on Medicaid hold just chasing claim status. Most don\'t realize there\'s a way to get real-time updates with zero phone calls to payers. Is this still a manual process at Salud Pediatrics?', '2+ hours daily on hold', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (Salud Pediatrics) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '34', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (Salud Pediatrics) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Ap