(234, 34, '2026-03-20 09:32:18', 'Pediatric Associates of Richmond', 'Pediatric Associates of Richmond', 'Trinika Jackson', 'Medical Biller', 'tjackson@parpeds.com', '', 'YES', 39, 'Pediatric practice with 39 employees shows strong specialty match but Medical Biller title lacks decision-making authority. Richmond location suggests US-based practice serving Medicaid-heavy pediatric population.', 'Pediatric Associates of Richmond appears to be a mid-size general pediatric practice with 39 employees serving the Richmond area, likely handling significant claim volumes across multiple payers including Virginia Medicaid.', 'mid-size', 'medium', 'Mid-size pediatric practice with 39 employees likely has 3-5 billers drowning in Virginia Medicaid claim status calls that can take 45+ minutes on hold per call', '39 employees suggesting mid-size practice with high patient volume, Virginia Medicaid known for complex claim status systems, general pediatric practice means high Medicaid/CHIP mix typical for pediatrics, likely 3-5 billing staff handling significant claim volume', 'high', 'Influencer', 'medium', 'With 39 staff members, your billing team is probably spending 6+ hours daily on Virginia Medicaid hold times alone.', 'Virginia Medicaid hold time cost at mid-size practice scale', 'virginia medicaid hold times', 'Trinika, many pediatric billing teams are spending 6+ hours daily just waiting on Virginia Medicaid hold times for claim status updates. With 3-5 billers at a 39-person practice like Pediatric Associates of Richmond, those 45+ minute hold times per call add up fast. The manual claim status follow-up process eats through entire days before any actual billing work gets done.', 'automated claim status updates', 'Trinika, that\'s why I\'m reaching out about Calyxr\'s Claim Status Agent. It automates your 276/277 claim status requests directly with Virginia Medicaid and other payers, no phone calls or portal logins required. Real-time claim status updates surface automatically, and denials appear immediately when they hit. Is claim status follow-up still a manual process at Pediatric Associates of Richmond?', 'Trinika, if your billing team is spending 6+ hours daily on Virginia Medicaid hold times, that\'s roughly $50,000+ in annual staff costs just for claim status follow-up. Worth seeing how other pediatric practices eliminated those hold times entirely with automated claim status tracking. No long contracts, live in days, no IT lift required. Is this something you\'d want to see in action?', 'Hi Trinika, many pediatric billing teams spend hours daily on Virginia Medicaid hold times just for claim status updates. Calyxr automates those 276/277 requests entirely. Is claim status follow-up still manual at Pediatric Associates of Richmond?', '6 hours daily on hold', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (Pediatric Associates of Richmond) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '39', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (Pediatric Associates of Richmond) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'tjackson@parpeds.com', '', '', '', 'medical practice', '', '', '', '', '', 'Medical Biller', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
