(236, 34, '2026-03-20 09:32:59', 'Eastern Pediatrics', 'Eastern Pediatrics', 'Yoicha Ray', 'Billing Manager', 'cookie@eastern.pcc.com', '', 'YES', 46, '17-employee pediatric practice with dedicated Billing Manager indicates manual claim status workflow and likely high Medicaid volume typical of pediatrics. Small team size suggests billing efficiency pain points.', 'Eastern Pediatrics is a mid-size pediatric practice with 17 employees, indicating a significant patient volume that likely requires substantial billing and claim status follow-up operations across multiple payers including Medicaid/CHIP.', 'mid-size', 'medium', '17-person pediatric practice likely has 2-4 billing staff managing high-volume Medicaid/CHIP claims with extensive manual payer portal logins and phone follow-ups consuming 10+ hours weekly', 'mid-size pediatric practice, 17 employees indicating high patient volume, Medicaid/CHIP heavy payer mix typical for pediatrics, likely small billing team relative to claim volume', 'high', 'Champion', 'high', 'With 17 staff members, your billing team is likely spending 10+ hours weekly navigating Medicaid portals and phone queues for claim status updates.', 'billing staff to volume ratio creating manual claim follow-up bottleneck', 'medicaid hold times', 'Most billing teams at 17-person pediatric practices like Eastern Pediatrics tell us they\'re spending 10+ hours weekly on Medicaid and CHIP claim status calls. The hold times with state payers keep getting longer, and the payer portals often show outdated information anyway. Meanwhile, AR keeps aging while staff sit on hold instead of working denials that actually need attention.', 're: claim status automation', 'That\'s why I\'m writing about Calyxr\'s Claim Status Agent. It automatically pulls 276/277 claim status directly from Medicaid and CHIP payers, so your billing team never has to log into another payer portal or sit on hold again. Pediatric practices using it see denials surface automatically while their staff focus on revenue-generating work instead of claim status detective work.', 'If your billing team is spending even 10 hours weekly on Medicaid hold times, that\'s over $25,000 annually in staff time just for claim status updates. We\'d be happy to show you exactly how the Claim Status Agent works for pediatric billing, no long contracts and you\'re live in days with no IT lift required. Is claim status follow-up still a manual process at Eastern Pediatrics?', 'Most billing teams at pediatric practices tell us they spend 10+ hours weekly on Medicaid hold times just for claim status. We built something that automates the entire 276/277 process so your team never sits on hold again. Is claim status still manual at Eastern Pediatrics?', '10 hours weekly on hold', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (Eastern Pediatrics) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '17', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (Eastern Pediatrics) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'cookie@eastern.pcc.com', '', '', '', 'hospital