(246, 34, '2026-03-20 09:34:11', 'Remy Healthcare', 'Remy Healthcare', 'Madison McFarlane', 'Revenue Cycle Manager', 'madison@remydata.com', '', 'NO', 18, 'Revenue Cycle Manager title is strong fit, but health/wellness/fitness industry suggests non-pediatric focus and likely lacks insurance billing workflows that drive claim status automation needs.', 'Remy Healthcare appears to be a mid-size healthcare practice with 18 employees in the health and wellness sector. Without specific pediatric indicators or website content, the practice type and billing complexity cannot be definitively determined.', 'mid-size', 'medium', 'With 18 employees and unknown specialty mix, billing team likely lacks bandwidth to manually track claim status across multiple payers leading to delayed follow-up on outstanding claims', 'mid-size practice with 18 employees, unknown specialty creates billing complexity uncertainty, no clear pediatric indicators but health/wellness sector suggests potential mixed payer types', 'medium', 'Champion', 'high', 'With 18 staff members, your revenue cycle team is probably spending 2-3 hours daily on payer portal logins for claim status checks.', 'billing staff to volume ratio creating portal login time burden', 'claim status tracking bottleneck', 'Madison, billing teams at 18-person practices like Remy Healthcare often find themselves caught in a daily cycle of logging into multiple payer portals just to check claim status. Between Medicaid, CHIP, and commercial payers, that\'s easily 2-3 hours per day of manual checking before any actual follow-up work begins. The irony is that the bigger the practice gets, the more time gets consumed by this administrative tracking rather than productive billing work.', 'automated claim status tracking', 'Madison, that\'s actually why I\'m reaching out about Calyxr\'s Claim Status Agent. Instead of your team logging into payer portals, our system automatically sends 276 requests and processes 277 responses in real-time, surfacing claim status updates and denials without any manual checking. One practice similar to Remy Healthcare saw a 70% reduction in manual billing tasks once they stopped chasing claim status by hand.', 'Madison, quick math on those 2-3 daily hours spent on claim status checks: that\'s 10-15 hours weekly, roughly $30k annually in staff time just for tracking. Meanwhile, actual denials and aging claims sit unaddressed. We can show you how claim status becomes completely hands-off, no long contracts, live in days, no IT lift required. Is claim status follow-up still a manual process at Remy Healthcare?', 'Hi Madison, billing teams at practices like Remy Healthcare typically spend 2-3 hours daily just logging into payer portals for claim status checks. That\'s a lot of productive billing hours lost to administrative tracking. Is claim status follow-up still manual at your practice?', 'billing hours vs revenue cycle', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (Remy Healthcare) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '18', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (Remy Healthcare) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'madison@remydata.com', '', '', '', 'health, wellness & fitness', '', '', '', '', '', 'Revenue Cycle Manager', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
