(273, 35, '2026-03-20 09:56:52', 'Gateway Pediatrics', 'https://gatewaypediatricsltd.com', 'Shari Milliano', 'Billing', 'millianos@gatewaypediatrics.com', '', 'YES', 43, 'Small pediatric practice with dedicated billing role suggests manual claim status workflows. Company name Gateway Pediatrics indicates specialty match, though missing geographic and technology signals limit optimization potential.', 'Gateway Pediatrics is a small general pediatric practice in Chesterfield, MO with 16 employees offering routine pediatric services including well-child visits, sick visits, sports physicals, and immunizations. The practice appears to have typical small practice billing workflows with likely manual claim status processes.', 'small', 'low', 'Small 16-person pediatric practice likely has 1-2 billing staff manually calling Medicaid/CHIP payers and logging into multiple portals daily for claim status on high-volume well-child visits and immunizations.', 'small practice size (16 employees), high-volume pediatric services (well-child visits, immunizations), typical small practice manual billing workflows, general pediatric specialty with likely high Medicaid/CHIP volume', 'medium', 'Champion', 'high', 'With 16 staff handling routine pediatric volume, your billing team likely spends 2+ hours daily on Medicaid hold times for well-child and immunization claims.', 'billing staff to volume ratio creating daily Medicaid hold time bottleneck', 'medicaid hold times eating hours', 'Most pediatric billing teams at 16-person practices spend 2+ hours daily on hold with Medicaid and CHIP for well-child and immunization claim status. Those 10+ hours weekly could be generating revenue instead of waiting for payer reps to pick up. The manual portal logins for each claim add another layer of time drain that compounds daily.', 'automated 276/277 claim tracking', 'Shari, that\'s why I\'m writing about Calyxr\'s Claim Status Agent. It automatically pulls 276/277 status updates on every claim without your team touching a payer portal or dialing a single number. Pediatric practices see denials surface immediately instead of weeks later when they finally get through to Medicaid reps. Is claim status follow-up still a manual process at Gateway Pediatrics?', 'If your billing staff spends 10+ hours weekly on Medicaid hold times, that\'s 520+ hours annually that could go toward collections or patient care. The cost compounds when claim issues sit unresolved for weeks while you wait for callbacks. Worth seeing how practices eliminate payer hold time entirely with no long contracts, live in days, no IT lift required. Is claim status follow-up still a manual process at your practice?', 'Hi Shari, most pediatric billing teams spend hours daily on Medicaid hold times chasing well-child claim status. Curious if that\'s still manual at Gateway Pediatrics or if you\'ve found ways around those endless hold times?', '10 hours weekly on hold', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://gatewaypediatricsltd.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '16', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://gatewaypediatricsltd.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'millianos@gatewaypediatrics.com', '', '', '', 'hospital & health care', '', '', '', '', '', 'Billing', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
