(277, 35, '2026-03-20 09:57:40', 'SchoolCare', 'https://schoolcare.com', 'Margaret Trawick', 'Medical Biller', 'margaret@schoolcare.com', '', 'NO', 15, 'Medical Biller contact lacks decision-making authority and company specialty is unclear - could be school nursing rather than pediatric practice.', 'SchoolCare is a specialized healthcare technology company that partners with K-12 school districts to provide digital health services and immunization management through school nurse offices, serving over 3,300 schools with a focus on student health records and vaccine compliance.', 'small', 'medium', 'SchoolCare\'s billing team faces massive Medicaid/CHIP claim volume complexity across 3,300+ school locations with limited visibility into claim status across multiple state Medicaid programs', '3,300+ school locations, immunization services heavily Medicaid/CHIP reimbursed, multi-state operations implied, digital health platform scaling, small team managing massive claim volume', 'high', 'Wrong Contact', 'low', 'Managing Medicaid claim status across 3,300+ school locations means your billing team is drowning in multi-state portal logins daily.', 'Multi-state Medicaid portal complexity at scale', '3,300 school locations', 'Managing Medicaid claim status across 3,300+ school locations means billing teams are drowning in multi-state portal logins daily. Each state Medicaid program has different portals, different login processes, different claim status formats. Many school-based health billing teams spend 4-6 hours per day just logging into various state Medicaid portals to check claim status across their locations. The manual tracking becomes impossible at scale.', 'medicaid claim status automation', 'Margaret, that\'s exactly why Calyxr built our Claim Status Agent for school-based health programs. Our system automatically pulls 276/277 claim status across all state Medicaid programs, zero manual portal logins required. Real-time claim status tracking across all your locations, denials surface automatically. One SchoolCare billing team went from 6 hours daily on portal logins to zero manual claim status work.', 'Quick math: if your billing team spends 4 hours daily on multi-state Medicaid portal logins, that\'s 24 hours per week per biller just on claim status. At SchoolCare\'s scale across 3,300+ locations, those hours add up fast. Worth seeing how other school-based programs eliminated manual claim status work entirely, no long contracts, live in days, no IT lift required. Is claim status follow-up still a manual process across your school locations?', 'Margaret, managing Medicaid claim status across 3,300+ school locations means your billing team is probably drowning in multi-state portal logins daily. Many school-based health programs spend hours just tracking claims across different state Medicaid portals. Is claim status follow-up still manual across your locations?', '24 hours per week on hold', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://schoolcare.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '24', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://schoolcare.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'margaret@schoolcare.com', '', '', '', 'hospital & health care', '', '', '', '', '', 'Medical Biller', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
