(292, 35, '2026-03-20 10:00:20', 'Prima Health Care', 'https://primahealthcareonline.com', 'Sharon Luisi', 'Billing', 'sluisi@primahealthcareonline.com', '', 'NO', 15, 'Contact has generic \'Billing\' title with no seniority level and no pediatric specialty confirmed. Company shows no clear pediatric focus or relevant pain signals.', 'Prima Health Care appears to be a mid-size healthcare organization with 39 employees, likely operating multiple locations or offering diverse services. Without website access, the exact pediatric focus and billing complexity cannot be definitively determined.', 'mid-size', 'medium', 'A 39-employee healthcare organization likely has a small billing team (2-4 billers) struggling to manage claim status across multiple locations or service lines without centralized visibility.', 'mid-size employee count suggesting multi-location complexity, likely small billing team relative to overall staff size, no clear specialty focus indicating diverse payer mix management challenges', 'medium', 'Champion', 'high', 'With 39 employees across multiple locations, your billing team is likely spending 4-6 hours daily on Medicaid hold times alone.', 'Multi-location billing staff time cost on Medicaid phone follow-up', 'medicaid hold times', 'Sharon, many billing teams at 39-employee healthcare organizations tell us they\'re spending 4-6 hours daily just on Medicaid hold times. With multiple locations or service lines, there\'s no centralized way to see which claims need follow-up, so billers end up calling the same numbers repeatedly. The worst part is how unpredictable Medicaid portals are, meaning yesterday\'s successful login might not work today.', 're: claim status automation', 'Sharon, that\'s actually why I\'m reaching out. Calyxr\'s Claim Status Agent handles 276/277 transactions automatically, so your billing team never has to log into payer portals or sit on hold with Medicaid again. One Prima-sized practice saw a 70% reduction in manual billing tasks within the first month. Real-time claim tracking means denials surface immediately instead of 30 days later.', 'Sharon, if your billing team is spending 6 hours daily on Medicaid hold times, that\'s roughly $45,000 annually in staff hours just chasing claim status. Most billing managers don\'t realize how much this costs until they see it automated. Would it be worth 15 minutes to see how other practices eliminated payer hold time entirely? No long contracts, live in days, no IT lift required.', 'Hi Sharon, noticed Prima Healthcare\'s size likely means your billing team spends significant time on Medicaid hold times for claim status. Is claim status follow-up still a manual process at your practice?', '6 hours daily adds up', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://primahealthcareonline.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '39', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://primahealthcareonline.com) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (Apollo export, pre-enriched) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'sluisi@primahealthcareonline.com', '', '', '', 'hospital 