(311, 36, '2026-03-24 07:45:20', 'Associates of Internal Medicine', 'http://www.drwiddows.com', NULL, 'Director of Operations', NULL, '', 'YES', 26, 'Small medical practice with 24 employees fits industry and size criteria, but lacks key signals like named EHR, decision-maker contact, technology stack, and pain indicators.', 'Associates of Internal Medicine is a primary care practice in Delray Beach, FL focused on comprehensive adult healthcare including prevention, diagnosis, and treatment. With 24 employees, this appears to be a mid-sized practice serving adult patients with preventative care needs.', 'mid-size', 'medium', '', '', '', 'Champion', 'high', 'With 24 staff managing comprehensive adult care in Delray Beach, your eligibility verification workload likely creates daily bottlenecks before patient visits.', 'billing staff overload', 'eligibility verification bottlenecks', 'Most practices with 20+ staff spend 2-3 hours daily verifying patient eligibility before appointments. The calls, holds, and portal logins create a morning rush that pushes back schedules. When verification takes longer than expected, front desk staff either delay patients or risk denials later. This daily bottleneck affects the entire flow of comprehensive adult care visits.', 'why calyxr built eligibility automation', 'That eligibility verification challenge is exactly why Calyxr exists. Our platform handles real-time eligibility checks automatically, eliminating the morning verification rush for practices like yours. One internal medicine group in Florida cut their daily eligibility work from 3 hours to 15 minutes. The front desk team now focuses on patient care instead of insurance phone trees.', 'Three hours of eligibility verification daily costs about $45,000 annually in staff time at current rates. Calyxr typically pays for itself within 60 days, with no long contracts required. Most practices go live within a week. Would it help to see how the eligibility automation would work specifically for comprehensive adult care workflows?', 'Hi there, noticed Associates of Internal Medicine has 24 staff managing comprehensive care. Most practices that size face daily eligibility verification bottlenecks that push back schedules. Mind if I connect to share how similar groups solved this?', '3 hours daily adds up quickly', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue) + CSV (org data) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (http://www.drwiddows.com) + CSV (org data) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '24', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue) + CSV (org data) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (http://www.drwiddows.com) + CSV (org data) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', NULL, NULL, 'Agent 2 Research Summary + Inferred Persona + CSV (org data) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 3 Personalisation Insight + Persona Pain Angle + CSV + CSV (org data) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'Medical Practice', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'P1', 'operational and billing inefficiency', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(312, 37, '2026-03-24 07:58:31', 'Associates of Internal Medicine', 'http://www.drwiddows.com', NULL, 'Director of Operations', NULL, '', 'YES', 22, 'Small internal medicine practice with 24 employees fits basic firmographic criteria but lacks key signals like named EHR, decision-maker contact, geographic location, and pain indicators to drive higher score.', 'Associates of Internal Medicine is a primary care practice in Delray Beach, FL led by Dr. Joanna Widdows, focusing on comprehensive adult healthcare from prevention to treatment. With 24 employees, this appears to be a mid-sized practice serving the adult population in South Florida.', 'mid-size', 'medium', '', '', '', 'Champion', 'high', 'With 24 staff members handling comprehensive adult care in Delray Beach, your billing team likely spends hours daily on insurance eligibility verification.', 'billing staff overload', '24 staff, endless verification calls', 'Most internal medicine practices with 20+ staff end up with billing teams spending 3-4 hours daily just on insurance eligibility verification. The calls pile up, patients get delayed, and your team burns out on hold music. It\'s become the hidden time sink that nobody talks about but everyone feels.', 'why I\'m writing about verification', 'I\'m reaching out because Calyxr eliminates the manual insurance verification grind for internal medicine practices. Instead of your billing team making dozens of calls daily, our platform pulls eligibility data directly from payers in real-time. One practice in Tampa cut their verification time from 4 hours to 20 minutes daily.', 'If your billing team spends 4 hours daily on verification calls, that\'s roughly $52,000 in annual labor costs just for eligibility checks. Most practices see their verification time drop 85% within the first week of going live, no long implementation needed. Worth a quick look at how this would work for Associates of Internal Medicine?', 'Noticed Associates of Internal Medicine has grown to 24 staff. Most practices that size end up with billing teams spending hours daily on insurance verification calls. Worth a quick conversation about how some practices are cutting that time by 85%?', '4 hours daily = $52k annually', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue) + CSV (org data) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (http://www.drwiddows.com) + CSV (org data) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '24', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue) + CSV (org data) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (http://www.drwiddows.com) + CSV (org data) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', NULL, NULL, 'Agent 2 Research Summary + Inferred Persona + CSV (org data) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 3 Personalisation Insight + Persona Pain Angle + CSV + CSV (org data) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'Medical Practice', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'P1', 'operational and billing inefficiency', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(313, 38, '2026-03-24 08:02:36', 'Associates of Internal Medicine', 'http://www.drwiddows.com', NULL, 'Director of Operations', NULL, '', 'YES', 14, 'Medical practice with 24 employees fits industry criteria but lacks critical data points including contact persona, geographic location, and technology stack to score higher.', 'Associates of Internal Medicine is a primary care practice in Delray Beach, FL, led by Dr. Joanna Widdows, focusing on comprehensive adult healthcare from prevention to treatment. With 24 employees, this appears to be a mid-sized primary care practice serving the adult population in South Florida.', 'mid-size', 'medium', '', '', '', 'Champion', 'high', 'Running 24 staff members in South Florida primary care, your eligibility verification workload must be crushing with snowbird insurance changes.', 'eligibility verification staff overload during seasonal population shifts', 'snowbird season hits different', 'Most South Florida primary care practices see their eligibility verification workload triple during snowbird season. Patients switching from summer plans to winter coverage, temporary address changes, and out-of-state insurance creates a verification nightmare. With 24 staff members already stretched thin, the insurance chaos from October through April can crush operational efficiency.', 'why calyxr built this', 'That snowbird verification chaos is exactly why we built Calyxr for practices like Associates of Internal Medicine. Our platform handles real-time eligibility checks and automates the insurance verification process, even when patients bounce between seasonal coverage. One Florida practice cut their verification time by 78% and eliminated claim denials from coverage gaps.', 'Each denied claim from missed coverage changes costs about $25 to rework, plus staff time. For a 24-person practice, that adds up to thousands monthly during snowbird season. Calyxr goes live in days, no long contracts. Would it help to see how this looks for a practice your size during peak season?', 'Noticed Associates of Internal Medicine operates in South Florida with 24 staff. The snowbird insurance verification chaos must be intense right now. Built something specifically for this problem, curious if you\'re seeing the usual seasonal surge in coverage mix-ups?', 'the real cost here', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue) + CSV (org data) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (http://www.drwiddows.com) + CSV (org data) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '24', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue) + CSV (org data) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (http://www.drwiddows.com) + CSV (org data) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', NULL, NULL, 'Agent 2 Research Summary + Inferred Persona + CSV (org data) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 3 Personalisation Insight + Persona Pain Angle + CSV + CSV (org data) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'Medical Practice', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'P1', 'operational and billing inefficiency', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(314, 39, '2026-03-24 08:06:35', 'Associates of Internal Medicine', 'http://www.drwiddows.com', NULL, 'Director of Operations', NULL, '', 'YES', 14, 'Internal medicine practice with 24 employees fits core healthcare industry but lacks key signals like named EHR, decision-maker contact, technology pain points, and geographic/revenue data to drive higher qualification.', 'Associates of Internal Medicine is a primary care practice led by Dr. Joanna Widdows in Delray Beach, FL, providing comprehensive adult healthcare services including prevention, diagnosis, and treatment. With 24 employees, this appears to be a mid-size practice focused on compassionate, timely patient care.', 'mid-size', 'medium', '', '', '', 'Champion', 'high', 'With 24 staff members handling Delray Beach\'s aging population, your eligibility verification workload likely consumes hours daily across multiple insurance plans.', 'billing staff overload', 'eligibility checks eating hours', 'Most internal medicine practices with 24+ staff spend 3-4 hours daily on eligibility verification calls. Between Medicare Advantage plans, commercial insurance changes, and prior auth requirements, front desk teams lose half their productive time navigating phone trees and insurance portals. The Delray Beach market\'s aging demographics make this even more complex, with patients frequently switching between Medicare plans mid-year.', 'why calyxr built verification tools', 'This eligibility verification bottleneck is exactly why we built Calyxr for practices like Associates of Internal Medicine. Our platform verifies patient eligibility in real-time before appointments, eliminating those daily phone calls and portal logins your team currently manages. One Florida internal medicine group reduced their verification time from 4 hours to 20 minutes daily using our system.', 'At $25 per hour in staff time, those 4 daily verification hours cost roughly $26,000 annually in lost productivity. Calyxr practices typically see verification time drop 85% within the first week, with no long-term contracts required. Would a 10-minute conversation about your current eligibility process make sense?', 'Noticed Associates handles Delray Beach\'s complex Medicare population. Most practices your size lose 3-4 hours daily on eligibility calls. Calyxr cuts that to minutes. Worth a brief conversation about your verification process?', 'quick eligibility verification audit', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue) + CSV (org data) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (http://www.drwiddows.com) + CSV (org data) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '24', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue) + CSV (org data) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (http://www.drwiddows.com) + CSV (org data) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', NULL, NULL, 'Agent 2 Research Summary + Inferred Persona + CSV (org data) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 3 Personalisation Insight + Persona Pain Angle + CSV + CSV (org data) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'Medical Practice', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'P1', 'operational and billing inefficiency', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(315, 40, '2026-03-24 08:16:04', 'Associates of Internal Medicine', 'http://www.drwiddows.com', NULL, 'Office Manager', NULL, '', 'YES', 14, 'Small internal medicine practice with 24 employees fits healthcare industry requirement, but lacks geographic, revenue, persona, and technology signals needed for strong qualification.', 'Associates of Internal Medicine is a small primary care practice in Delray Beach, FL led by Dr. Joanna Widdows, serving adult patients with comprehensive preventative health care. With 24 employees, they emphasize compassionate, timely patient care but likely face typical small practice challenges around appointment scheduling and patient communication.', 'small', 'medium', 'Manual phone-based appointment scheduling creates front desk bottlenecks and patient access friction for this 24-person primary care practice.', 'phone-only scheduling, no patient portal visible, primary care high-volume appointments, Medicare patient base likely, manual appointment coordination', 'medium', 'Champion', 'high', 'With 24 staff handling Delray Beach\'s aging population, your front desk is probably drowning in appointment calls during peak hours.', 'appointment scheduling bottleneck', 'busy signals during peak hours', 'Most internal medicine practices with 20+ staff face the same bottleneck. Peak appointment hours create a perfect storm where multiple phone lines ring simultaneously while staff juggle existing patients. The result? Busy signals that send frustrated patients straight to urgent care or competitors down the street. Serving Delray Beach\'s aging population makes this even more challenging since appointment volume tends to spike predictably.', 're: busy signals during peak hours', 'I\'m reaching out because Calyxr helps practices like Associates of Internal Medicine eliminate busy signals without hiring more front desk staff. Our system handles appointment scheduling intelligently, routing calls based on real-time staff availability and appointment types. One similar Florida practice with 22 employees reduced busy signals by 89% in their first month. The difference was immediate and measurable.', 'Every busy signal costs roughly $200 in lost revenue when patients book elsewhere. With typical internal medicine practices experiencing 15-20 busy signals daily, that\'s $3,000-4,000 monthly walking out the door. Calyxr typically pays for itself within 60 days, no long contracts required. Would it help to see exactly how this would work with your current call volume?', 'Hi there! I noticed Associates of Internal Medicine serves Delray Beach\'s busy market. Many similar practices struggle with appointment call overload during peak hours. Worth exploring how others are solving this without adding staff?', '89% fewer busy signals', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue) + CSV (org data) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (http://www.drwiddows.com) + CSV (org data) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '24', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue) + CSV (org data) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (http://www.drwiddows.com) + CSV (org data) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', NULL, NULL, 'Agent 2 Research Summary + Inferred Persona + CSV (org data) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 3 Personalisation Insight + Persona Pain Angle + CSV + CSV (org data) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'Medical Practice', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'P1', 'drowning in appointment calls while patients get busy signals', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(316, 40, '2026-03-24 08:16:22', 'Associates of Internal Medicine', 'http://www.drwiddows.com', NULL, 'Practice Administrator', NULL, '', 'YES', 14, 'Small internal medicine practice with 24 employees fits healthcare industry requirement, but lacks geographic, revenue, persona, and technology signals needed for strong qualification.', 'Associates of Internal Medicine is a small primary care practice in Delray Beach, FL led by Dr. Joanna Widdows, serving adult patients with comprehensive preventative health care. With 24 employees, they emphasize compassionate, timely patient care but likely face typical small practice challenges around appointment scheduling and patient communication.', 'small', 'medium', 'Manual phone-based appointment scheduling creates front desk bottlenecks and patient access friction for this 24-person primary care practice.', 'phone-only scheduling, no patient portal visible, primary care high-volume appointments, Medicare patient base likely, manual appointment coordination', 'medium', 'Influencer', 'medium', 'Managing appointment coordination across 24 staff members without automated scheduling workflows must create daily bottlenecks for your internal medicine patient volume.', 'staff coordination inefficiency', '24 staff scheduling chaos', 'Most internal medicine practices with 24+ staff members face the same scheduling nightmare. Manual coordination between that many team members creates constant bottlenecks, especially when patient volume fluctuates. The ripple effect hits everything from appointment availability to staff productivity. It\'s one of those problems that gets worse as the practice grows, not better.', 'why calyxr exists', 'The scheduling chaos at larger practices is exactly why we built Calyxr. Instead of manual coordination across your 24 staff members, everything flows through one intelligent scheduling system. Associates of Cardiology reduced their scheduling conflicts by 78% in the first month. When appointment coordinat