(327, 44, '2026-03-24 09:56:38', 'Associates of Internal Medicine', 'http://www.drwiddows.com', NULL, 'Billing Manager', NULL, '', 'YES', 22, 'Small medical practice with 24 employees fits industry criteria but lacks all key signals - no persona data, technology stack, pain indicators, or geographic information to drive higher scoring.', 'Associates of Internal Medicine is a primary care practice in Delray Beach, FL led by Dr. Joanna Widdows, serving adult patients with comprehensive preventative healthcare services. With 24 employees, this mid-size practice focuses on timely, compassionate patient care but likely faces typical primary care challenges with scheduling, patient communication, and insurance processing.', 'mid-size', 'medium', 'High call volume for appointment scheduling with only phone-based booking creates front desk bottlenecks and missed appointment opportunities.', 'phone-only scheduling, primary care volume, no automation mentioned, 24 employees managing full patient lifecycle', 'medium', 'Influencer', 'medium', 'With 24 staff members handling Delray Beach\'s aging population, your billing team is probably drowning in Medicare Advantage prior auth requests.', 'billing staff overload', 'medicare advantage drowning you?', 'Most billing teams with aging patient populations are drowning right now. Medicare Advantage prior auth requests have tripled since 2022, but staffing hasn\'t kept pace. The result? Billing managers spending 60% of their day chasing authorizations instead of working denials. With 24 people already stretched thin in Delray Beach\'s Medicare-heavy market, every prior auth that takes 45 minutes instead of 5 minutes costs real money.', 'why calyxr built this', 'The Medicare Advantage nightmare is exactly why we built Calyxr. Our platform handles insurance verification and prior auth requests without adding headcount to your billing team. One practice in Tampa reduced their prior auth time from 45 minutes to under 8 minutes per request