(353, 56, '2026-03-24 11:20:59', 'Acclaimed Mobile Health', 'https://acclaimedmobile.com', '', 'Billing Manager', '', '', 'YES', 38, 'Small mobile health clinic with healthcare focus but very limited staff (7 employees) and no clear decision-maker identified. Mobile diagnostic model suggests potential for patient communication automation but size constraints limit fit.', 'Acclaimed Mobile Health operates a 38-foot mobile medical unit providing on-site preventative health and wellness services to employer organizations, focusing on annual physicals and comprehensive health screenings at worksites.', 'small', 'medium', 'Manual scheduling coordination across multiple employer client sites with limited staff managing complex logistics for mobile unit deployments', 'mobile health services, 7 employees, multi-site operations, employer health programs, scheduling complexity, small staff for operational scope', 'medium', 'Influencer', 'medium', 'Managing payment cycles with 7 staff across multiple employer contracts while your mobile unit rotates worksites creates receivables bottlenecks.', 'B2B payment collection complexity', 'mobile billing bottlenecks', 'Managing payment cycles across rotating mobile health units creates unique challenges most billing teams never face. When your 7-person team handles multiple employer contracts while units move between worksites, receivables naturally pile up. The constant coordination between field operations and billing cycles means payments get delayed, cash flow becomes unpredictable, and staff spend more time chasing down documentation than processing collections.', 'why we built calyxr', 'Mobile health operations like yours are exactly why we built Calyxr. Most healthcare billing platforms assume you\'re working from a fixed location with standard workflows. Calyxr connects your mobile operations directly to employer billing cycles, automatically syncing worksite visits with payment processing. One of our mobile health clients redu