(360, 57, '2026-03-24 11:32:31', 'Acclaimed Mobile Health', 'https://acclaimedmobile.com', '', 'CEO', '', '', 'NO', 0, 'Mobile medical RV service model is fundamentally misaligned with Calyxr\'s fixed-location practice automation platform designed for traditional medical offices with scheduling systems, patient access workflows, and stationary operations.', 'Acclaimed Mobile Health provides on-site preventative healthcare services to employer organizations using a 38-foot mobile medical unit, focusing on workplace wellness programs and annual physicals to reduce healthcare costs.', 'small', 'medium', 'Managing insurance eligibility verification and claims processing across multiple employer sites with varying insurance plans creates significant administrative complexity for mobile operations.', 'mobile operations, multiple employer sites, varying insurance plans, workplace wellness programs, preventative care billing complexity', 'high', 'Economic Buyer', 'medium', 'Running a 38-foot mobile unit across multiple employer sites means your scheduling coordinators are constantly juggling location logistics and employee availability windows.', 'scheduling complexity and coordination overhead', '38-foot mobile unit scheduling', 'Running mobile health units across employer sites creates a scheduling nightmare most people don\'t see. Coordinators spend hours each week playing phone tag between HR departments and employees, trying to align availability windows with travel logistics. The bigger the unit, the more complex it gets. One scheduling conflict can cascade into missed appointments, frustrated employees, and unhappy employer clients.', 'why calyxr built this', 'Mobile health providers like Acclaimed face unique scheduling challenges that standard booking systems can\'t handle. That\'s exactly why we built Calyxr, a healthcare operations platform designed for complex multi-site coordination. Our system automatically manages location logistics, employee availability, an