(367, 59, '2026-03-25 12:59:29', 'Aduddell Dentistry', 'https://aduddelldentistry.com', 'Scott Aduddell', 'General Dentist', 'scott@aduddelldentistry.com', '', 'YES', 52, 'Strong industry match for dental practice in high-value Texas geography, but contact is clinical staff influencer rather than decision-maker. Limited firmographic and technology signals available.', '', '', '', 'Limited practice information suggests potential front desk communication gaps and manual scheduling processes typical of smaller general dentistry practices', 'general dentistry practice, minimal online presence, likely small team structure, no visible patient communication platform', 'medium', 'Champion', 'high', 'Single-provider practice like Aduddell likely loses hygiene recall revenue when patients don\'t respond to basic phone-only outreach attempts.', 'hygiene recall drop-off revenue loss from single-touch communication method', 'hygiene patients going quiet', 'Scott, many general practices notice the same pattern with their hygiene schedule. Patients who were religious about their six-month cleanings suddenly go quiet. The front desk makes a few calls, leaves voicemails, maybe sends a postcard. Then those patients just fade into the recall gap. It\'s especially common in single-provider practices where the focus stays on chair time and treatment, but the hygiene revenue quietly walks out the door. Have you noticed this happening at Aduddell?', 'why i\'m following up', 'Scott, I\'m following up because of Calyxr. We help dental practices recover hygiene recall revenue that gets lost in manual outreach gaps. Instead of your front desk making calls and hoping patients call back, Calyxr reaches overdue hygiene patients through multiple channels automatically. One practice like yours saw no-shows dropped from 28% to under 12% in 90 days after implementing our recall system. Does this sound like something worth exploring for Aduddell?', 'Scott, quick math on what manual hygiene recall typically costs. If 100 overdue patients represent $15,000 in hygiene revenue, and manual phone calls only recover 30% of them, that\'s $10,500 sitting on the table every quarter. Over a year, that\'s $42,000 in hygiene revenue that never gets scheduled. Calyxr lives in under a week and works with your existing practice management system. Worth a five-minute conversation about how this would work at Aduddell?', 'Scott, noticed Aduddell is a single-provider practice. Most practices like yours lose hygiene recall revenue when patients don\'t respond to basic phone outreach. The revenue just sits there while overdue patients fade into the gap. Seeing this pattern at your practice too?', 'the recall revenue math', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://aduddelldentistry.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://aduddelldentistry.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'scott@aduddelldentistry.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/scott-aduddell-dds-42b7641a8', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'General Dentist',