(368, 59, '2026-03-25 13:00:19', 'Advanced DDS', 'https://advanceddds.com', 'Wendy Miller', 'Lead Dental Hygienist', 'wmiller@advanceddds.com', '', 'YES', 47, 'Strong industry match with dental practice in favorable NY market, but contact is clinical staff influencer rather than decision-maker, limiting immediate sales potential.', '', '', '', 'Limited practice information prevents specific pain identification, but general dental practices typically struggle with manual patient communication and front desk inefficiencies.', 'minimal practice profile data, general dental practice assumed', 'medium', 'Wrong Contact', 'low', 'Leading a hygiene team without automated recall systems likely means your practice loses 15-20% hygiene revenue to manual phone tag.', 'hygiene recall drop-off revenue loss due to manual outreach inefficiency', 'hygiene revenue sitting idle', 'Most dental practices have 15-20% of their hygiene patients sitting overdue for their next cleaning, but the manual outreach process means many never get contacted. Phone tag with busy patients often means these appointments never get scheduled. The hygiene schedule stays partially empty while revenue sits in the patient database. Many hygienists notice their chairs could be fuller if there was a reliable way to reach patients who are past due.', 'following up on recall gaps', 'The reason I\'m writing is Calyxr handles the entire recall outreach process, so overdue hygiene patients actually book their next appointment instead of falling through the cracks. We automatically reach patients through text, email, and calls until they respond or schedule. One practice saw their no-shows dropped from 28% to under 12% in 90 days. Would something like this help fill those empty hygiene slots at Advanced DDS?', 'Every month that recall outreach stays manual, Advanced DDS is likely missing 15-20% of potential hygiene revenue. That empty chair time compounds when patients drift to other practices or skip cleanings altogether. Calyxr works with your existing PMS and can be live in under a week. Would it make sense to see how this might work for your hygiene department\'s specific situation?', 'Most hygiene departments have 15-20% of patients sitting overdue with no systematic outreach process. The manual phone calls just don\'t reach busy patients effectively. Are you seeing similar recall gaps at Advanced DDS?', 'cost of empty chairs', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://advanceddds.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://advanceddds.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'wmiller@advanceddds.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/wendy-miller-78b297181', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Lead Dental Hygienist', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
