(369, 59, '2026-03-25 13:01:09', 'Advanced Dental Care of Richmond', 'https://richmondsmile.com', 'Thomas Han', 'Associate Dentist', 'dr.han@richmondsmile.com', '', 'YES', 31, 'Dental practice in US with Associate Dentist contact, but limited firmographic data and non-decision-maker contact reduces score significantly.', '', '', '', 'General dentistry practice likely struggles with manual patient communication, appointment reminders, and insurance verification workflows that burden their small front desk team', 'general dentistry practice, Richmond location suggests PPO-heavy patient mix, no visible automation tools detected, likely small team based on practice name', 'medium', 'Wrong Contact', 'low', 'Richmond\'s competitive general dentistry market means your front desk is likely juggling constant insurance verification calls when they could be scheduling more new patients.', 'front desk administrative burden limiting new patient acquisition capacity', 'insurance calls eating front desk time', 'Thomas, many general practices in Richmond are watching their front desk teams spend 3-4 hours daily on manual insurance verification calls. The competitive market means new patient slots are precious, but staff time gets eaten up checking eligibility by hand before every appointment. Meanwhile, scheduling opportunities slip through the cracks because the team is tied up on hold with insurance companies instead of answering incoming calls from potential patients.', 'the reason i\'m following up', 'Thomas, I\'m reaching out because Calyxr solves exactly what I mentioned yesterday about manual insurance verification. Instead of your front desk spending hours on hold with insurance companies, eligibility gets confirmed in 12 seconds before every appointment automatically. One Richmond practice told us their team reclaimed 15+ hours a week on verification calls alone, which they redirected to scheduling more new patients in your competitive market.', 'Thomas, staying with manual insurance verification is costing Richmond practices about $2,400 monthly in lost scheduling opportunities. While your front desk is on hold with Aetna, potential patients are calling competitors who can answer immediately. Calyxr works with your existing PMS and goes live in under a week. Would it make sense to see how this looks for your specific patient volume at Advanced Dental Care?', 'Thomas, noticed Richmond general practices are losing scheduling time to manual insurance verification calls. Your front desk probably spends hours daily on hold with carriers when they could be booking new patients. How much time would you estimate your team spends on eligibility checks weekly?', 'cost of manual verification', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://richmondsmile.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://richmondsmile.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'dr.han@richmondsmile.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/thomas-han-69429589', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Associate Dentist', '', '', 