0 annually in labor costs just for something that runs automatically.\n\nPlus every recall call they make is time not spent on patient experience when people walk through your door.\n\nCalyxr works with your existing PMS and goes live in under a week.\n\nWorth seeing what this looks like for Advanced Dental Care specifically?', 'Joe, noticed Advanced Dental Care\'s growth in Round Rock. Most expanding practices hit the same wall where front desk teams get buried in manual recall calls instead of focusing on patient experience. Seeing this at your practice too?', 'the hidden cost here', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://adcroundrock.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://adcroundrock.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'adcrr@mb2dental.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/joe-widdison-60506722', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Doctor of Dental Medicine', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(371, 59, '2026-03-25 13:02:51', 'Advanced Dental Care of Round Rock', 'https://adcroundrock.com', 'Yazmin Miranda', 'General Dentist', 'adcrr@mb2dental.com', '', 'YES', 38, 'Strong dental industry fit in Texas, but contact is clinical staff rather than decision-maker. Limited data prevents higher scoring on firmographic and technology signals.', '', '', '', 'General dental practice likely struggles with manual appointment reminders, insurance verification workflows, and front desk staff managing high call volume without automation', 'general dentistry practice, Round Rock location suggests family-oriented patient base, no visible automation tools detected, likely PPO-heavy insurance mix', 'medium', 'Wrong Contact', 'low', 'Round Rock\'s competitive dental market means missed appointment calls directly impact your schedule fill rate and production targets.', 'competitive market pressure on appointment conversion', 'front desk buried in calls', 'Yazmin,\n\nMost dental practices in Round Rock are seeing their front desk teams spend 3-4 hours daily just on appointment confirmations and reminder calls. That\'s half a workday your staff could be focusing on patient experience and treatment coordination instead of playing phone tag.\n\nWith Round Rock\'s competitive market, every missed call or delayed response gives patients a reason to look elsewhere.', 'why i\'m following up', 'Yazmin,\n\nI\'m following up because Calyxr handles all those confirmation calls and patient reminders automatically, so your front desk can focus on patients walking through the door instead of chasing down appointments.\n\nOne practice similar to yours saw their front desk teams reclaim 15+ hours a week on reminder calls alone, which they redirected to treatment plan conversations and patient care.\n\nWorth exploring for Advanced Dental Care?', 'Yazmin,\n\nIf your team spends even 3 hours daily on confirmation calls, that\'s roughly $45,000 in annual labor costs just for basic appointment management. Plus every missed call in Round Rock\'s market means potential patients finding other practices.\n\nCalyxr works with your existing PMS and requires no IT setup. Would you be open to seeing how this looks for a practice your size?', 'Hi Yazmin, noticed Advanced Dental Care is in Round Rock\'s competitive market. Most practices there are seeing front desk teams buried in confirmation calls instead of focusing on patient experience. How are you handling the appointment reminder workload currently?', 'cost of manual calling', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://adcroundrock.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://adcroundrock.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'adcrr@mb2dental.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/yazmin-miranda-dmd-520466ba', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'General Dentist', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(372, 59, '2026-03-25 13:03:42', 'Advanced Dental Care of Round Rock', 'https://adcroundrock.com', 'David Firmage', 'General Dentist', 'adcrr@mb2dental.com', '', 'YES', 42, 'Strong industry match (dental practice in Texas) but contact is clinical staff influencer rather than decision-maker. Missing employee/revenue data limits scoring potential.', '', '', '', 'General dental practice likely struggles with manual appointment reminders, recall outreach, and front desk staff handling high call volume without automation.', 'general dentistry practice, Round Rock location suggests family/community practice with high recall volume, no visible automation tools detected', 'medium', 'Wrong Contact', 'low', 'Round Rock\'s competitive dental market means missed hygiene recalls directly impact your patient retention against nearby practices.', 'hygiene recall drop-off revenue loss in competitive market', 'round rock recall rates', 'David, noticed something about dental practices in Round Rock. Most are sitting on 6-12 months of overdue hygiene patients with zero systematic outreach happening. Patients who came in religiously for years just... disappear from the schedule. The front desk knows they should call the recall list, but between answering phones and checking people in, those calls never happen consistently. Meanwhile, new practices keep opening on every corner.', 'why i\'m following up', 'The reason I\'m writing is Calyxr. We handle hygiene recall outreach automatically for dental practices, so those overdue patients actually book their next cleaning instead of just sitting in your software. One practice here in Texas saw their hygiene recall rate jump from 42% to 78% in four months, just by having consistent automated outreach instead of hoping the front desk finds time to make calls. Worth a conversation about what\'s possible at Advanced Dental Care?', 'Quick math on recall gaps. If you have 200 overdue hygiene patients at $180 average, that\'s $36,000 in revenue just sitting there. Every month you wait, more patients drift to competitors or forget about their dental health entirely. Calyxr works with your existing practice management system and goes live in under a week. No long-term contracts required. What does your current recall rate look like compared to where you\'d want it?', 'David, been looking at dental practices around Round Rock and noticed most are sitting on months of overdue hygiene patients with no systematic recall outreach. The front desk stays busy with phones, so those calls never happen consistently. How\'s your hygiene booking looking these days?', 'cost of waiting', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://adcroundrock.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://adcroundrock.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'adcrr@mb2dental.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/david-firmage-3599a826', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'General Dentist', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(373, 59, '2026-03-25 13:04:35', 'Advanced Endodontics of New York', 'https://ronganik.com', 'Ron Ganik', 'Owner & Endodontist', 'drganik@ronganik.com', '', 'YES', 32, 'Strong persona fit as owner-endodontist but limited by single-specialty focus, NY location outside priority geographic zone, and lack of firmographic data to confirm practice size and operations scale.', '', '', '', 'Endodontic specialty practice likely struggles with complex insurance pre-authorizations for root canals and retreatments, plus coordinating referral communication with general dentists.', 'endodontic specialty, New York market, complex procedures requiring pre-auth, referral-based practice model', 'high', 'Champion', 'high', 'Endodontic referrals typically need same-day insurance verification for emergency root canals, but manual VOB calls create treatment delays.', 'emergency endodontic treatment delays from manual insurance verification', 'insurance delays emergency cases', 'Ron,\n\nMany endodontic practices face the same challenge: emergency root canal patients arrive needing immediate treatment, but insurance verification takes 20-45 minutes on hold with carriers.\n\nMeanwhile the patient is in pain, your schedule backs up, and referring doctors wonder about the delay. Some practices are spending 2-3 hours daily just on pre-auth calls for retreatments and complex cases.\n\nThe referring dentist expects quick turnaround, especially for emergency cases, but manual VOB calls create bottlenecks right when patients need care most.', 'the reason i\'m following up', 'Ron,\n\nI\'m following up because Calyxr handles insurance verification for endodontic practices like yours.\n\nInstead of your team spending time on hold with carriers, our system confirms eligibility and pre-auth requirements in 12 seconds before every appointment. This includes complex endodontic procedures, retreatments, and emergency cases.\n\nOne endodontic group we work with went from 2+ hours daily on insurance calls to having verification completed automatically before patients even arrive.\n\nCurious if this kind of speed would help with your referral relationships?', 'Ron,\n\nStaying with manual insurance verification typically costs endodontic practices about $180 per day in staff time, plus the patient experience impact when emergency cases get delayed.\n\nOver a year, that\'s roughly $47,000 in labor costs just for insurance calls. Not counting the referring dentist frustration when cases take longer than expected.\n\nCalyxr works with your existing practice management system and requires no IT setup on your end.\n\nWorth exploring how this would work with your current referral workflow?', 'Ron, noticed Advanced Endodontics probably deals with same-day insurance verification for emergency root canals. Most endo practices spend hours daily on carrier hold times while patients wait in pain. Does this sound familiar with your referral cases?', 'cost of manual verification', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://ronganik.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://ronganik.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (compa