(374, 59, '2026-03-25 13:05:26', 'Advanced Oral Specialty Group', 'https://advancedoralspecialtygroup.com', 'Bryanna Jones', 'Dental Secretary', 'bjones@aosgdental.com', '', 'YES', 42, 'Strong dental industry match with \'Advanced Oral Specialty Group\' indicating oral surgery or specialty dental practice in Pennsylvania. Contact is front office staff (Dental Secretary) who influences but doesn\'t make final purchasing decisions.', '', '', '', 'Multi-specialty oral surgery practice likely struggles with complex insurance pre-verification for surgical procedures and coordinating patient communication across different treatment types.', 'oral surgery specialty, likely high-value procedures requiring pre-authorization, complex insurance verification needs', 'high', 'Wrong Contact', 'low', 'Multi-specialty oral surgery practices like yours typically burn 2-3 hours daily on surgical pre-auths and eligibility checks across different procedure codes.', 'surgical insurance pre-verification time burden across multiple specialties', 'surgical pre-auths taking forever', 'Multi-specialty oral surgery practices typically burn 2-3 hours daily on surgical pre-auths and eligibility checks across different procedure codes. Your team probably knows this frustration well, calling insurance companies to verify coverage for extractions, implants, bone grafts, and periodontal procedures. Each surgical case needs different authorization requirements, and carriers keep you on hold while appointment slots sit empty. The manual verification process gets even more complex when patients need multiple procedures or have secondary insurance.', 'why i\'m following up', 'The reason I\'m writing is Calyxr. We handle surgical pre-authorization and insurance eligibility for oral surgery practices like Advanced Oral Specialty Group. Instead of your team spending hours on hold with carriers, our system confirms insurance eligibility in 12 seconds before every appointment, regardless of procedure complexity. One multi-specialty practice saw their front desk team reclaim 15+ hours a week on reminder calls alone. Does this sound like something that could help your daily workflow?', 'Every hour your team spends on manual pre-auths is an hour not spent on patient care and scheduling optimization. At 2-3 hours daily, that\'s 10-15 hours weekly of staff time tied up in insurance verification instead of growing the practice. Surgical cases get delayed, patients reschedule, and revenue sits in limbo while you wait for carrier approvals. We work with your existing practice management system and go live in under a week. Would you be curious to see how this works for other oral surgery practices?', 'Multi-specialty oral surgery practices typically burn hours daily on surgical pre-auths across different procedure codes. Your team at Advanced Oral Specialty Group probably knows this pain well. Are you finding the manual verification process is eating up more time lately?', 'cost of manual verification', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://advancedoralspecialtygroup.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://advancedoralspecialtygroup.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'bjones@aosgdental.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/bryanna-jones', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Dental Secretary', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(375, 59, '2026-03-25 13:06:15', 'Aesthetic Dentistry of Georgetown', 'https://aestheticdentistrygt.com', 'Mark Duncan', 'Dentist', 'mark@adgtown.com', '', 'YES', 65, 'Aesthetic dentistry practice in Texas with clinical owner contact - strong geographic and industry fit, though limited operational intelligence available for deeper qualification.', '', '', '', 'High-end aesthetic dental practice likely struggles with complex treatment plan communication and follow-up for expensive procedures, plus insurance pre-verification for cosmetic vs covered work', 'aesthetic/cosmetic specialty, Georgetown location suggests affluent clientele, complex treatment planning communication needs, insurance coverage verification for cosmetic vs restorative work', 'medium', 'Economic Buyer', 'high', 'Georgetown aesthetic practice likely loses revenue when patients delay $5K+ veneers/crowns due to unclear insurance coverage communication.', 'treatment plan follow-up revenue leakage for high-value cosmetic procedures', 'aesthetic treatment follow-up gap', 'Many aesthetic practices see patients get excited about veneers or crown work during the consultation, then go radio silent for weeks. The treatment plan sits in the chart while patients try to figure out what insurance covers versus what they\'ll pay out of pocket. Most practices don\'t have a system to follow up on these high-value cases, so $8,000 veneer treatments just sit there collecting dust.', 'why i\'m following up', 'I\'m following up because of Calyxr. We help aesthetic practices like yours turn those stalled treatment plans into scheduled procedures through automated patient communication that handles both the insurance verification piece and the follow-up nurturing. One cosmetic practice in Dallas saw their case acceptance on treatments over $5,000 jump 40% once they stopped letting patients disappear after the consultation.', 'Every treatment plan sitting in your system represents real revenue walking out the door. If you have 20 unscheduled cosmetic cases averaging $6,000 each, that\'s $120,000 in potential production just sitting idle. Most aesthetic practices are losing 30-40% of their high-value consultations to follow-up gaps. The system works with your existing practice management software and lives in under a week. What\'s your current follow-up process for patients who don\'t schedule after big case presentations?', 'Georgetown aesthetic practices usually have great consultation close rates, but I\'m curious about what happens to those $5K+ treatment plans when patients leave to think about it. Do you have a systematic way to follow up on the bigger cosmetic cases?', 'what sitting plans cost you', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://aestheticdentistrygt.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://aestheticdentistrygt.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'mark@adgtown.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/mark-duncan-37a72113', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Dentist', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, N