(377, 60, '2026-03-25 13:13:28', '1385 Dental Studio', 'https://1385dentalstudio.com', 'Hala Mustafa', 'Owner-General Dentist', 'dr.m@1385dentalstudio.com', '', 'YES', 67, 'Strong persona fit with Owner-General Dentist in Texas dental practice, but limited technology and pain signals visible. Prime target for workflow automation given solo practitioner profile.', '', '', '', 'Small dental practice likely struggles with manual patient communication, appointment reminders, and front desk staff managing phone calls without automation', 'small practice size, likely limited front desk staff, no automation systems mentioned, general dentistry practice', 'medium', 'Champion / Economic Buyer', 'high', 'Owner-operated practices like yours typically lose 2-3 hours daily on appointment confirmations and insurance verifications that could go toward production.', 'owner time allocation inefficiency - clinical revenue vs administrative burden', 'production time vs confirmation calls', 'Most owner-operated dental practices face the same daily reality. Your front desk team spends 2-3 hours confirming appointments, verifying insurance, and fielding patient questions. Meanwhile, your clinical time gets interrupted for administrative decisions that pull you away from what generates revenue. The manual confirmation process means staff can\'t focus on the patient experience when people walk through the door. Many practices see this as just part of the business, but it doesn\'t have to be.', 'why i\'m following up', 'Following up because Calyxr handles all those confirmation calls and insurance verifications automatically, giving your team back those 2-3 hours daily to focus on patient care instead of phone work. One practice owner told us their front desk teams reclaim 15+ hours a week on reminder calls alone. Your clinical time stays protected, and patients get confirmed without your staff spending their day on the phone. The system handles the administrative burden so you can stay chairside where you belong.', 'Every hour your team spends on confirmation calls is an hour they can\'t spend on treatment coordination or patient experience. At $25 per hour, that\'s $750 weekly in labor costs just for appointment confirmations. Plus the opportunity cost of distracted chairside time when you\'re pulled into administrative decisions. Calyxr works with your existing practice management system and goes live in under a week. Would it make sense to see how this looks for your specific patient volume?', 'Most owner-dentists I talk to say their biggest frustration is losing clinical time to administrative interruptions. Between confirmation calls and insurance verifications, it\'s hard to stay chairside. How much time does your team spend on appointment confirmations daily?', 'cost of manual confirmations', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://1385dentalstudio.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://1385dentalstudio.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'dr.m@1385dentalstudio.com', '',