(390, 60, '2026-03-25 13:28:16', 'Advanced Oral Specialty Group', 'https://advancedoralspecialtygroup.com', 'Bryanna Jones', 'Dental Secretary', 'bjones@aosgdental.com', '', 'YES', 45, 'Strong dental industry match with Advanced Oral Specialty Group indicating oral surgery/specialty focus, but limited by Dental Secretary contact who is an influencer rather than decision-maker. Pennsylvania location provides good geographic fit.', '', '', '', 'Multi-specialty oral surgery group likely struggles with complex insurance verification across medical and dental benefits, requiring manual portal logins and staff coordination between specialties.', 'oral specialty group, multi-specialty practice, complex medical/dental insurance crossover, likely high-value procedures requiring pre-authorization', 'high', 'Gatekeeper', 'low', 'Multi-specialty oral surgery groups like yours typically burn 2+ hours daily on medical/dental benefit crossover verification across different specialties.', 'cross-specialty insurance verification burden and staff coordination overhead', 'medical dental crossover verification', 'Multi-specialty oral surgery groups face a unique verification challenge that single-specialty practices never deal with. When patients need procedures that cross medical and dental benefits, someone has to manually log into multiple portals, check coverage limits across different plan types, and coordinate between specialties to confirm what\'s covered where. Most practices I talk to say this process takes 2-3 hours daily just for the complex cases. The back-and-forth between medical and dental coverage creates gaps where procedures get delayed or patients show up thinking they\'re covered when they\'re not.', 'the reason i\'m following up', 'The reason I\'m writing is because of Calyxr. We specifically built our insurance verification system to handle the medical/dental crossover that oral surgery groups deal with every day. Instead of logging into separate portals and piecing together coverage manually, our system pulls both medical and dental eligibility in one automated check. Advanced Oral Specialty Group in Tampa saw their insurance eligibility confirmed in 12 seconds before every appointment, eliminating the daily portal hunting their front desk was doing across multiple specialties. Worth exploring for your team?', 'If your team is still doing medical/dental crossover verification manually, you\'re likely losing 10-15 hours weekly just on the complex cases. That\'s $400-600 in staff time, plus the revenue impact when coverage surprises delay procedures or create patient confusion. We can have your verification process running automatically within your existing workflow, no long-term contracts required. The system works alongside whatever PMS you\'re currently using without any IT setup. Would it make sense to see how this looks for a multi-specialty group like yours?', 'Multi-specialty oral surgery groups always seem to get stuck with the most complex insurance verification, especially when procedures cross medical and dental benefits. Does your team spend much time juggling between different portals to piece together coverage?', 'cost of manual verification', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://advancedoralspecialtygroup.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://advancedoralspecialtygroup.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'bjones@aosgdental.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/bryanna-jones', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Dental Secretary', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
