(391, 60, '2026-03-25 13:29:19', 'Aesthetic Dentistry of Georgetown', 'https://aestheticdentistrygt.com', 'Mark Duncan', 'Dentist', 'mark@adgtown.com', '', 'YES', 60, 'Strong industry fit with aesthetic dentistry practice in Texas, but contact is clinical staff rather than decision-maker. Aesthetic practices typically have higher-value patients making retention critical.', '', '', '', 'High-end aesthetic dental practice likely struggles with complex treatment plan follow-up, insurance pre-verification for cosmetic procedures, and maintaining premium patient communication standards that match their upscale brand.', 'aesthetic specialty indicates complex treatment plans, Georgetown location suggests affluent patient base expecting premium service, cosmetic procedures require extensive insurance verification and patient education', 'medium', 'Champion / Economic Buyer', 'high', 'Georgetown aesthetic practice likely loses cosmetic case revenue when complex veneers/implant treatment plans sit in limbo without systematic follow-up.', 'high-value treatment plan follow-up revenue leakage', 'veneer cases sitting idle', 'Mark, many aesthetic practices have treatment plans sitting in patient charts for months without follow-up. A patient comes in excited about veneers, gets the full workup, then life happens and they go quiet. Most practices rely on the front desk to manually track these cases, but with high-end treatments averaging $15K to $30K per case, even a few lost opportunities add up fast. The patients want the work done, they just need the right nudge at the right time.', 'why i\'m following up', 'Mark, I\'m writing because of what I mentioned yesterday about treatment plans going cold. Calyxr handles the systematic follow-up for unscheduled cosmetic cases so nothing falls through the cracks. One aesthetic practice we work with saw 70% of their dormant veneer and implant cases convert to scheduled treatment within 60 days of implementing automated touchpoints. The system knows when someone has an unscheduled crown or full mouth case and keeps them warm with the right message sequence. Worth exploring for Georgetown?', 'Mark, if Aesthetic Dentistry has even 10 unscheduled cosmetic cases sitting idle right now, that\'s potentially $200K in treatment plan revenue that could convert with proper follow-up. Most aesthetic practices lose 40% of their complex cases to patient procrastination, not price objection. Calyxr works with your existing practice management system and goes live in under a week with no IT setup required. Would you be curious to see how this plays out specifically for cosmetic treatment acceptance?', 'Mark, noticed Georgetown focuses on aesthetic cases. Most high-end practices have this challenge where complex veneer and implant treatment plans sit in charts for months without systematic follow-up. Does this ring true for your practice?', 'cost of waiting', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://aestheticdentistrygt.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://aestheticdentistrygt.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (p