(398, 60, '2026-03-25 13:36:11', 'Apex Dental Studio Inc', 'https://apexwarsaw.com', 'Leela Buddaraju', 'General Dentist', 'leela.buddaraju@apexwarsaw.com', '', 'YES', 18, 'Strong industry match with Apex Dental Studio indicating dental practice, but contact is General Dentist (influencer role, not decision-maker). Missing critical data on geography, size, and decision-maker access limits qualification potential.', '', '', '', 'General dental practice likely struggling with manual patient communication, appointment scheduling, and basic front desk workflow automation needs.', 'general dentistry practice, limited company information available, likely small practice size, no visible technology stack', 'medium', 'Wrong Contact', 'low', 'With Warsaw\'s seasonal population shifts, your front desk is probably fielding more scheduling calls than they can handle efficiently.', 'seasonal volume spikes overwhelming manual scheduling systems', 'warsaw scheduling chaos', 'Most dental practices in areas with seasonal population shifts see the same pattern. Summer hits and suddenly your front desk is drowning in scheduling calls, confirmations, and reschedules. What used to be manageable patient volume becomes a full-time job just keeping appointments straight. Your team spends more time on the phone than they do helping patients at the front desk. The seasonal rush makes it impossible to give each caller the attention they deserve.', 'why i\'m following up', 'The reason I\'m writing is Calyxr. We handle all those confirmation calls, reschedule requests, and appointment reminders automatically, so your front desk can focus on patients who actually show up. One practice similar to yours saw their front desk teams reclaim 15+ hours a week on reminder calls alone. Instead of playing phone tag during your busy season, patients get confirmed through text and voice without tying up your staff.', 'Every hour your front desk spends on confirmation calls is an hour they\'re not helping patients, processing payments, or handling treatment questions. During seasonal rushes, that\'s easily 20+ hours weekly of premium staff time on basic scheduling tasks. Calyxr works with your existing PMS and can be live in under a week. Would it help to see exactly how much front desk time you could reclaim during your next busy period?', 'Most dental practices in Warsaw probably see the same thing during busy seasons - front desk teams drowning in confirmation calls instead of helping patients. How much time does your team spend on scheduling calls daily?', 'cost of manual scheduling', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://apexwarsaw.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://apexwarsaw.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'leela.buddaraju@apexwarsaw.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/leela-buddaraju-000aa0347', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'General Dentist', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(399, 60, '2026-03-25 13:37:12', 'AQUIA DENTAL CARE', 'https://aquiadentalcare.com', 'Norma Gutierrez', 'General Dentist', 'james@aquiadentalcare.com', '', 'YES', 40, 'Solid dental industry match with US location, but General Dentist is an influencer rather than decision-maker, and missing key firmographic data limits qualification confidence.', '', '', '', 'Small dental practice likely struggling with manual patient communication, missed appointment reminders, and front desk staff handling all scheduling and recall outreach manually.', 'general dental practice, likely small team, no visible automated communication system, manual recall processes', 'medium', 'Wrong Contact', 'low', 'Running a solo practice in Stafford means your front desk is juggling phone calls, appointment reminders, and hygiene recalls manually.', 'solo practice operational burden - owner time diverted from clinical production', 'front desk juggling everything', 'Most solo practices in smaller markets like Stafford end up with their front desk team wearing too many hats. Between answering phones, checking patients in, and manually calling through recall lists, there\'s barely time for the actual patient experience. The hygiene recall process alone can eat up hours each week, and when someone calls in sick, those reminder calls just don\'t happen. It\'s the reality of running a tight operation, but it leaves revenue sitting in charts instead of on the schedule.', 'why i\'m following up', 'The reason I\'m writing is Calyxr handles all that manual outreach your front desk is drowning in. Instead of spending hours calling through hygiene recall lists and appointment reminders, the system reaches every patient automatically through text, email, and voice. One practice similar to yours saw their front desk teams reclaim 15+ hours a week on reminder calls alone. Your team gets to focus on patients walking through the door instead of chasing down the ones who should be scheduled.', 'Every week your front desk spends calling recall lists manually is probably costing you 8-12 hygiene appointments that never get scheduled. At $200+ per hygiene visit, that adds up fast over a year. Plus your team is burning out on repetitive tasks instead of creating great patient experiences. Calyxr works with your existing practice management system and goes live in under a week. Would it make sense to see how this looks for a practice your size?', 'Running a solo practice in Stafford, your front desk is probably juggling phone calls, appointment reminders, and recall lists manually. Most practices your size see their teams spending 15+ hours weekly on outreach that could be automated. How are you handling hygiene recalls currently?', 'what manual recalls cost', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://aquiadentalcare.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://aquiadentalcare.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'james@aquiadentalcare.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/norma-gutierrez-d-d-s-9368a949', '', '', '',