(401, 60, '2026-03-25 13:39:09', 'Ashar Dentistry', 'https://ashardentistry.com', 'Farkhanda Tirmizi', 'Dentist', 'azim@ashardentistry.com', '', 'YES', 35, 'Texas-based dental practice with clear industry match, but limited contact authority and missing operational signals. Contact is clinical staff rather than decision-maker.', '', '', '', 'Limited practice information makes it difficult to identify specific operational pain points, but as a general dentistry practice they likely struggle with manual appointment reminders and patient communication inefficiencies.', 'general dentistry practice name, minimal online presence or information available', 'medium', 'Champion', 'high', 'Running a solo practice means you\'re likely handling appointment confirmations manually while trying to focus on patient care.', 'solo practitioner clinical time being consumed by front desk tasks', 'appointment reminder reality check', 'Many solo practice dentists find themselves stuck between two competing priorities. You want to be fully present with the patient in your chair, but there\'s also that mental load of knowing your front desk team is manually calling through tomorrow\'s schedule. The confirmation calls that don\'t get made often turn into last-minute cancellations or no-shows. It\'s one of those operational tasks that directly impacts your clinical time, even when you\'re not the one making the calls.', 'the reason i\'m following up', 'I\'m writing because Calyxr handles those appointment confirmations automatically, so you can stay focused on patient care without worrying about tomorrow\'s schedule. Our system reaches every patient through text, voice, and email without any manual work from your team. One solo practice owner saw no-shows dropped from 28% to under 12% in 90 days once their confirmation process became fully automated. Worth exploring for Ashar Dentistry?', 'Every missed confirmation call typically costs a practice $200-400 in lost revenue when that appointment slot goes unfilled. For a solo practice seeing 20 patients daily, even a 15% no-show rate means losing $3,000+ monthly in preventable revenue. Calyxr works with your existing PMS and goes live in under a week. Would it make sense to see exactly how this would work with your current patient flow?', 'I noticed you\'re running Ashar Dentistry solo. Many dentist-owners mention feeling torn between patient care time and making sure appointment confirmations actually happen. What\'s your current approach to keeping tomorrow\'s schedule full?', 'cost of manual confirmations', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://ashardentistry.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://ashardentistry.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'azim@ashardentistry.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/farkhanda-tirmizi-44bb84387', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Dentist', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(402, 60, '2026-03-25 13:40:07', 'ASTORIA DENTAL GROUP', 'https://cosmeticdentistrynewyork.com', 'Pranvera Haxhi', 'Lead Dental Assistant', 'phaxhi@smiledr.com', '', 'YES', 47, 'Dental group in high-value NY market with clear industry match, but contact is clinical staff (influencer role) rather than decision-maker. Missing key data limits full qualification.', '', '', '', 'Limited information available, but as a dental group, likely faces challenges with patient communication automation and coordinating care across multiple providers without centralized systems.', 'Multi-provider group name suggests coordination complexity, lack of visible technology stack information, general dentistry group likely has recall management needs', 'medium', 'Wrong Contact', 'low', 'With multiple providers under one roof, your lead assistants are likely juggling appointment coordination across different doctors\' schedules and treatment timelines.', 'multi-provider scheduling complexity and care coordination burden on clinical staff', 'coordinating multiple doctor schedules', 'Most dental groups with multiple providers end up with lead assistants manually coordinating patient flow between different doctors\' schedules. When Dr. A finishes a crown prep, getting the patient back to Dr. B for the seat becomes a juggling act across treatment timelines. The bigger the group gets, the more these coordination gaps create scheduling conflicts and patient confusion about their next steps.', 'why i\'m following up', 'Following up because Calyxr handles multi-provider coordination automatically. Instead of you manually tracking which patients need to come back to which doctor and when, the system manages treatment sequences across all your providers. One dental group saw their front desk teams reclaim 15+ hours a week on reminder calls alone once they stopped manually coordinating between doctors. Does this type of provider-to-provider patient flow coordination sound familiar at Astoria Dental Group?', 'Every week spent manually coordinating patients between multiple providers means appointment slots going unfilled, treatment plans sitting incomplete, and your time pulled away from chairside patient care. Most dental groups lose 2-3 hours daily just on scheduling coordination between doctors. Calyxr works with your existing PMS and goes live in under a week. Would it be worth seeing how this handles provider coordination for a group like yours?', 'Lead assistants at multi-provider dental groups usually end up being the scheduling coordination hub between all the different doctors and treatment timelines. Does this patient flow coordination piece sound familiar at Astoria?', 'what manual coordination costs', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://cosmeticdentistrynewyork.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://cosmeticdentistrynewyork.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'phaxhi@smiledr.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/pranvera-haxhi-2043401b2', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Lead D