en two additional cases per month represents $360K in annual production. Calyxr works with your existing PMS and goes live in under a week. What does your current follow-up process look like for unscheduled comprehensive cases?', 'Most prosthodontic practices I talk to have comprehensive treatment plans sitting in charts for months without any follow-up system. Your clinical expertise deserves better patient communication support than manual tracking. How are you currently handling follow-up on complex cases?', 'cost of manual follow-up', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://dentalimplants-austintx.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://dentalimplants-austintx.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'drcarmona@smilesatx.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/ernesto-carmona-9b661556', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Prosthodontist', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(412, 60, '2026-03-25 13:50:21', 'Authentic Smiles', 'https://authenticsmiles.com', 'Jeannie Klepper', 'Dental Insurance Claims Specialists', 'jeannie@authenticsmiles.com', '', 'YES', 45, 'Texas-based dental practice with strong geography fit and dental industry match, but contact is mid-level operations staff rather than decision-maker. Insurance claims specialist role suggests billing pain points that Calyxr\'s 12-second VOB could address.', '', '', '', 'Limited practice information makes it difficult to pinpoint specific pain points, but the name suggests a general dentistry practice that likely faces standard patient communication and recall management challenges.', 'general dentistry practice name, no visible technology stack information, unknown staffing levels', 'medium', 'Influencer', 'medium', 'With a dedicated insurance claims specialist on staff, your VOB processes are likely more thorough than most practices but still time-intensive.', 'manual insurance verification bottleneck despite having dedicated staff', 'running eligibility all day', 'Most dental practices with dedicated insurance specialists end up in the same pattern. Hours spent manually running eligibility checks, calling carriers for updates, and cross-referencing benefits before each appointment. The thoroughness pays off in fewer claim denials, but it eats up entire days that could be spent on higher-value tasks. Even with experience, each verification still takes 8-12 minutes when you factor in hold times and system slowdowns.', 'why i\'m following up', 'The reason I\'m writing is Calyxr. We built something specifically for practices like Authentic Smiles where insurance verification is taken seriously but shouldn\'t consume your entire day. Instead of manual carrier calls, eligibility gets confirmed in 12 seconds before every appointment, automatically. One of our clients saw their insurance specialist reclaim 20+ hours per week from verification tasks alone. Does this sound like something worth exploring for your practice?', 'Running eligibility manually costs most practices 15-25 hours per week in staff time. At $20/hour, that\'s $15,600-$26,000 annually just in labor costs for something that can happen automatically. Plus the opportunity cost of what else that specialist could be handling during those hours. Calyxr works with your existing practice management system and goes live in under a week. Would you be open to seeing how this looks for Authentic Smiles specifically?', 'I noticed Authentic Smiles has a dedicated insurance specialist, which tells me eligibility verification is taken seriously there. Most practices with that setup still spend hours daily on manual carrier calls. Have you found a way around the time drain of running benefits before every appointment?', 'cost of manual verification', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://authenticsmiles.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://authenticsmiles.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'jeannie@authenticsmiles.com