(415, 60, '2026-03-25 13:53:16', 'Authentic Smiles', 'https://authenticsmiles.com', 'Makai Rosa', 'Registered Dental Hygienist', 'makai@authenticsmiles.com', '', 'YES', 45, 'Dental practice in strong Texas geography with hygienist contact, but limited decision-making authority and no technology or pain signals visible.', '', '', '', 'Without visible staff size or technology stack, this practice likely struggles with manual patient communication and recall management common to smaller dental practices.', 'generic practice name suggests smaller independent practice, no visible technology stack, likely manual processes', 'medium', 'Wrong Contact', 'low', 'Having a hygienist as the primary contact suggests you\'re handling recall scheduling manually — most practices lose 15-20% hygiene revenue this way.', 'hygiene recall drop-off revenue loss from manual scheduling processes', 'hygiene chairs sitting empty', 'Most dental practices see 15-20% of their hygiene patients fall through the cracks between 6-month cleanings. The manual recall process means some patients go 8, 10, even 12 months without scheduling. Meanwhile, hygiene chairs sit empty during what should be prime appointment slots. It\'s not anyone\'s fault, it\'s just how recall has always been handled in most practices.', 'the reason i\'m following up', 'I\'m reaching back out because Calyxr handles exactly what I mentioned yesterday about hygiene recall gaps. Instead of manually calling overdue patients, it automatically reaches every patient when they\'re due for their next cleaning. One practice we work with saw no-shows dropped from 28% to under 12% in 90 days, mostly because patients were getting consistent reminders they actually responded to. Worth a quick look?', 'Every hygiene chair that sits empty for an hour costs the practice $200-300 in lost production. If recall gaps are leaving 15-20% of your hygiene schedule unfilled, that\'s potentially $3,000-5,000 per month walking out the door. Calyxr works with your existing practice management system and goes live in under a week. What would filling those empty hygiene appointments mean for Authentic Smiles?', 'Most practices lose 15-20% of hygiene revenue because recall scheduling is still handled manually. Patients fall through the cracks between 6-month cleanings and chairs sit empty. Is this something you\'re seeing at Authentic Smiles?', 'what empty chairs cost', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://authenticsmiles.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://authenticsmiles.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'makai@authenticsmiles.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/makai-rosa-901189244', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Registered Dental Hygienist', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(416, 60, '2026-03-25 13:54:24', 'Avenue of the Arts Dental', 'https://avenueartsdental.com', 'Mark Hoang', 'Dentist', 'mark.hoang@avenueartsdental.com', '', 'YES', 47, 'Pennsylvania-based dental practice with clear industry match, but limited contact authority (clinical staff vs owner) and missing firmographic data reduces overall qualification score.', '', '', '', 'General dental practice likely struggles with manual appointment reminders, patient recall outreach, and front desk staff handling high call volume without automation.', 'general dentistry practice, no visible patient communication automation, likely phone-dependent workflow, manual recall management', 'medium', 'Wrong Contact', 'low', 'Arts district location likely sees higher patient turnover requiring more aggressive recall outreach than typical suburban practices.', 'urban patient retention and recall frequency challenges', 'recall revenue sitting idle', 'Mark, many dental practices in high-turnover areas like arts districts see a common pattern. Hygiene recall lists grow longer each month, but there\'s no systematic way to reach overdue patients beyond sporadic phone calls. The front desk gets pulled in ten directions, so recall outreach becomes whoever-has-time work. Meanwhile, thousands in hygiene revenue sits in the chart with patients who\'d book if someone just reached out consistently.', 'why i\'m writing today', 'Mark, following up because of Calyxr. We help dental practices turn their recall gap into booked appointments without adding work to the front desk. Our system reaches overdue patients through multiple touchpoints until they book. One practice similar to yours saw their hygiene recall gap close by 60% in the first quarter, adding $47K in previously idle revenue. The system runs completely in the background while your team focuses on patient care.', 'Mark, every month without systematic recall outreach, your practice likely loses $8-12K in hygiene revenue that\'s just sitting there. Patients forget, get busy, or find another dentist who reaches out first. In an arts district location with natural patient turnover, that loss compounds quickly. Calyxr works with your existing PMS, no IT setup required, and practices typically see results within two weeks.', 'Mark, noticed Avenue of the Arts is in a high-turnover area. Many practices there struggle with hygiene recall patients falling through the cracks while the front desk handles everything else manually. How much of your recall revenue would you estimate is just sitting idle in charts right now?', 'cost of waiting', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://avenueartsdental.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://avenueartsdental.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'mark.hoang@avenueartsdental.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/mark-hoang-33535847', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Dentist', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(417, 60, '2026-03-25 13:55:23', 'Avery Dental Group', 'https://averydentalgroup.com', 'Alex Leffler', 'Dental Assistiant', 'alex@averydentalgroup.com', '', 'YES', 25, 'Strong industry match with dental practice in Ohio, but contact is clinical staff (Dental Assistant) rather than decision-maker, limiting immediate sales potential.', '', '', '', 'General dental practice likely struggles with patient communication automation and missed appointment opportunities due to manual reminder processes.', 'general dental practice name, no visible employee count suggests small team, likely handles routine hygiene recall manually', 'medium', 'Wrong Contact', 'low', 'With a dental assistant handling outreach coordination, your front desk is likely burning hours on manual appointment confirmations and hygiene recalls.', 'front desk administrative burden and manual patient communication workload', 'reminder calls eating your day', 'Alex,\n\nMany dental practices have their assistants and front desk teams spending 2-3 hours daily just on confirmation calls and recall reminders. The manual process of calling every patient 48 hours before, then again day-of, plus chasing down overdue hygiene appointments means less time for actual patient care. Most practices don\'t realize how much productivity gets lost to these routine calls that could happen automatically.', 'why I\'m following up', 'Alex,\n\nI\'m reaching out because Calyxr handles all those confirmation and recall calls automatically, so your team can focus on chairside care instead of phone duty. We\'ve seen dental practices where front desk teams reclaim 15+ hours a week on reminder calls alone. The system reaches patients through text, email, and voice calls without any manual work from your staff.', 'Alex,\n\nSticking with manual confirmation calls means your team will keep losing 15+ hours weekly to routine outreach, which costs about $400 in staff time per week. That\'s over $20K annually just on reminder calls, not counting the appointments you miss because someone couldn\'t get through. Calyxr works with your existing system and lives in under a week. Worth exploring what those reclaimed hours could mean for patient experience at Avery Dental Group?', 'Alex, noticed most dental assistants end up handling confirmation calls on top of chairside duties. Does your team at Avery Dental Group find themselves stuck on reminder call duty too?', 'cost of manual reminders', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://averydentalgroup.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://averydentalgroup.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'alex@averydentalgroup.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/alex-leffler-4bba04318', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Dental Assistiant', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
