(420, 60, '2026-03-25 13:58:26', 'Balcones Family Dental', 'https://balconesfamilydental.com', 'Darlene Greene', 'Dental Receptionist', 'dgreene@balconesfamilydental.com', '', 'YES', 27, 'Dental practice in Texas with receptionist contact, but low persona fit and missing key data. Receptionist is influencer-only, not decision-maker.', '', '', '', 'Small family dental practice likely struggles with manual patient communication, missed calls, and no-show management without dedicated front desk automation.', 'family dental specialty, likely small team size, no automation visible, general dentistry recall needs', 'medium', 'Wrong Contact', 'low', 'With one receptionist handling all patient calls, Balcones is likely missing revenue from patients who hang up during busy periods or don\'t receive timely appointment confirmations.', 'single receptionist bottleneck causing missed calls and no-show revenue loss', 'busy phone lines lately', 'Darlene, noticed something happening at a lot of family dental practices lately. Patients are calling during procedures or when the front desk is tied up with insurance verification, and by the time someone can pick up, they\'ve already hung up. Some practices are seeing dozens of missed calls per week without realizing it. The tricky part is you never know which calls were new patients trying to schedule versus existing patients with urgent needs.', 'why i\'m following up', 'Darlene, following up because of Calyxr. We handle patient calls when your line is busy so no one gets a voicemail or busy signal. Every caller reaches someone within 8 seconds, even during procedures or lunch breaks. One family practice in Austin told us they went from missing 30+ calls weekly to zero missed calls, and it freed them up to focus on patients in the chair instead of constantly watching the phone.', 'Darlene, a family practice missing 30 calls weekly is potentially losing $15,000+ in monthly revenue from new patients who don\'t leave voicemails. The calls that do come through still interrupt patient care or insurance work. Calyxr works with your existing phone system, no IT setup required. Would it help if I showed you exactly how other family practices handle their call overflow?', 'Hi Darlene, been seeing family practices lose potential patients when calls come in during busy periods. As the person answering those calls, you probably know exactly what I mean. How many calls would you estimate go to voicemail during your busiest hours?', '30 calls per week', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://balconesfamilydental.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://balconesfamilydental.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'dgreene@balconesfamilydental.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/darlene-greene-591aa0188', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Dental Receptionist', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
