ts are overdue for their cleaning?', 'Tom,\n\nStaying with manual recall outreach typically costs practices $2,000-4,000 per month in missed hygiene revenue. Every overdue patient who doesn\'t get contacted is money walking out the door to a competitor.\n\nCalyxr works with your existing practice management system, no IT setup required. Most practices see recall appointments start filling within the first week.\n\nWould it make sense to see exactly how many recall patients Beacon Dentistry could recover in the next 30 days?', 'Tom, noticed many dental practices have thousands in hygiene revenue just sitting idle in their patient charts. Overdue recall patients with no systematic outreach while the front desk stays buried in daily calls. How are you currently handling patients who are overdue for cleanings?', 'cost of empty recall slots', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://beacondentistry.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://beacondentistry.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'tom@tomthe