(430, 63, '2026-03-26 10:11:58', '1385 Dental Studio', 'https://1385dentalstudio.com', 'Hala Mustafa', 'Owner-General Dentist', 'dr.m@1385dentalstudio.com', '', 'YES', 63, 'Strong dental industry match with clinical owner persona in Texas, but limited operational signals and missing firmographic data prevent higher scoring.', '1385 Dental Studio is a solo general dentistry practice in Aubrey, Texas, led by Dr. Mustafa, offering comprehensive family dental care including cosmetic treatments and implants. As a newly established practice serving multiple communities (Aubrey, Prosper, Denton), they likely face challenges with patient acquisition, appointment scheduling, and establishing efficient operational workflows.', 'small', 'medium', 'New practice struggling with patient acquisition and building efficient communication workflows to establish recall base while managing front desk operations with minimal staff', 'solo general dentistry practice, newly established, serving multiple communities, patient acquisition challenges, appointment scheduling issues, operational workflow establishment needs', 'medium', 'Champion', 'high', 'New Aubrey practice serving three communities likely spending significant chair time on recall scheduling instead of clinical production.', 'owner-operator time displacement from clinical to administrative tasks', 'new practices and recall gaps', 'Many new dental practices face the same challenge in their first two years. The patient base is growing, but recall scheduling becomes this manual process that pulls the owner back to the front desk constantly. You\'re spending chair time calling patients who are due for cleanings instead of focusing on clinical production. The recall gap widens because there\'s no systematic way to stay on top of who needs to come back when.', 'why i\'m following up', 'The reason I\'m writing is Calyxr. We help new practices like yours automate the entire recall process so you stay in the chair doing what you do best. Instead of manual outreach, your patients get reached automatically when they\'re due. One practice similar to yours saw their hygiene recall gap close by 40% in the first 60 days without adding front desk hours. Worth exploring how this might work for 1385 Dental Studio?', 'Every hour you spend on recall scheduling is an hour not generating clinical revenue. For a new practice, that\'s roughly $400-500 in lost production per hour spent on administrative tasks. Over a month, the opportunity cost adds up quickly. We can have you live in under a week with no IT setup required. Would it make sense to see exactly how this would work for your Aubrey location?', 'Noticed you\'re building something special with 1385 Dental Studio in Aubrey. New practices often struggle with recall scheduling pulling owners away from clinical time. Are you finding yourself spending chair hours on front desk tasks that could be automated?', 'cost of manual recall', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://1385dentalstudio.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://1385dentalstudio.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, 