(434, 63, '2026-03-26 10:16:52', 'ACE Endodontics', 'https://ezrootcanal.com', 'Mauricio Ceballos', 'Endodontist', 'ace@ezrootcanal.com', '', 'YES', 42, 'Strong industry match as ACE Endodontics is a dental specialty practice in Texas, but limited by contact being clinical staff rather than decision-maker. Missing employee and revenue data prevents higher scoring.', 'ACE Endodontics is a Houston-based specialty endodontic practice founded in 1996 by Dr. Mauricio Ceballos, with Dr. Jeffrey Adcock as a second provider. This referral-based practice focuses exclusively on root canal therapy and endodontic procedures.', 'small', 'medium', 'Referral-based specialty practice likely struggles with complex insurance pre-verification and authorization requirements for endodontic procedures across multiple referring offices', 'specialty endodontics practice, referral-based model, complex procedure coding, multi-provider practice, established since 1996 suggests potential legacy systems', 'high', 'Economic Buyer', 'high', 'Referral-based endodontic practice likely burns hours on pre-auth calls since referring offices rarely handle endo insurance verification complexity.', 'referral coordination insurance burden and pre-authorization complexity', 'pre-auth calls all day', 'Most endodontic practices spend 3-4 hours daily on pre-authorization calls. The referring office sends patients over, but they rarely verify coverage for specialty procedures like retreatments or apicos. So your front desk ends up calling insurance companies to confirm benefits, get prior auth numbers, and check annual maximums while patients wait in the chair. It\'s the hidden time drain that comes with referral-based practice.', 'why I\'m following up', 'The reason I\'m writing is Calyxr. We handle insurance eligibility and pre-authorization for endodontic procedures automatically, even when referring offices haven\'t done the legwork. One specialty group saw their front desk reclaim 15+ hours a week on reminder calls alone, but the bigger win was eliminating the pre-auth bottleneck that was delaying treatment starts. Does this sound familiar for your practice?', 'Every hour your team spends on pre-auth calls is an hour not spent on patient care or case coordination. At 3-4 hours daily, that\'s roughly $40,000 in lost productivity annually, plus the patient frustration when treatment gets delayed over insurance questions. Calyxr works with your existing practice management system and goes live in under a week. Worth exploring how this might work for ACE Endodontics?', 'Most endodontic practices burn hours daily on insurance pre-auth calls since referring offices rarely handle the specialty verification complexity. Your front desk probably knows this pain well. How are you handling pre-authorization workflow at ACE Endodontics?', 'cost of manual pre-auth', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://ezrootcanal.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://ezrootcanal.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'ace