e-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'http://www.linkedin.com/company/comprehensive-family-dental', '+1 361-573-7722', 'raineydds@victoriatxdentist.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/tim-rainey-dds-fagd-dabdsm-95484ab9', 'victoriatxdentist.com', 'medical practice', 'general dentistry & pediatric dentistry, pediatric dentistry, general dentistry, medical practices, medical practice, hospital & health care', 'For over 45 years we been dedicated to the oral health, and most importantly, the comfort of our patients. As a pillar in the Victoria healthcare community, our mission is to provide you and your family with the highest standards of dental care and service. From our friendly and compassionate staff, to emergency services, and understanding for those with dental anxieties, our goal is to provide quality dentistry to all of our friends and neighbors in Victoria, Texas.\nOur team strives for excelle', 'Victoria', '', '', 'General Dentist', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
