(441, 64, '2026-03-30 13:02:15', 'Core Dentistry', 'https://coredentistrytx.com', 'Daniel Kou', 'General Dentist', 'dkou@philadentist.com', '', 'YES', 33, 'Texas-based dental practice with strong geographic fit, but General Dentist contact is an influencer rather than decision-maker, limiting immediate sales potential.', 'Core Dentistry is a new private general dentistry practice in Frisco, TX, owned and operated by Dr. Daniel Kou and his wife. This is a third-generation dentist opening his first solo practice, positioning as a neighborhood family business with comprehensive general dentistry services.', 'small', 'medium', 'New solo practice needs automated patient communication and recall system to build patient base without overwhelming small staff', 'new practice startup, solo practitioner, family-owned operation, general dentistry, building patient base from scratch', 'medium', 'Champion', 'high', 'New solo practice in competitive Frisco market needs automated recall system to build patient loyalty without Dr. Kou handling admin calls.', 'solo practice owner productivity drain from manual patient outreach', 'building recall as solo practice', 'Daniel,\n\nMany solo practices in competitive markets like Frisco face the same challenge. New patients come in for cleanings, but without a systematic recall process, they quietly drift away to established practices down the street.\n\nThe front desk gets buried in manual outreach calls, and as the dentist, you end up fielding admin calls between patients. Meanwhile, your hygiene schedule stays half-empty because patients forget to book their six-month visits.\n\nIt\'s especially tough when you\'re competing against larger practices with full recall departments.', 'why i\'m following up', 'Daniel,\n\nI\'m following up because Calyxr handles exactly what solo practices struggle with, automated recall campaigns that keep your hygiene schedule full without your staff spending hours on the phone.\n\nOne solo practice owner in Dallas saw no-shows dropped from 28% to under 12% in 90 days after switching from manual reminder calls to automated campaigns.\n\nFor a new practice building its patient base, that kind of consistency makes the difference between surviving and thriving in a competitive market like Frisco.\n\nAre you currently handling patient recalls manually, or do you have some system in place?', 'Daniel,\n\nEmpty hygiene appointments cost solo practices roughly $400 per unfilled slot when you factor in overhead and lost production. Over a month, that adds up quickly for a practice still building its patient base.\n\nMost solo dentists stay stuck in manual recall mode because they think automated systems are complex to set up. Calyxr works with your existing PMS and goes live in under a week with no IT setup required.\n\nWould it help to see how other solo practices are filling their hygiene schedules without adding staff hours to manual outreach?', 'Hey Daniel, noticed Core Dentistry is relatively new to the Frisco market. Most solo practices struggle with keeping hygiene schedules full without overwhelming their small teams with manual recall calls. Are you finding that challenge as you build your patient base?', 'cost of empty hygiene chairs', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://coredentistrytx.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://coredentistrytx.com) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'dkou@philadentist.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/daniel-kou-99342464', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'General Dentist', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
