(448, 64, '2026-03-30 13:09:06', 'CS Family Dentistry', 'https://csdentistrybastrop.com', 'Darla Campbell', 'Dental Front Office', 'darla@csdentistrybastrop.com', '', 'YES', 52, 'Texas-based solo dental practice with only 3 employees indicates understaffed front office operations. Contact is front office staff who could be an entry point for workflow automation discussions.', 'CS Family Dentistry is a solo dentist practice in Bastrop, Texas with 3 employees serving general dentistry needs. The practice operates as a small family-focused dental office with minimal staff structure.', 'small', 'medium', '3-person team handling all patient communication, scheduling, and billing manually without automation, creating front desk overload and missed revenue opportunities', 'solo practice, 3 employees total, general dentistry, small family-focused office, minimal staff structure', 'high', 'Influencer', 'medium', 'With just 3 team members handling everything from scheduling to billing, your front desk is probably drowning in manual appointment confirmations and insurance verifications.', 'front desk overload at understaffed solo practice', '3 person teams drowning', 'Most 3-person dental front offices are handling appointment confirmations, insurance verifications, and follow-ups completely by hand. That means someone is on the phone for hours every day just trying to keep the schedule full, while billing questions and new patient calls pile up. The math doesn\'t work when every confirmation call takes 3 minutes and half the patients don\'t answer on the first try.', 'why I\'m following up', 'The reason I\'m writing is Calyxr. We handle all the appointment confirmations, insurance eligibility checks, and patient follow-ups automatically so your team can focus on patients walking through the door instead of being glued to the phone. One practice with a similar setup saw their front desk teams reclaim 15+ hours a week on reminder calls alone. Does this sound like something worth exploring for CS Family Dentistry?', 'A 3-person team spending 15+ hours weekly on manual confirmations means roughly $12,000 per year in labor costs just for basic appointment management. That doesn\'t count the revenue lost when no-shows happen because reminders didn\'t reach patients. Calyxr works with your existing practice management system and requires no IT setup. Would you be open to seeing exactly how this would work for your current workflow?', 'Hey Darla, noticed CS Family Dentistry runs with a tight 3-person team. Most offices that size are drowning in manual appointment confirmations and insurance checks while trying to handle everything else. How are you managing the phone volume these days?', 'what manual costs you', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://csdentistrybastrop.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CS Family Dentistry', '', '3', '', '', 'Texas', 'United States', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://csdentistrybastrop.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'http://www.linkedin.com/company/cs-family-dentistry', '+1 512-321-2188', 'darla@csdentistrybastrop.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in