(455, 64, '2026-03-30 13:16:03', 'Dallas Uptown Endodontics', 'https://dallasuptownendodontics.com', 'Amit Sethi', 'Endodontist', 'sethi@krish.com', '', 'YES', 49, 'Small endodontic specialty practice in high-value Texas market with clinical contact who could influence decision-making, but limited scale and non-decision-maker persona reduces immediate priority.', 'Dallas Uptown Endodontics is a 2-person specialty endodontic practice in Dallas, TX focused on root canal procedures, tooth pain management, and retreatment of failed root canals in the competitive Uptown Dallas market.', 'small', 'medium', '2-person endodontic practice likely missing referral follow-up calls and post-procedure check-ins due to manual communication processes overwhelming limited staff', '2-person team, specialty endodontics requiring referral coordination, post-procedure follow-up intensive, competitive Dallas market, root canal retreatment complexity', 'medium', 'Champion', 'high', 'Two-person endodontic practice handling complex retreatments likely missing critical referring dentist communication after procedures, impacting referral relationships.', 'referral relationship maintenance strain from manual post-procedure communication gaps', 'referring dentist relationships', 'Most endodontic practices with small teams find themselves in the same spot. Between root canals and retreatments, the referring dentist gets a quick procedure note, but the follow-up communication that strengthens those relationships often falls through the cracks. The referring doctors want to know how their patient is healing, any complications, or next steps for restoration. When that communication is manual and relies on a 2-person team already managing clinical work, referring dentists start to feel disconnected from their patients\' specialty care.', 'why i\'m following up', 'The reason I\'m writing is because of Calyxr. We help endodontic practices maintain strong referral relationships without adding manual work to your clinical team. Instead of your assistant making follow-up calls to referring dentists, Calyxr sends automatic updates on patient progress, complications, and restoration readiness. One endo practice in Austin saw their referral volume increase 35% within 6 months because referring dentists felt more connected to patient outcomes. Would this type of automated referring doctor communication be helpful for your practice?', 'When referring dentists don\'t hear back about patient progress, they start sending cases elsewhere. Each lost referral relationship can mean 15-20 fewer cases per year, which adds up to significant revenue impact for a specialty practice. The practices that stay on top of referring doctor communication consistently see more repeat referrals and stronger professional relationships. Calyxr works with your existing practice management system and requires no IT setup. Would it make sense to see how this would work specifically for Dallas Uptown Endodontics?', 'Most endodontic practices struggle with the same thing - staying connected with referring dentists after procedures without overwhelming the clinical team. In a 2-person practice, those follow-up calls to referring doctors often get pushed aside during busy clinical days. How do you currently handle post-procedure communication with your referring dentists?', 'what missing follow-ups cost', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://dallasuptownendodontics.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Dallas Uptown Endodontics', '', '2', '', '', 'Texas', 'United States', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://dallasuptownendodontics.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'http://www.linkedin.com/company/dallas-uptown-endodontics', '+1 214-826-2364', 'sethi@krish.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/amit-sethi-308689150', 'dallasuptownendodontics.com', 'medical practice', 'medical practices, hospital & health care', 'Dental specialist & endodontist in Dallas Uptown specializes in Root Canal, Tooth Pain & Retreating failed Root Canals in Uptown & Dallas TX 214-826-2364', 'Dallas', '', '', 'Endodontist', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(456, 64, '2026-03-30 13:17:09', 'Danner Dental', 'https://dannerdental.com', 'Deizaray McDole', 'Dental Receptionist/Dental Assistant', 'mcdoled@dannerdental.com', '', 'YES', 67, 'Strong dental practice fit with $11.3M revenue, 6 employees, and advanced service offerings including same-day procedures and multiple specialties. Contact is clinical staff (influencer level) but may be only available contact at this practice size.', 'Danner Dental is a comprehensive 30+ year established practice in Canton, OH offering advanced services including same-day implants, sleep apnea treatment, TMJ therapy, and cosmetic procedures. With 6 employees and $11.3M revenue, they serve patients from multiple surrounding areas with complex, high-value treatments.', 'small', 'high', 'High-revenue practice with complex procedures needs automated insurance verification and pre-authorization for implants, sleep apnea devices, and surgical treatments to avoid claim delays and patient financial surprises', 'high revenue with small team, complex procedures requiring pre-auth, surgical extractions, implants, sleep apnea treatment, TMJ therapy, cosmetic procedures, multi-area patient base', 'high', 'Influencer', 'low', 'With same-day implants and complex TMJ cases, your front desk is probably drowning in pre-auth calls and insurance eligibility checks before high-dollar procedures.', 'front desk administrative burden from complex procedure insurance verification', 'implant pre-auth nightmare', 'Most front desk teams at high-volume practices spend 2-3 hours daily on insurance eligibility checks and pre-authorization calls for complex cases. Same-day implants, TMJ treatments, and sleep apnea devices require multiple verification steps before patients even sit in the chair. The phone tag with insurance carriers alone can eat up half your morning, especially when you\'re trying to confirm coverage for $15,000+ procedures. Your surgeons are ready to work, but someone has to make sure the patient won\'t get hit with surprise denials.', 'why i\'m following up', 'The reason I\'m writing is Calyxr. We handle all the insurance verification and pre-authorization work for complex dental procedures automatically. Instead of your team spending hours on hold with carriers, our system confirms eligibility for implants, sleep devices, and surgical treatments before the patient arrives. One practice doing high-end reconstructive work saw insurance eligibility confirmed in 12 seconds before every appointment. Would this type of verification speed help with your complex cases?', 'Every hour your team spends on insurance calls for pre-auth is an hour not spent on patient care or scheduling. At your procedure volume, manual verification is probably costing 15-20 hours of front desk time weekly. That\'s before counting the revenue delays when approvals come back late or patients discover coverage gaps at treatment time. Calyxr works with your existing practice management system and requires no IT setup. What would getting those verification hours back mean for your daily workflow?', 'Noticed Danner Dental handles complex implants and TMJ cases. Most front desk teams at practices your size spend half their morning on insurance pre-auth calls for high-dollar procedures. How much time does your team spend on eligibility verification daily?', 'cost of manual checks', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://dannerdental.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Danner Dental', '11.3M', '6', '', '', 'Ohio', 'United States', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://dannerdental.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, em