(458, 64, '2026-03-30 13:19:02', 'David M Caldwell DDS', 'https://drdavidcaldwell.com', 'Jackson Harlan', 'Dental Assistant', 'jackson.harlan@drdavidcaldwell.com', '', 'YES', 48, 'Strong industry match for Texas-based dental practice with 5 employees, but contact is a dental assistant (influencer role, not decision-maker). Small practice size fits ICP parameters.', 'David M Caldwell DDS is a small general dentistry practice in Beaumont, Texas serving children, teens, and adults across multiple East Texas communities. The practice shows critical technology neglect with an expired website, indicating likely gaps in patient communication systems.', 'small', 'medium', 'Small 5-person practice with expired website likely struggling with manual patient communication and appointment reminders, leading to no-shows and recall drop-off', 'expired website, small 5-person team, general dentistry serving children/teens/adults, multi-location coverage area, technology neglect indicators', 'medium', 'Wrong Contact', 'low', '5-person practice with expired website likely missing 40+ hygiene recalls monthly due to outdated patient communication systems.', 'hygiene recall revenue leakage from technology neglect', '40 hygiene recalls sitting idle', 'Jackson, small practices with outdated websites often see the same pattern, 40+ hygiene recalls pile up each month because patients never get reminded. The front desk ends up making manual calls that rarely connect, or worse, the recalls just sit in the system collecting dust. Most practices don\'t realize how much revenue is sitting idle in overdue recalls until someone actually counts the chairs that could be filled.', 'why i\'m following up', 'Jackson, following up because Calyxr handles exactly what I mentioned yesterday about those overdue recalls. Instead of manual outreach, patients get reached automatically through text, email, and voice until they book. One practice with 6 team members went from 40+ overdue recalls to under 10 within 60 days, just by having consistent patient touchpoints that actually connect. The front desk barely touches recall scheduling anymore.', 'Jackson, 40 overdue hygiene recalls at $200 average is $8,000 in revenue sitting idle every month. That adds up to nearly $100K annually just from patients who want to come back but never get properly reminded. Calyxr works with your existing practice software and goes live in under a week, no IT setup required. Worth taking a look at what those empty recall slots are actually costing the practice?', 'Jackson, noticed your practice website needs updating and wondering if you\'re seeing the same recall drop-off pattern most small practices deal with. Are overdue hygiene appointments piling up without good patient outreach?', 'cost of empty chairs', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://drdavidcaldwell.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'David M Caldwell DDS', '', '5', '', '', 'Texas', 'United States', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://drdavidcaldwell.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'http://www.linkedin.com/company/david-m-caldwell-dds', '+1 409-923-1658', 'jackson.harlan@drdavidcaldwell.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/jackson-harlan-7966101a7', 'drdavidcaldwell.com', 'medical practice', 'medical practices, hospital & health care', 'David M. Caldwell, D.D.S. is your Beaumont, Port Niches, and Orange, TX dentist, providing quality dental care for children, teens, and adults. Call today.', 'Beaumont', '', '', 'Dental Assistant', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(459, 64, '2026-03-30 13:20:01', 'David Tillman DDS', 'https://tillmansmiles.com', 'Hollye Myers-Perry', 'Registered Dental Hygienist', 'hollye@tillmansmiles.com', '', 'YES', 58, 'Strong dental practice fit with good size and revenue in Texas, but contact is clinical staff (RDH) rather than decision-maker. Practice shows need for automation with personalized care focus.', 'David Tillman DDS is a comprehensive family dental practice in Fort Worth, Texas with 8 employees and $4.1M revenue. The practice offers general, cosmetic, and restorative services under one roof with sedation dentistry options, targeting families and anxious patients.', 'small', 'medium', '8-person team managing $4.1M revenue across comprehensive services likely overwhelmed with patient communication, recall outreach, and insurance verification without automation', 'high revenue per employee ($512K), comprehensive service mix, sedation dentistry requiring complex scheduling, family practice with high recall volume, no technology stack mentioned', 'high', 'Wrong Contact', 'low', '8-person team handling $4.1M across comprehensive plus sedation services means your hygienists are likely stuck making recall calls instead of seeing patients.', 'hygienist productivity loss from manual recall outreach burden', 'hygienists making recall calls', 'Many dental practices with comprehensive services find their hygienists spending chunks of the day making recall calls instead of seeing patients. When you\'re running $4M+ revenue with an 8-person team, that\'s a lot of clinical time going to phone work. The math gets painful quickly, especially when recall patients are sitting at home not knowing they\'re overdue. Seems like there should be a better way to handle this.', 'why i\'m following up', 'Following up because of Calyxr. We handle all the recall outreach automatically so your hygienists can stay chairside where they belong. One practice saw their hygiene team reclaim 15+ hours a week on reminder calls alone, which meant more patients in the chair and better revenue per hygienist. Figured this might make sense for a busy practice like yours with comprehensive services and sedation work.', 'Quick math: if one hygienist spends 2 hours daily on recall calls at $45/hour clinical rate, that\'s $23,400 in lost production annually. Multiply across your team and the numbers add up fast. Meanwhile, patients who don\'t get reached stay overdue and eventually find care elsewhere. We can get this live in under a week with no IT setup required. Worth exploring how this might work for your practice?', 'Noticed you\'re with David Tillman DDS, impressive operation with comprehensive services. I imagine with an 8-person team handling that volume, your hygienists probably get pulled into making recall calls pretty regularly. How much clinical time would you estimate gets spent on phone outreach weekly?', 'cost of phone time', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://tillmansmiles.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'David Tillman DDS', '4.1M', '8', '', '', 'Texas', 'United States', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://tillmansmiles.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude 