(460, 64, '2026-03-30 13:20:58', 'Dayton Dental Group', 'https://daytondentalgroup.com', 'Yuchun Zhang', 'Dentist', 'ddg@daytondentalgroup.com', '', 'YES', 68, 'Strong dental industry match with growth signals (founded 2019, 8 employees) and favorable Ohio location, but limited by clinical staff contact rather than owner/decision-maker persona.', 'Small general dentistry practice founded in 2019 in Dayton, OH with 8 employees, heavily focused on restorative services including dental implants, dentures, and Invisalign. Strong emphasis on insurance acceptance and affordability with multiple payment options.', 'small', 'high', '8-person practice handling high-volume restorative procedures needs insurance verification automation to prevent claim denials and reduce front desk administrative burden', 'small team (8 employees), founded 2019 (growing practice), restorative focus (implants/dentures = high-dollar claims), heavy insurance acceptance emphasis, multi-payment options complexity', 'high', 'Champion / Economic Buyer', 'high', 'With your focus on high-ticket restorative work like implants and dentures, each insurance eligibility miss costs you significantly more than typical cleanings.', 'restorative procedure revenue protection from insurance verification failures', 'insurance eligibility delays', 'Most restorative practices discover eligibility issues after the procedure is complete. The front desk checks benefits before scheduling, but insurance changes happen between booking and treatment. When a $4,000 implant case gets denied because the patient\'s coverage lapsed last month, someone has to make those calls to work out payment. The bigger the case value, the bigger the problem when eligibility wasn\'t confirmed day-of-service.', 'why i\'m writing', 'The reason I\'m following up is Calyxr. We help restorative practices verify insurance eligibility in real-time before every appointment, not just at scheduling. One implant practice saw insurance eligibility confirmed in 12 seconds before every appointment, which eliminated surprise denials on their high-ticket cases. Your 8-person team could focus on patient care instead of chasing down eligibility issues after procedures are complete.', 'Every surprise denial on a crown, bridge, or implant case costs your practice weeks in collections work plus the patient relationship strain. Manual verification means eligibility gaps slip through until it\'s too late. Practices typically lose 12-15% of restorative revenue to preventable eligibility issues. Calyxr works with your existing PMS and requires no IT setup. Would real-time eligibility verification before your high-ticket cases make sense for Dayton Dental Group?', 'Most restorative practices find out about insurance issues after completing expensive procedures. The manual verification process misses changes that happen between scheduling and treatment day. Are you seeing eligibility surprises on your implant and crown cases?', 'cost of manual verification', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://daytondentalgroup.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Dayton Dental Group', '', '8', '', '', 'Ohio', 'United States', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://daytondentalgroup.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation 