ontact, specialty) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'http://www.linkedin.com/company/dd-family-dentistry-of-carrollton', '+1 972-245-3395', 'durga@ddfamilydentistrytx.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/durga-devarakonda-97901575', 'ddfamilydentistrytx.com', 'medical practice', 'dentists, medical practice, hospital & health care', 'We practice preventive dentistry and dedicate considerable resources to patient education, thorough hygiene exams, and cleanings. Quality restorative dental treatments preserve and protect your oral health and potentially preclude the need for expensive procedures. We do understand that some cosmetic and general dental care procedures may be expensive — in such situations, we present the trade-offs between cost and effectiveness to equip the patient with the necessary background to make an educa', 'Carrollton', '', '', 'Family Dentist', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(462, 64, '2026-03-30 13:21:59', 'DDS Practice Success, LLC', 'https://ddspracticesuccessllc.com', 'Irina Falletta', 'Dental Practice Consultant/ Dental Broker', 'irina@ddspracticesuccessllc.com', '', 'Skipped', 0, 'ICP score 0 is below the threshold of 35. This is a dental consulting and brokerage firm, not an operating dental practice. The contact is a consultant/broker, not a practice decision-maker.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(463, 64, '2026-03-30 13:22:58', 'Defiance Dental Group', 'https://defiancedentalgroup.com', 'Tami Backhaus', 'Registered Dental Hygienist', 'tamibackhaus@defiancedentalgroup.com', '', 'YES', 67, 'Small dental practice in Ohio with $1.9M revenue hits firmographic sweet spot, but contact is clinical staff (hygienist) rather than decision-maker. 50+ year established practice suggests operational pain points that Calyxr can address.', 'Defiance Dental Group is a 50+ year established general dentistry practice in Defiance, OH with 8 employees serving families across all ages. They emphasize affordable care with flexible scheduling and financing options, indicating a price-conscious patient base likely heavy on insurance dependencies.', 'small', 'medium', 'Small 8-person team managing insurance-heavy patient base with manual eligibility verification and appointment reminders creating front desk bottleneck', '8 employees for $1.9M revenue, 50+ year established practice likely with legacy systems, emphasis on affordable care suggesting insurance-dependent patients, flexible scheduling indicating manual coordination burden', 'high', 'Wrong Contact', 'low', 'With 8 staff handling insurance-heavy patients over 50+ years, your front desk likely burns hours daily on manual eligibility calls before appointments.', 'front desk VOB burden at established insurance-dependent practice', 'insurance calls eating your day', 'Tami, most dental practices with heavy insurance loads find their front desk calling to verify benefits hours before every appointment. With 8 people managing that volume, someone\'s probably on hold with Anthem or Delta Dental while patients are waiting to be scheduled. The manual eligibility process becomes the bottleneck that slows everything else down.', 'why i\'m following up', 'Tami, the reason I\'m writing is Calyxr. We handle insurance eligibility verification automatically, so your front desk never has to call carriers again. Benefits get confirmed in 12 seconds before every appointment, with real-time updates sent directly to your PMS. One practice saw their team reclaim 15+ hours a week on reminder calls alone after switching from manual verification.', 'Tami, if your team spends even 2 hours daily on eligibility calls, that\'s 10 hours per week of clinical support time lost to phone holds. At $25/hour, you\'re looking at $13,000 annually just in staff time, not counting the appointment delays or patient frustration. Calyxr works with your existing PMS and goes live in under a week. Worth exploring how much time your team could get back?', 'Hi Tami, noticed Defiance Dental has been around 50+ years with a solid team. With that insurance-heavy patient base, your front desk probably spends hours daily calling carriers for eligibility verification. How much time does your team lose to those calls each week?', 'cost of those daily calls', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://defiancedentalgroup.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Defiance Dental Group', '1.9M', '8', '', '', 'Ohio', 'United States', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://defiancedentalgroup.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (clau