lists end up stalled in administrative limbo.', 'why i\'m following up', 'The reason I\'m writing is Calyxr. We handle the entire pre-authorization workflow for multi-specialty practices, coordinating insurance approvals across all treatment phases automatically. Your front desk stops playing middleman between departments. Insurance eligibility confirmed in 12 seconds before every appointment, whether it\'s initial consult with perio or final restoration placement. One practice with six specialists saw 70% reduction in manual front office tasks without adding headcount. Worth exploring for a seven-person practice like Dentiq?', 'Every day your front desk spends coordinating pre-auths manually costs you completed treatment cases. Complex cases like full-mouth restorations get delayed when insurance approvals don\'t align between specialists. Patients drop out when communication feels disjointed across departments. A typical multi-specialty practice loses $40K annually just from treatment plan coordination delays. We work with your existing systems, no long-term contracts required. Simple question, how many All-on-4 cases currently sit stalled waiting for insurance coordination to catch up?', 'Noticed Dentiq has seven specialists coordinating complex cases. Most practices your size struggle with pre-auth workflows between perio, oral surgery, and ortho departments. Does your front desk end up playing middleman on treatment plan approvals?', 'cost of manual coordination', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://dentiq.net) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Dentiq Comprehensive Dental Center', '', '7', '', '', 'Texas', 'United States', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https