(472, 64, '2026-03-30 13:30:17', 'Dent-Well: Onsite Dental Solutions', 'https://wellsmilescitywest.com', 'Blane Kingsmore', 'Entrepreneur', 'bkingsmore@dent-well.com', '', 'YES', 54, 'Dental industry match with Texas location and clinical owner persona, but lacks technology signals and specific pain indicators for higher scoring.', 'WellSmiles Dental is a boutique general dentistry practice located within CityWest Place office complex in Houston, Texas, serving corporate tenants and surrounding community for over a decade with PPO-heavy insurance acceptance.', 'small', 'medium', 'Manual insurance verification and PPO eligibility checks consuming significant front desk time with high volume of different insurance plans from corporate tenants', 'PPO-heavy insurance mix, corporate tenant patient base, onsite location serving office complex, boutique practice size likely means small staff handling high verification volume', 'high', 'Economic Buyer', 'high', 'Corporate tenant patient base means your front desk is juggling dozens of different PPO plans daily — that eligibility verification bottleneck before appointments.', 'front desk PPO verification burden from diverse corporate tenant insurance mix', 'corporate tenant insurance maze', 'Most onsite dental practices serving corporate tenants face the same challenge. Your front desk spends hours manually verifying eligibility across dozens of different PPO plans every day. Each corporate client brings their own insurance mix, and there\'s no way to predict which Aetna, Cigna, or United plan each patient carries until they\'re in your chair. The verification calls alone can consume half your front desk capacity, especially when you\'re dealing with out-of-state corporate employees who don\'t know their own plan details.', 'why i\'m following up', 'The reason I\'m writing is Calyxr. We solve the corporate tenant PPO verification bottleneck you\'re dealing with. Instead of your team making dozens of eligibility calls across 