 in phone work, confirmation calls, and manual insurance verification. One of our practices went from their front desk spending 6 hours daily on recalls and confirmations to under 30 minutes, with insurance eligibility confirmed in 12 seconds before every appointment. Curious how a practice generating your revenue manages patient communication with such a lean team?', 'Quick math: if one team member spends 4 hours daily on patient calls and VOBs, that\'s $50,000+ in annual labor costs just for tasks that can run automatically. Meanwhile, patients slip through recall cracks and appointments go unconfirmed because there simply aren\'t enough hours in the day. We work with your existing system, no long-term contracts, and practices typically see results in the first week. Would it make sense to see how this applies to a 3-person team managing $6M?', 'Saw Dr. Della Bella\'s practice generates $6M with just 3 team members. That\'s impressive but probably means someone is spending way too much time on confirmation calls and insurance checks instead of chairside work. How does your team handle all the patient communication?', 'cost of staying manual', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://cincinnatidentalexcellence.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Dr. Alexander M. Della Bella', '6.0M', '3', '', '', 'Ohio', 'United States', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://cincinnatidentalexcellence.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude