(479, 64, '2026-03-30 13:37:13', 'Dr. Fred G. Blum & Associates (Rochester/ Brighton Dentist)', 'https://drfredblum.com', 'Caprice Dakwar', 'Dentist', 'caprice@drfredblum.com', '', 'YES', 47, 'Small 2-person family dental practice in Rochester, NY with clinical owner as contact. Strong industry match and geographic fit, but limited by small size and single-dentist operation.', 'Dr. Fred G. Blum & Associates is a boutique family dental practice serving Rochester/Brighton NY for 30+ years with a unique concierge model - they schedule only one patient at a time and position themselves as \'compassionate dentists\'.', 'small', 'medium', '2-person boutique practice with one-patient-at-a-time scheduling model likely struggles with manual appointment management, missed calls during appointments, and no automated patient communication system', '2 employees total, boutique practice model, one-patient-at-a-time scheduling, 30+ years established (likely legacy systems), family dentistry with implants/cosmetics mix, no mention of automated communication systems', 'medium', 'Champion', 'high', 'Two-doctor boutique with one-patient-at-a-time scheduling means every missed call during appointments is lost revenue.', 'missed calls during appointments at boutique practice with premium positioning', 'calls during procedures', 'Boutique practices face an impossible choice every time the phone rings during patient care. Answer and interrupt treatment, or let it ring and hope they call back. Most dental practices with one-patient-at-a-time scheduling lose 30-40% of inbound calls this way. The patient in the chair gets your full attention, but the one calling often goes to voicemail or finds another dentist.', 'following up about calls', 'The reason I\'m following up is Calyxr. We handle every inbound call for dental practices so you never miss a patient again. Our live answering service picks up in 8 seconds, books appointments directly into your schedule, and handles insurance questions. Zero missed calls, every patient reached within 8 seconds, around the clock. Perfect for boutique practices where every call matters.', 'A missed call in a two-doctor practice isn\'t just one lost appointment, it\'s often a lost family. When patients can\'t reach you, they move on quickly. At $300 average per new patient visit, just 5 missed calls per week costs $78,000 annually. Calyxr works with your existing schedule and has no long-term contracts. Worth exploring what you\'re currently losing to missed calls?', 'Boutique practices with one-patient-at-a-time scheduling face impossible choices when the phone rings during treatment. Answer and interrupt care, or let potential patients go to voicemail. What\'s your current approach when calls come in during procedures?', 'cost of missed calls', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://drfredblum.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Dr. Fred G. Blum & Associates (Rochester/ Brighton Dentist)', '', '2', '', '', 'New York', 'United States', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://drfredblum.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'http://www.linkedin.com/company/dr-blum-dentist', '+1 585-461-1670', 'caprice@drfredblum.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/dr-caprice-dakwar-279445192', 'drfredblum.com', 'medical practice', 'rochester dentist, tooth filling, brighton dentist, toothache, dentist, teeth cleaning, dr caprice dakwar, dental implants, dental crowns, dr fred g blum, gum disease, teeth whitening', 'For Over 30 years we have been serving the Rochester Area with our unique approach to dentistry. We treat every patient like family.\n\n===Cosmetic, Implant, & Family Dentistry===\nKnown as the compassionate dentists, Dr. Fred Blum and Dr. Caprice Dakwar are located in the 12-corners area of Brighton, near Rochester, New York. Our doctors and hygienists never schedule more than one patient at a time, so we can get to know you as a person and explain every treatment option and procedure. have person', 'Rochester', '', '', 'Dentist', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
