(481, 64, '2026-03-30 13:38:18', 'DRS. HERINGHAUS FAMILY DENTISTRY', 'https://drsheringhaus.com', 'Chelsie Pensante', 'Dental Assistant', 'chelsie@drsheringhaus.com', '', 'YES', 43, 'Small Ohio dental practice with clear industry match but limited by Clinical Staff contact role and very small team size (3 employees). Good geographic fit in EST zone.', 'Heringhaus General Dentistry is a small husband-and-wife practice in Mansfield, OH with only 3 employees serving comprehensive family dental care. With such a lean team handling all patient communications and scheduling, they face classic small practice challenges around front desk coverage and manual patient outreach.', 'small', 'medium', 'With only 3 employees handling all patient communications, scheduling, and front desk operations, this husband-and-wife practice likely struggles with phone coverage, missed calls, and manual appointment reminders that overwhelm their small team.', '3 total employees, husband-and-wife practice, small team size, comprehensive family dental care requiring diverse scheduling, general dentistry patient communication demands', 'medium', 'Wrong Contact', 'low', 'Running comprehensive family dentistry with just 3 employees means your front desk coverage gaps likely translate to missed hygiene recall revenue and appointment scheduling bottlenecks.', 'small practice front desk coverage gaps causing revenue leakage', '3 person teams, endless phones', 'Most small family practices with 3 employees face the same challenge. Someone\'s always in the back with a patient when the phone rings. Calls go to voicemail during procedures, lunch breaks, or when you\'re helping the front desk patient. Those missed calls often mean lost new patients who call the next practice on their list instead of leaving a message. Your team probably fields the same question dozens of times: did anyone call that patient back yet?', 'why i\'m following up', 'The reason I\'m writing is Calyxr. We handle every call for dental practices when your team can\'t pick up. Patients get a real person within 8 seconds, even during procedures or after hours. For small practices like yours, this means zero missed calls, every patient reached around the clock. One practice similar to yours saw their new patient bookings increase 40% just by never missing another call. Does this sound like something worth knowing more about?', 'A 3 person practice that misses 5 calls per week loses roughly $180,000 in annual revenue from new patients alone. That\'s not counting existing patients who don\'t reschedule when they can\'t reach anyone. Your team already works hard enough without losing revenue to something this fixable. We can have you covered within days with no long-term contracts. What would capturing every single call be worth to your practice?', 'Small practices with 3 employees always seem to miss calls during procedures or patient care. Patients calling back usually find another dentist instead. How often does your team wonder if they missed someone important?', 'what missed calls cost', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://drsheringhaus.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'DRS. HERINGHAUS FAMILY DENTISTRY', '', '3', '', '', 'Ohio', 'United States', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://drsheringhaus.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'http://www.linkedin.com/company/drs.-heringhaus-family-dentistry', '+1 419-524-7409', 'chelsie@drsheringhaus.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/chelsie-pensante-3296611a1', 'drsheringhaus.com', 'health, wellness & fitness', 'wellness & fitness services, health, wellness & fitness', 'Heringhaus General Dentistry offers a wide range of services and uses advanced technology. Schedule an appointment today!', 'Mansfield', '', '', 'Dental Assistant', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(482, 64, '2026-03-30 13:39:26', 'Dublin Dental Care', 'https://dublindentalcareohio.com', 'Zach Taylor', 'Dental Assistant', 'zach@dublindentalcareohio.com', '', 'YES', 66, 'Strong dental practice match in EST time zone with good revenue range, but contact is clinical staff influencer rather than decision-maker. Multiple dental specialties indicate sophisticated practice that could benefit from workflow automation.', 'Dublin Dental Care is a 6-employee, high-revenue family dental practice in Dublin, Ohio serving busy professionals and families with spa-like amenities and comprehensive dental services including prosthodontics specialty.', 'small', 'medium', 'High-revenue prosthodontics and cosmetic practice likely struggling with complex treatment plan follow-up and recall automation for expensive procedures requiring multiple visits', 'high revenue per employee ($1.8M), specialty prosthodontics and cosmetic procedures, complex multi-visit treatments (implants, crowns, veneers), small 6-person team managing high patient volume, TMJ specialty requiring frequent follow-ups', 'medium', 'Wrong Contact', 'low', 'With $10.8M revenue from just 6 staff, your prosthodontics and cosmetic cases likely generate significant treatment plan follow-up complexity that manual systems can\'t handle efficiently.', 'high-value treatment plan follow-up revenue leakage', 'treatment plans sitting idle', 'Many high-revenue dental practices see the same pattern with prosthodontics and cosmetic cases. Patients leave excited about their $15,000 smile makeover or full mouth reconstruction, then life gets in the way. Six months later, those treatment plans are still sitting in the chart with no systematic follow-up happening. The front desk gets pulled in ten directions, so those big cases just sit there while patients forget or second-guess the investment.', 'why i\'m following up', 'The reason I\'m writing is Calyxr. We handle the complex follow-up sequences that high-value cases require, automatically nurturing those prosthodontics and cosmetic treatment plans that would otherwise go cold. One practice similar to Dublin Dental saw no-shows dropped from 28% to under 12% in 90 days because patients stayed engaged between appointments instead of losing momentum. Does this sound like something worth exploring for your complex cases?', 'Every month those $10,000+ treatment plans sit unscheduled, that\'s real revenue walking out the door. At Dublin Dental\'s volume, even five delayed cases per month could mean $600,000+ in deferred production annually. The manual follow-up approach works until it doesn\'t, and with only six team members handling that revenue level, something has to give. We get practices live in under a week with no IT setup required. What would recapturing those stalled treatment plans mean for your production goals?', 'Noticed Dublin Dental\'s impressive revenue with such a lean team. Bet those complex prosthodontics and cosmetic treatment plans create some serious follow-up challenges when patients go radio silent after the consultation. How are you currently staying on top of those big cases that need multiple appointments?', 'what sitting still costs', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://dublindentalcareohio.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Dublin Dental Care', '10.8M', '6', '', '', 'Ohio', 'United States', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://dublindentalcareohio.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'http://www.linkedin.com/company/dublin-dental-care', '+1 614-932-0200', 'zach@dublindentalcareohio.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/zachctaylor', 'dublindentalcareohio.com', 'health, wellness & fitness', 'periodontics, temporomandibular joint disorder specialist, cosmetic dentistry, prosthodontics, dentistry, whitening, dentures, sedation dentistry, vaneers, dental implants, deep cleaning, one day crowns', 'You\'ll leave our Dublin dental office smiling, every time!\n\nAt Dublin Dental Care, we offer patients a modern, calming environment with spa-like amenities to enhance dental treatments and enliven the spirit. We are unique, in the best sense of the word. Our mission is the genuine care and comfort of each guest. Our goal is happiness.', 'Dublin', '2003', '', 'Dental Assistant', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(483, 64, '2026-03-30 13:40:24', 'Dugas Dental - Family and Cosmetic Dentistry', 'https://dugasdental.com', 'Justin Dugas', 'Dentist, Owner', 'drdugas@dugasdental.com', '', 'YES', 86, 'Ideal dental practice owner with 3 locations in Ohio, strong revenue profile ($15M), and perfect employee size (9). Family and cosmetic dentistry serving all age groups indicates high patient volume ideal for Calyxr\'s communication automation.', 'Dugas Dental is a successful multi-location general and cosmetic dentistry practice with 9 employees operating in Lewis Center and Mt. Gilead, Ohio, generating $15M revenue with high patient satisfaction (4.9 stars, 400+ reviews).', 'small', 'medium', 'High-volume multi-location practice with 9 employees managing $15M revenue likely struggling with staff efficiency and manual communication workflows across locations', 'multi-location practice, $15M revenue with only 9 employees, high patient volume indicated by revenue size, general and cosmetic dentistry mix requiring different scheduling patterns', 'high', 'Champion / Economic Buyer', 'high', 'With $15M revenue across three Ohio locations but only 9 total employees, your front desk is likely drowning in cross-location appointment coordination and insurance verifications.', 'multi-location coordination burden with lean staffing model', '9 people, 15m revenue', 'Most dental groups hitting $15M have 25-30 staff members. Running three locations with 9 people means each team member is covering multiple roles that would normally be specialized positions. The front desk coordination alone between locations probably feels impossible some days. When one location gets slammed with calls, the others can\'t help because they\'re equally stretched thin.', 'why i\'m following up', 'The reason I\'m writing is Calyxr. We handle the patient communication workload that\'s burning out your front desk across all three locations. One system manages appointment confirmations, insurance verifications, and recall outreach for every location simultaneously. A similar Ohio group saw their front desk teams reclaim 15+ hours a week on reminder calls alone. Does this sound like something worth exploring?', 'Running $15M in revenue with 9 people means every manual task is costing you exponentially. Each insurance verification taking 8 minutes instead of 30 seconds adds up to thousands in lost productivity monthly. Every missed recall patient is $400+ in hygiene revenue walking out the door. Calyxr works with your existing PMS and lives in under a week. What\'s the biggest communication bottleneck you\'re seeing between locations right now?', 'Running three locations with 9 total employees is impressive but probably exhausting for your front desk teams. Most practices your size have triple the staff just to handle the communication volume. What\'s the biggest coordination challenge you\'re seeing between your Ohio locations?', 'cost of staying manual', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://dugasdental.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Dugas Dental - Family and Cosmetic Dentistry', '15.0M', '9', '', '', 'Ohio', 'United States', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://dugasdental.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company