(484, 64, '2026-03-30 13:41:26', 'El Paso Periodontics & Implant Specialists', 'https://epimplant.com', 'Nasim Ravari', 'Founder', 'east@epimplant.com', '', 'YES', 67, 'Strong industry fit with periodontics specialty practice in Texas, founder-led with clear dental services alignment. Limited by single employee count but owner-founder persona is ideal decision-maker.', 'El Paso Periodontics & Implant Specialists is a dual-location specialty periodontal practice with two specialist periodontists offering implant surgery, laser therapy, and complex periodontal procedures across East and West El Paso locations.', 'small', 'high', 'Two-location specialty practice with only 1 employee listed needs automated patient communication and recall to manage complex periodontal treatment sequences across multiple sites without overwhelming limited staff', 'dual-location practice, specialty periodontics with complex multi-visit treatments, extremely lean staffing (1 employee Apollo count), implant and surgical procedures requiring extensive follow-up sequences', 'high', 'Champion', 'high', 'With two periodontal locations but only one employee listed, complex implant treatment sequences likely fall through recall cracks between sites.', 'multi-location specialty practice understaffing leading to treatment sequence discontinuity', 'implant sequences between locations', 'Running periodontal treatment across two locations creates gaps most practices don\'t see coming. Patients start their implant sequence at one site, then life happens. They miss the follow-up at location two, or forget which office handles their next phase. The complex treatment plans that make specialty practices profitable become the hardest to track when patients move between sites. Most founders with multiple locations find their highest-value cases sitting incomplete in different charts.', 'why i\'m following up', 'I\'m writing because of Calyxr. We handle the treatment sequence communication between your locations so nothing falls through the cracks. Your patients get reminded about their next implant phase regardless of which El Paso Periodontics location they\'re scheduled at. One practice saw their incomplete treatment follow-through jump 70% after we started tracking their multi-phase cases automatically. Does this sound like something worth exploring for your two locations?', 'Every incomplete implant sequence sitting in your charts represents revenue that should have been collected months ago. With two locations and complex periodontal cases, the average practice loses $47,000 annually to treatment plan abandonment. The longer those cases sit without follow-up, the less likely patients are to complete care. Calyxr works with your existing setup, no long-term contracts required. Would you be open to seeing how this would work specifically for periodontal sequences?', 'Managing implant treatment sequences between two locations while keeping overhead lean is tough. Most specialty founders I talk to lose track of multi-phase cases when patients bounce between sites. Are you seeing this challenge with your periodontal treatments?', 'incomplete implant revenue', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://epimplant.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'El Paso Periodontics & Implant Specialists', '', '1', '', '', 'Texas', 'United States', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://epimplant.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'http://www.linkedin.com/company/el-paso-periodontics-&-implant-specialists', '+1 915-581-6688', 'east@epimplant.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/nasim-ravari-b773b9158', 'epimplant.com', 'medical practice', 'medical practices, hospital & health care', 'El Paso Periodontics & Implant Specialists offers a wide range of services. From diagnostic and treatment of gum health issues to crown lengthening, extractions, and sinus floor elevations, patients have access to the very latest in periodontal care.', 'El Paso', '', '', 'Founder', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(485, 64, '2026-03-30 13:42:25', 'El Paso Quality Dentistry, P.A.', 'https://elpasoqualitydentistry.com', 'Adela Cabrera', 'Founder', 'cabrera.adela@elpasoqualitydentistry.com', '', 'YES', 67, 'Texas-based dental practice with clinical owner/founder, perfect geography and persona fit, but lacks technology signals and clear pain indicators to reach Tier A.', 'El Paso Quality Dentistry is a premium, single-doctor practice led by Dr. Adela Cabrera with 30+ years specializing in complex restorative, cosmetic, and implant dentistry. With 6 employees serving high-end patients, they focus on \'one patient at a time\' personalized care and receive referrals from other dentists.', 'small', 'high', 'High-value restorative and implant patients require extensive insurance pre-verification and treatment plan coordination that\'s likely eating up front desk time at this boutique practice', 'premium single-doctor practice, complex restorative/cosmetic/implant cases, 6 employees, receives referrals from other dentists, high-end patient base', 'medium', 'Champion / Economic Buyer', 'high', 'Six-person boutique practice handling complex implant cases probably spends hours daily on multi-phase treatment pre-authorizations and eligibility checks.', 'front desk administrative burden from high-value treatment planning workflow', 'implant pre-auths taking forever', 'Adela, boutique practices doing high-end restorative and implant work face a unique burden. Every complex case means your front desk team spends hours calling insurance companies, waiting on hold, and chasing down multi-phase pre-authorizations. The more sophisticated your treatment plans, the more administrative complexity you inherit. Meanwhile, patients are waiting weeks to know their coverage details before they can commit to moving forward.', 'why I\'m following up', 'The reason I\'m writing is Calyxr handles insurance eligibility verification instantly for complex dental cases, including multi-phase implant and restorative work. Instead of your team spending hours on pre-auths, our system confirms coverage details in 12 seconds before every appointment. One practice doing similar implant-focused work saw their front desk teams reclaim 15+ hours a week on reminder calls alone. How much time does your team currently spend on insurance verification for complex cases?', 'Every hour your team spends on manual insurance verification is an hour not spent on patient care or case acceptance. At six team members, that\'s likely 10-15 hours weekly just on pre-authorizations and eligibility checks. That translates to thousands in lost productivity monthly, plus delayed treatment starts when patients wait weeks for coverage clarity. Calyxr works with your existing PMS and requires no IT setup. What would getting those hours back mean for your practice growth?', 'Hi Adela, noticed El Paso Quality Dentistry focuses on complex restorative and implant cases. Boutique practices like yours often get buried in multi-phase pre-authorizations and insurance verification. How many hours weekly does your team spend chasing down coverage details for implant cases?', 'cost of manual verification', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://elpasoqualitydentistry.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'El Paso Quality Dentistry, P.A.', '', '6', '', '', 'Texas', 'United States', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://elpasoqualitydentistry.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (cla