(489, 65, '2026-03-30 14:04:31', 'Elizabeth L. Wakim DDS LLC', 'https://elizabethlwakimdds.com', 'Liza Wakim', 'Dentist', 'liza@elizabethlwakimdds.com', '', 'YES', 67, 'Small dental practice with specialty services (implants, oral surgery, Invisalign) led by clinical owner-dentist. Strong industry match and comprehensive service offering suggests patient volume potential, though limited by small team size.', 'Elizabeth L. Wakim DDS LLC is a boutique dental and facial aesthetics practice in Washington, PA with 4 employees offering comprehensive dental services plus cosmetic injectables. The practice positions itself as \'Enhanced Wellness\' with high-end aesthetic focus and advanced surgical capabilities.', 'small', 'high', 'Small 4-person team handling high-end cosmetic/surgical cases with complex scheduling, treatment coordination, and patient communication needs that likely overwhelm front desk capacity', '4-employee boutique practice, high-end aesthetic focus, complex procedures (implants, full-mouth reconstruction, maxillofacial surgery), likely PPO patients for cosmetic work, no mention of automation tools', 'medium', 'Champion / Economic Buyer', 'high', 'With full-mouth reconstruction and All-on-X cases requiring multiple appointments, your 4-person team likely spends hours coordinating complex treatment sequences and pre-appointment insurance verification.', 'complex surgical case coordination overwhelming small team capacity', '4-person teams and complex cases', 'Most dental practices with 4-person teams weren\'t designed to handle full-mouth reconstructions and All-on-X cases. The treatment coordination alone can consume entire days, your front desk gets pulled into scheduling multi-appointment sequences instead of focusing on patient experience, and someone always ends up staying late to coordinate the insurance verification for tomorrow\'s surgical case. It\'s the hidden cost of doing high-end work with a lean team.', 'why I\'m following up', 'I\'m writin