specialty, employees) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'http://www.linkedin.com/company/fairfax-dental-group', '+1 703-560-6301', 'youngdds@fairfaxdentalgroup.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/brenda-young-64407327', 'fairfaxdentalgroup.com', 'medical practice', 'sleep apnea, tmj, veneers, invisalign, restorative dentistry, implant dentistry, cosmetic dentistry, general dentistry, teeth whitening, dental emergency, medical practices, dental technology', 'We are a Fairfax family dental practice devoted to restoring and enhancing the natural beauty of your smile using conservative, state-of-the-art procedures that will result in beautiful, long lasting smiles!\n\nA standard of excellence in personalized dental care enables us to provide the quality dental services our patients deserve.  We provide comprehensive treatment planning and use restorative and cosmetic dentistry to achieve your optimal dental health.  Should a dental emergency occur, we ma', 'Fairfax', '1992', '', 'Dentist', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(497, 65, '2026-03-30 14:11:55', 'Fairmont Dental Care', 'https://fairmontdentalcare.com', 'Kandi Korn', 'Registered Dental Assistant', 'kandi@fairmontdentalcare.com', '', 'YES', 61, 'Strong dental practice fit in Texas with 7 employees serving multiple cities, but contact is clinical staff (RDA) rather than decision-maker. Multi-location service area suggests operational complexity that Calyxr can address.', 'Solo cosmetic dentistry practice owned by Dr. Mark McGrath in Pasadena, TX serving Houston metro area. 7 employees with $20M revenue indicates high-volume cosmetic procedures requiring extensive patient communication and appointment coordination.', 'small', 'high', 'High-volume cosmetic practice with $20M revenue and only 7 staff needs automated patient communication and scheduling to handle extensive treatment plan coordination without overwhelming small team', '7 employees managing $20M revenue, cosmetic specialty requiring multi-visit treatment plans, extensive geographic coverage across Houston metro, high-value procedures needing patient education and follow-up', 'high', 'Wrong Contact', 'low', 'With $20M revenue from just 7 staff, your cosmetic cases likely require multiple pre-treatment consultations and follow-ups that could overwhelm front desk scheduling.', 'high-revenue cosmetic practice scheduling bottleneck with lean staffing', 'cosmetic case coordination chaos', 'Many high-volume cosmetic practices face the same challenge. Complex cases requiring multiple pre-treatment visits, follow-up consultations, and coordination calls create a scheduling nightmare. When you\'re running $20M in revenue with a lean team, every cosmetic treatment plan that sits unscheduled represents lost revenue. The manual back-and-forth to coordinate multi-step cases often overwhelms front desk staff, leading to patient leakage and incomplete treatment acceptance.', 'why I\'m following up', 'The reason I\'m writing is Calyxr. We help high-volume cosmetic practices coordinate complex treatment plans without overwhelming small teams. Instead of manual follow-ups for multi-step cases, patients receive automated sequences tailored to their specific treatment timeline. One cosmetic practice saw 70% reduction in manual front office tasks without adding headcount. Worth exploring for a practice doing $20M with just 7 staff?', 'Every cosmetic case sitting unscheduled in your charts represents roughly $3,000-8,000 in lost revenue. When coordination calls and follow-ups are handled manually, cases slip through cracks and patients lose momentum. At your volume, that\'s potentially six figures annually. Calyxr works with your existing PMS and requires no IT setup. What if you could recover those unscheduled cosmetic cases without adding staff burden?', 'High-volume cosmetic practices with lean teams face a unique challenge. Complex multi-step cases create coordination nightmares that overwhelm front desk staff. At $20M revenue with 7 people, every unscheduled treatment plan hurts. How are you currently managing cosmetic case follow-ups?', 'unscheduled cosmetic treatment cost', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://fairmontdentalcare.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Fairmont Dental Care', '20M', '7', '', '', 'Texas', 'United States', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://fairmontdentalcare.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'http://www.linkedin.com/company/fairmont-dental-care', '+1 281-487-1486', 'kandi@fairmontdentalcare.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/kandi-korn-a54aa35a', 'fairmontdentalcare.com', 'health, wellness & fitness', 'wellness & fitness services, health, wellness & fitness, dentists, general dentistry, health & medical', 'Mark T. McGrath, DDS is a professional dedicated to cosmetic dentistry including veneers and Zoom.  His office is located in Pasadena and serves patients in surrounding cities of Deer Park, LaPorte, Houston, and Clear Lake.', 'Pasadena', '', '', 'Registered Dental Assistant', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(498, 65, '2026-03-30 14:12:51', 'Family Dental Group', '', 'Susan Sloane', 'Registered Dental Hygienist', 'susan@familydentalfostercity.com', '', 'YES', 45, 'Family Dental Group in NY matches dental industry perfectly, but contact is a Registered Dental Hygienist (clinical staff, influencer role only). Missing critical data on practice size and decision-makers limits qualification confidence.', 'Family Dental Group is a New York-based general dental practice, likely serving multiple family members across age groups. With a Registered Dental Hygienist as the primary contact, this suggests a hygiene-focused practice model with preventive care emphasis and likely multiple hygienists on staff.', 'small', 'medium', 'Hygiene-focused practice likely struggles with recall automation and maintaining consistent preventive care schedules across multiple family members without manual outreach', 'general dentistry practice, family-focused patient base, hygienist as primary contact, New York location with likely high patient volume', 'medium', 'Wrong Contact', 'low', 'With a hygienist-led contact structure, your recall coordination across multiple family members per household likely creates manual scheduling conflicts and missed prevention revenue.', 'hygiene-led practice model with family-unit recall complexity and prevention revenue leakage', 'family recall scheduling chaos', 'Most family dental practices see the same pattern with recall scheduling. Mom books her cleaning, but somehow the kids\' six-month checkups slip through the cracks. Dad\'s overdue by eight months because nobody followed up after his last visit. The hygienist ends up manually cross-referencing family schedules, trying to coordinate everyone\'s prevention care while staying on top of production goals. Meanwhile, recall revenue sits idle because there\'s no systematic way to reach entire families when they\'re due.', 'why i\'m following up', 'The reason I\'m writing is Calyxr. We help dental practices automatically coordinate recall scheduling for entire family units, not just individual patients. Instead of manually tracking who\'s due when across each household, the system reaches out to families with coordinated scheduling options that make sense for parents managing multiple kids\' appointments. One practice saw their hygiene recall completion rate jump from 60% to 89% within 90 days just by fixing the family coordination piece. Does this sound familiar at Family Dental Group?', 'Every family with overdue recall appointments represents about $800-1200 in lost hygiene production per year. When you multiply that across even 50 overdue families, that\'s $40K+ in prevention revenue just sitting there. The manual approach keeps hygienists juggling coordination instead of focusing on patient care and clinical excellence. Calyxr works with your existing practice management system, no IT setup required. Would it make sense to see how this could work specifically for family scheduling at your practice?', 'Hi Susan, noticed Family Dental Group likely handles a lot of family units for recall scheduling. Most hygienists tell me coordinating entire families\' prevention care manually becomes overwhelming pretty quickly. How do you currently manage recall coordination when you have multiple family members all due around the same time?', 'sitting recall revenue', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, specialty) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, specialty) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + CSV (partial Apollo export) → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', '', '', 'susan@familydentalfostercity.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/susan-sloane-744aa532', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Registered Dental Hygienist', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
