(499, 65, '2026-03-30 14:13:50', 'Family Smiles Dental Group', 'https://familysmilesdg.com', 'Jared Terry', 'Dentist', 'mydentist@familysmilesdg.com', '', 'YES', 69, 'Strong dental practice fit in Texas with $3.9M revenue and dentist owner-operator, but small team size of 3 employees suggests limited front office complexity and lower automation needs.', 'Family Smiles Dental Group is a well-established single-location general dentistry practice in Flower Mound, TX, led by Dr. Jenifer Nichols with 3 employees generating $3.9M revenue, serving multi-generational families with comprehensive general, cosmetic, and restorative dentistry.', 'small', 'medium', '3-person team managing $3.9M revenue creates severe front desk bottleneck with missed calls, manual scheduling, and insurance verification overload', '3 employees, $3.9M revenue, general dentistry, single location, multi-generational families, comprehensive services', 'high', 'Champion', 'high', 'With just 3 team members handling $3.9M in production, Dr. Nichols\' front desk is likely drowning in insurance verification calls during peak scheduling hours.', 'front desk bottleneck from manual VOB burden at high-revenue small practice', '3 people, 3.9m revenue', 'Most dental practices hitting $3.9M in production have 8-12 front office staff. When you\'re running that volume with just 3 people, insurance verification becomes the silent practice killer. Peak scheduling hours turn into a phone juggling act, patients get busy signals during lunch breaks, and eligibility checks eat up time that should be spent on patient experience. The math just doesn\'t work when your front desk is buried in manual VOB calls while the phones keep ringing.', 'why i\'m writing today', 'The reason I\'m following up is Calyxr. We handle insurance eligibility verification automatically so your 3-person team can focus on patients instead of hold music with Aetna. One practice similar to yours saw their front desk teams reclaim 15+ hours a week on reminder calls alone. Your revenue per employee ratio tells me you\'ve built something special at Family Smiles, but the administrative load is probably crushing your team during busy periods.', 'Every day your front desk spends 2-3 hours on insurance verification is 2-3 hours not spent on treatment plan follow-ups or patient retention. At $3.9M production with 3 staff members, that manual work is costing you roughly $180 per day in lost productivity. Calyxr works with your existing PMS and requires no IT setup. Would it make sense to see how this would look for Family Smiles specifically?', 'Running $3.9M with just 3 team members is impressive, but I imagine your front desk gets buried in insurance verification calls during peak hours. Most practices your size struggle with the same bottleneck. How are you managing the VOB workload currently?', 'cost of staying manual', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://familysmilesdg.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Family Smiles Dental Group', '3.9M', '3', '', '', 'Texas', 'United States', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://familysmilesdg.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-202