(507, 65, '2026-03-30 14:22:26', 'Fresh Dentistry by CanDDS', 'https://freshbycandds.com', 'Jayson Scroggins', 'Cosmetic Dentist', 'jayson.scroggins@freshbycandds.com', '', 'YES', 52, 'Strong industry match as a dental practice in Texas with cutting-edge technology focus, but limited by small size (2 employees) and clinical staff contact rather than owner/decision-maker.', 'Fresh Dentistry by CanDDS is a small 2-employee cosmetic dentistry practice in Cedar Hill, Texas, founded in 2018. As a boutique cosmetic practice with cutting-edge technology focus, they likely serve elective procedures requiring extensive consultation and treatment plan follow-up.', 'small', 'medium', 'Two-person cosmetic practice likely struggles with manual treatment plan follow-up and consultation scheduling between high-value elective procedures', '2-employee team, cosmetic specialty requiring extensive follow-up, founded 2018 (likely outgrowing manual processes), boutique practice with high-touch patient journey', 'medium', 'Champion', 'high', 'Two-person cosmetic practice means your dentist time gets pulled into treatment plan follow-ups instead of chair-side production.', 'cosmetic dentist losing production time to administrative follow-up tasks', 'treatment plans sitting idle', 'Most cosmetic practices have thousands of dollars in treatment plans sitting in charts with no systematic follow-up. Patients leave excited about veneers or Invisalign, then life gets busy and they never schedule. The front desk handles emergencies and insurance calls, so treatment plan follow-up becomes whenever someone remembers. Small cosmetic practices especially feel this because every unscheduled case represents significant lost production.', 'following up on treatment plans', 'That treatment plan follow-up gap is exactly why I\'m writing. Calyxr handles the systematic outreach to patients with unscheduled cosmetic treatment so you stay focused on clinical work instead of chasing cases. A similar two-person cosmetic practice saw 70% reduction in manual front office tasks without adding headcount. The system tracks every treatment plan automatically and reaches out at the right intervals. Are you seeing cases sit in charts longer than they should?', 'Every month that treatment plans sit without follow-up, cosmetic practices lose 15-20% of that production permanently. Patients find other providers or decide against treatment entirely. For a practice averaging $25K in unscheduled cosmetic work, that\'s $4,000+ walking out the door monthly. Calyxr works with your existing practice management system, no IT setup required. Would it be worth seeing how many treatment plans are currently sitting idle in your charts?', 'Noticed you run a two-person cosmetic practice. Most practices your size have treatment plans sitting in charts without systematic follow-up while handling day-to-day patient flow. How do you currently stay on top of unscheduled cosmetic cases?', 'cost of manual follow-up', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://freshbycandds.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Fresh Dentistry by CanDDS', '', '2', '', '', 'Texas', 'United States', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://freshbycandds.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'http://www.linkedin.com/company/freshbycandds', '+1 972-291-0800', 'jayson.scroggins@freshbycandds.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/jayson-scroggins-a6588199', 'freshbycandds.com', 'medical practice', 'medical practices, hospital & health care', 'We provide top-notch dental care in our first-rate facility equipped with dentistry\'s cutting edge and trusted technologies.', 'Cedar Hill', '2018', '', 'Cosmetic Dentist', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
