(528, 65, '2026-03-30 14:43:50', 'Gupta Orthodontics', 'https://guptaortho.com', 'Ashley Selph', 'Registered Dental Assistant', 'ashley@guptaortho.com', '', 'YES', 67, 'Strong orthodontic practice fit with ideal size (8 employees) and revenue ($3.4M), located in high-priority Texas market. Contact is clinical staff influencer rather than decision-maker, but practice shows clear dental specialty focus with Invisalign/braces services.', 'Gupta Orthodontics is a mid-size, single-location specialty orthodontic practice in Plano, TX with 8 employees and $3.4M revenue, led by Harvard-trained, board-certified Dr. Deepak Gupta who emphasizes advanced technology and premium treatment options.', 'mid-size', 'medium', 'Managing high-volume orthodontic appointment scheduling and patient communication across 2+ year treatment cycles with limited front desk staff for a $3.4M specialty practice', 'specialty orthodontics, 8 employees for $3.4M revenue, multi-year treatment cycles, Invisalign/Damon Braces requiring frequent adjustments, premium positioning suggests affluent patients with high communication expectations, single location handling multiple cities', 'medium', 'Wrong Contact', 'low', 'With 8 staff managing 2+ year orthodontic treatment cycles, your front desk likely spends hours daily on hygiene recall and progress appointment confirmations.', 'orthodontic treatment cycle communication burden with limited staffing', '2 year treatment cycles', 'Most orthodontic practices with 2+ year treatment cycles see their front desk teams spending 3-4 hours daily just on appointment confirmations and progress check reminders. With 8 staff managing hundreds of patients at different stages, someone is always calling about next adjustments, retainer checks, or missed appointments. The manual coordination gets overwhelming when you\'re trying to keep everyone on track for their treatment timeline. Every missed appointment pushes the entire cycle back and creates scheduling gaps.', 'why i\'m writing ashley', 'Following up because of Calyxr. We handle the entire appointment confirmation and reminder process for orthodontic practices, so your front desk can focus on patient care instead of constantly being on the phone. One practice similar to yours saw their front desk teams reclaim 15+ hours a week on reminder calls alone. The system tracks every patient\'s treatment stage and automatically handles all the follow-up communication. Worth exploring how this might work for your team?', 'If your front desk is spending 20+ hours weekly on appointment confirmations, that\'s over 1,000 hours annually that could go toward patient experience instead of phone work. At orthodontic billing rates, every missed adjustment appointment can cost $200-400 in lost production. Calyxr works with your existing practice management system and goes live in under a week. Would it help to see exactly how the automated reminder process works for orthodontic treatment cycles?', 'Ashley, noticed Gupta Orthodontics has grown to 8 staff managing those long orthodontic treatment cycles. Front desk probably spends hours daily just on appointment confirmations and progress reminders. How are you handling the reminder volume with your current setup?', 'the math on manual reminders', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://guptaortho.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Gupta Orthodontics', '3.4M', '8', '', '', 'Texas', 'United States', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://guptaortho.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'http://www.linkedin.com/company/gupta-orthodontics', '+1 972-473-3000', 'ashley@guptaortho.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/ashley-selph-b708371a7', 'guptaortho.com', 'medical practice', 'medical practices, dental clinic, offices of dentists, 3d radiography, treatment planning, dental services, damon braces, orthodontic consultation, teeth straightening, cbct, braces, ceramic braces', 'Gupta Orthodontics specializes in Invisalign & clear Damon Braces for adults, teens, and children.  We are the premier orthodontic practice in Plano, Frisco, and Dallas.  Dr. Deepak Gupta is a board certified orthodontist and graduated from the prestigious Harvard School of Dental Medicine.  We offer complimentary consultations to all new patients.  Call today for your complimentary exam by visiting our website at www.guptaortho.com or calling us at 972-473-3000.', 'Plano', '2011', '', 'Registered Dental Assistant', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(529, 65, '2026-03-30 14:44:51', 'Handley Dental', 'https://handleydental.com', 'Jeana Handley', 'Dental Hygienist', 'jeana@handleydental.com', '', 'YES', 53, 'Strong dental practice fit with Cypress TX location and dental keywords, but contact is clinical staff influencer rather than decision-maker. Small 6-person practice indicates potential for workflow automation needs.', 'Small family dental practice in Cypress, TX with 6 employees serving families with children. Dr. Ron Handley and Dr. Katie Chang provide general and cosmetic dentistry with strong patient retention (15+ year relationships mentioned).', 'small', 'medium', 'With only 6 employees serving families with children, front desk staff is likely overwhelmed with appointment scheduling, confirmation calls, and recall management for pediatric and family patients who have higher no-show rates', '6-person team, family dental practice, serves children, general dentistry, long patient relationships requiring consistent recall management', 'medium', 'Wrong Contact', 'low', 'Six-person team handling family patients with children creates front desk bottlenecks during after-school appointment rushes and summer break scheduling surges.', 'small team seasonal scheduling overload with pediatric patient families', 'family practices and phone chaos', 'Family practices with pediatric patients see this pattern constantly. Front desk staff drowning in confirmation calls, especially during after-school rush hours and summer booking surges. Six-person teams end up with everyone answering phones instead of focusing on patient care. The constant interruptions during hygiene appointments make it nearly impossible to stay on schedule when parents are calling to reschedule last-minute.', 'why I\'m following up', 'Following up because Handley Dental\'s team size caught my attention. We built Calyxr specifically for family practices dealing with pediatric scheduling chaos. Instead of your front desk spending hours on confirmation calls, families get automatic text reminders that actually work. One family practice saw no-shows dropped from 28% to under 12% in 90 days. What does your typical afternoon look like when school lets out?', 'A six-person team spending 2+ hours daily on confirmation calls costs roughly $18,000 per year in lost productivity. That\'s before factoring in the no-shows that slip through manual processes. Family practices usually see immediate ROI because parents actually respond to texts better than phone calls anyway. Calyxr works with your existing PMS and goes live in under a week. How many confirmation calls did your team make yesterday?', 'Noticed Handley Dental has six employees serving families with children. That front desk phone probably never stops ringing during after-school hours. Most family practices we talk to say confirmation calls eat up their entire afternoon. Does your team face the same challenge?', 'cost of manual confirmations', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://handleydental.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Handley Dental', '', '6', '', '', 'Texas', 'United States', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://handleydental.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) +