(530, 65, '2026-03-30 14:45:53', 'Hanna Dental Implant Center', 'https://hannadentalimplants.com', 'Raouf Hanna', 'Dental Implant Specialist', 'raouf@drhanna.co', '', 'YES', 67, 'Strong dental industry fit with implant specialty and Texas location, but contact is clinical staff (influencer) rather than decision-maker. Premier facility with luxury positioning suggests higher patient volume and revenue potential.', 'Hanna Dental Implant Center is a high-end periodontal specialty practice in Houston focused exclusively on dental implants and complex oral rehabilitation. Led by a Board Certified Periodontist with 14+ years experience, serving both local and international clientele with luxury amenities and advanced implant procedures including All-on-4.', 'small', 'high', 'High-value periodontal specialty practice with international clientele likely struggles with coordinating complex treatment sequences and ensuring seamless patient communication across multiple visit workflows for full-mouth reconstructions', 'periodontal specialty, complex implant procedures, All-on-4, international clientele, luxury service expectations, multi-visit treatment sequences, 10 employees suggesting substantial patient volume', 'medium', 'Champion', 'high', 'Full-mouth reconstruction cases likely create coordination headaches between your treatment phases and patient travel schedules for international clients.', 'complex multi-visit treatment sequence coordination burden for high-value international cases', 'full mouth reconstruction scheduling', 'Many specialty implant practices see the same pattern with full-mouth reconstruction cases. International patients book their initial consult and first phase, but coordinating the follow-up appointments across multiple treatment phases becomes a logistical maze. Patients travel back home between phases, time zones create communication delays, and the front desk ends up playing phone tag to confirm the next appointment block. The bigger the case value, the more complex the coordination becomes.', 'why i\'m following up', 'The reason I\'m writing is Calyxr. We handle the patient communication coordination for complex treatment sequences, especially when patients aren\'t local. Instead of your team managing multiple appointment confirmations across treatment phases, the system automatically reaches patients through their preferred method and handles the scheduling logistics. One of our implant specialists saw front desk teams reclaim 15+ hours a week on reminder calls alone. Does this coordination challenge sound familiar at Hanna Dental Implant Center?', 'Every week of manual coordination on full-mouth cases costs your practice in two ways. Your front desk spends hours confirming multi-phase appointments instead of supporting patients who are already in the chair. More importantly, when international patients miss their follow-up phase due to communication gaps, that\'s often $15,000+ in delayed revenue per case. We go live in under a week and work with your existing practice management system. What\'s your current process for keeping these complex cases on schedule?', 'Raouf, I imagine coordinating multi-phase reconstruction cases with international patients creates some interesting scheduling challenges at your practice. Between time zones and travel logistics, keeping those high-value treatment sequences on track probably takes significant front desk coordination. How are you currently handling the communication between phases?', 'cost of manual coordination', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://hannadentalimplants.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Hanna Dental Implant Center', '', '10', '', '', 'Texas', 'United States', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://hannadentalimplants.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'http://www.linkedin.com/company/hanna-dental-implant-center', '+1 855-374-2662', 'raouf@drhanna.co', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/raouf-hanna-06054276', 'hannadentalimplants.com', 'medical practice', 'dental implants, dentist, periodontist, all on four, medical practices, d2c, digital dentistry, digital impression, sedation options, bone loss solutions, dental health, dental services', 'Specialties\nHanna Dental Implant Center is a premier healthcare facility serving a worldwide clientele with cutting edge aesthetic and dental implant services. Dr. Hanna is a Board Certified Periodontist with over 14 years experience having performed thousands of implant procedures.\n\nWe aim to meld the luxury comforts that our clients expect with the specialist care insuring immaculate results.\n\nHanna Dental Implant Center provides everything from single site implant restorations to full mouth i', 'Houston', '2014', '', 'Dental Implant Specialist', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(531, 65, '2026-03-30 14:46:49', 'HARRIS PERIODONTICS AND IMPLANT DENTISTRY, INC.', 'https://harrisperio.com', 'Beth Heineman', 'Registered Dental Hygienist', 'beth@harrisperio.com', '', 'YES', 52, 'Periodontics specialty practice in Ohio with 6 employees fits industry requirements, but contact is clinical staff (hygienist) rather than decision-maker, limiting immediate sales potential.', 'Harris Periodontics and Implant Dentistry is a 6-person specialty periodontal practice in Mason, Ohio focusing on gum disease treatment and dental implants with individualized treatment plans.', 'small', 'high', 'Small 6-person specialty practice likely struggles with manual insurance verification for complex periodontal procedures and implant cases that require extensive pre-authorization documentation', 'specialty periodontal practice, 6 employees, complex treatment plans requiring pre-authorization, implant procedures with high insurance verification burden', 'high', 'Wrong Contact', 'low', 'Six-person perio team likely burns hours daily on pre-auth documentation for implant cases and complex grafting procedures.', 'specialty practice pre-authorization administrative burden', 'pre-auth documentation eating hours daily', 'Beth, many periodontal practices with small teams spend 3+ hours daily on pre-authorization paperwork for implant cases and complex grafting procedures. The insurance companies want every detail documented upfront, and someone has to pull together treatment histories, radiographs, perio charts, and medical justifications for each case. It\'s detailed work that pulls clinical staff away from patient care, but the alternative is claim denials or delayed treatment starts. Does this sound familiar at your practice?', 'why i\'m following up', 'Beth, I\'m writing because Calyxr handles the entire pre-authorization process for periodontal and implant practices. Instead of your team spending hours compiling documentation, our system pulls together treatment histories, imaging, and medical justifications automatically, then submits everything to the insurance company. One practice similar to yours saw insurance eligibility confirmed in 12 seconds before every appointment. Would something like this help free up time for your clinical work?', 'Beth, if your 6-person team spends even 2 hours daily on pre-authorization documentation, that\'s 520 hours annually that could go toward patient care instead of paperwork. At $35/hour, that\'s over $18,000 in labor costs just for insurance busy work. Calyxr works with your existing practice management system and goes live in under a week. Would it make sense to see how this could work for your perio practice?', 'Beth, noticed you work at Harris Perio. Most specialty practices your size spend hours daily on pre-auth documentation for implant and grafting cases. How much time does your team spend compiling insurance paperwork each week?', 'what manual pre-auth costs', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://harrisperio.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'HARRIS PERIODONTICS AND IMPLANT DENTISTRY, INC.', '', '6', '', '', 'Ohio', 'United States', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://harrisperio.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'http://www.linkedin.com/company/harris-periodontics-and-implant-dentistry-inc.', '+1 513-336-8100', 'beth@harrisperio.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/beth-heineman-77933b1a5', 'harrisperio.com', 'medical practice', 'medical practices, hospital & health care', 'Our exceptional team of periodontists, assistants, hygienists and office staff work closely with you to understand your needs and customize individualized treatment plans to accomplish our shared goals.  Our periodontists here at Harris Periodontics and Implants Dentistry are excited for the opportunity to earn your confidence and trust and guide you on a path to a optimal oral health!', 'Mason', '', '', 'Registered Dental Hygienist', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(532, 65, '2026-03-30 14:47:56', 'Hazzouri Dental', 'https://hazzouridental.com', 'Amy Evans', 'Dental Hygienist', 'aevans@hazzouridental.com', '', 'YES', 42, 'Established dental practice (1949) with 7 employees in Pennsylvania matches industry perfectly, but contact is clinical staff (Dental Hygienist) rather than decision-maker, limiting immediate sales potential.', 'Hazzouri Dental is a 75-year-old cosmetic-focused practice in Scranton, PA, combining high-end cosmetic dentistry with facial aesthetics services (Botox, fillers, Morpheus8). With 7 employees and premium service positioning, they likely serve an affluent patient base requiring sophisticated scheduling and follow-up coordination.', 'small', 'high', 'Cosmetic and aesthetics practice with premium services struggles to coordinate complex multi-visit treatment scheduling and follow-up communications for high-value patients expecting white-glove service', 'cosmetic dentistry focus, facial aesthetics services, 7-person team, premium positioning, multi-visit treatments, high patient expectations for service quality', 'medium', 'Wrong Contact', 'low', 'With Botox, fillers, and multi-visit cosmetic cases, your 7-person team likely spends significant time coordinating treatment sequences and follow-up appointments manually.', 'premium cosmetic practice coordination burden with multi-visit treatment scheduling', 'cosmetic treatment coordination chaos', 'Amy, cosmetic practices with Botox and multi-visit cases face a unique scheduling nightmare. Between coordinating treatment sequences, managing follow-up appointments, and keeping high-value patients informed about their next steps, the coordination workload multiplies fast. Most hygienists end up juggling manual reminders for touch-ups, follow-up injections, and aesthetic maintenance visits while trying to deliver that white-glove experience patients expect. The complexity grows exponentially when you\'re managing premium cases across a 7-person team.', 'why i\'m following up', 'Amy, following up because Calyxr handles the exact multi-visit treatment coordination challenge you\'re dealing with at Hazzouri Dental. Instead of manual follow-ups for cosmetic cases, it automatically sequences reminders for Botox touch-ups, filler maintenance, and aesthetic treatment plans. One cosmetic practice saw their front desk teams reclaim 15+ hours a week on reminder calls alone, letting them focus on patient experience instead of coordination chaos. The system tracks treatment timelines and sends the right message at the right interval.', 'Amy, when high-value cosmetic patients slip through follow-up cracks, the revenue impact compounds quickly. A missed Botox touch-up reminder costs $400-600 per patient, and aesthetic maintenance cases often represent $2,000+ in annual value per patient. Manual coordination across multi-visit treatments means some patients simply forget their next appointment or go elsewhere for touch-ups. Calyxr works with your existing PMS and goes live in under a week. Would it help to see how other cosmetic practices handle treatment sequence coordination?', 'Amy, noticed Hazzouri Dental offers Botox and aesthetic services. With multi-visit cosmetic cases, coordinating treatment sequences and follow-ups manually across your team must be time-intensive. How are you currently handling touch-up reminders and maintenance scheduling?', 'cost of manual coordination', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://hazzouridental.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Hazzouri Dental', '', '7', '', '', 'Pennsylvania', 'United States', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://hazzouridental.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'http://www.linkedin.com/company/hazzouridental', '+1 570-342-9136', 'aevans@hazzouridental.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/amy-evans-53767157', 'hazzouridental.com', 'health, wellness & fitness', 'botox, cosmetic dentistry, crowns, general dentistry, teeth whitening, laser teeth whitening, fillers, wellness & fitness services, cosmetics, beauty, apparel & fashion, medical practice', 'Hazzouri Dental is your source for outstanding cosmetic dentistry in the Scranton/Wilkes-Barre area. The Hazzouri name has been associated with helping Scranton smile beautifully since our practice first opened in 1949. We invite cosmetic dentistry patients throughout the area to become part of our tradition of beautiful smiles.', 'Scranton', '1949', '', 'Dental Hygienist', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
