(534, 65, '2026-03-30 14:49:06', 'Healing Wings Dental', 'https://healingwingsdental.com', 'Valerie Mukanga', 'Owner of Healing Wings Dental', 'drmukanga@healingwingsdental.com', '', 'YES', 58, 'Strong dental industry match with clinical owner persona in Texas, but small 2-employee size limits immediate automation needs. Keywords indicate full-service practice suggesting growth potential.', 'Healing Wings Dental is a 2-employee family dental practice in Arlington, TX offering comprehensive general dentistry with orthodontic services including Invisalign and FastBraces. The practice emphasizes patient education and comfort with a full spectrum of services from routine cleanings to complex procedures.', 'small', 'high', '2-person team handling comprehensive general dentistry plus orthodontics is overwhelmed with administrative tasks including appointment scheduling, patient communication, and insurance verification across multiple service lines', '2 employees total, comprehensive services including orthodontics, general dentistry with complex procedures, family practice serving all ages, emphasis on patient education and comfort', 'high', 'Champion', 'high', 'Two-person team juggling general dentistry plus orthodontics means constant interruptions from Invisalign progress check calls and FastBraces adjustment confirmations.', 'dual-specialty administrative burden with orthodontic follow-up communication overload', 'invisalign progress check calls', 'Most practices offering both general dentistry and orthodontics find their small teams constantly interrupted by patient calls. Every Invisalign tray change, FastBraces adjustment confirmation, and regular hygiene reminder pulls staff away from the patients sitting in front of them. The phone becomes the enemy when you\'re trying to deliver comprehensive care with a lean team. Two-person practices feel this the most, where every interruption means someone in the chair is waiting.', 'reason im following up', 'The reason I\'m following up is Calyxr handles all those patient communication interruptions automatically. Your team stops fielding progress check calls, tray pickup confirmations, and appointment reminders because patients get exactly what they need through text and voice without touching your phone lines. One orthodontic practice saw their front desk teams reclaim 15+ hours a week on reminder calls alone. Would something like this make sense for a comprehensive practice like Healing Wings?', 'Every phone interruption during patient care costs about 3-4 minutes of refocus time. With ortho patients calling about tray changes and general patients needing confirmations, a 2-person team loses roughly 2 hours daily to communication tasks that could run automatically. That\'s 10 hours weekly that could go toward patient care or practice growth instead. Calyxr works with your existing systems and goes live in under a week. Does reducing those daily interruptions sound worth exploring?', 'Hey Valerie, noticed Healing Wings offers both general and orthodontics with a 2-person team. Most practices that size get constantly interrupted by Invisalign progress calls and appointment confirmations. How are you handling all that patient communication without it disrupting chair time?', 'cost of constant interruptions', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://healingwingsdental.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Healing Wings Dental', '', '2', '', '', 'Texas', 'United States', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://healingwingsdental.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'http://www.linkedin.com/company/healing-wings-dental', '+1 972-213-0202', 'drmukanga@healingwingsdental.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/valerie-mukanga-dds-406268196', 'healingwingsdental.com', 'medical practice', 'root canal therapy, dental fillings, fast braces, invisalign, extractions, dental education, teeth whitening, dentures & bridges, orthodontist, routine cleanings & exams, crowns, medical practices', 'Our mission at Healing Wings Dental is to provide the most advanced dental treatment in a comfortable atmosphere. We strive to educate patients in good oral health habits. Each patient experience is important to us and our goal is to make you feel as comfortable as possible. Gentle and Caring Dental Services for Patients of All Ages!', 'Arlington', '', '', 'Owner of Healing Wings Dental', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(535, 65, '2026-03-30 14:50:10', 'Healthy Smile Dental Arts', 'https://drgrecymartinez.com', 'Grecy Martinez', 'Owner, CEO and Dentist', 'healthysmile@drgrecymartinez.com', '', 'YES', 78, 'Strong clinical owner fit with 30+ years experience in high-value cosmetic/restorative dentistry, excellent revenue ($4.4M), and established practice (1993) in prime NY market. Small team (3 employees) indicates high leverage opportunity for automation.', 'Healthy Smile Dental Arts is a minority woman-owned cosmetic dental practice in Upper Manhattan established in 1993, led by Dr. Grecy Martinez with 30+ years experience. High-end cosmetic focus with advanced technology but likely small front desk team managing premium patient volume.', 'small', 'high', 'Small 3-person team handling high-value cosmetic patients needs automated communication to maintain premium service levels without adding headcount', '3 employees only, $4.4M revenue, cosmetic specialty requiring extensive treatment coordination, full mouth rehabilitation cases, Invisalign requiring frequent check-ins, Upper Manhattan premium patient expectations', 'medium', 'Champion / Economic Buyer', 'high', 'Three-person team generating $4.4M suggests high-value cosmetic cases, but manual appointment coordination likely limits premium patient experience during complex treatment sequences.', 'premium cosmetic patient experience bottleneck with small team', 'cosmetic case coordination bottleneck', 'Most high-end cosmetic practices hit the same wall around $4M revenue. Three-person teams are brilliant at clinical excellence, but coordinating multi-visit veneers, full mouth rehabs, and smile makeovers becomes a manual juggling act. Patients paying premium fees expect flawless communication between prep appointments, lab work, and final placements. When your team is personally handling every confirmation, reminder, and scheduling change, it works until it doesn\'t. The bottleneck isn\'t clinical capacity, it\'s coordination bandwidth.', 'why i reached out', 'The reason I\'m following up is Calyxr. We handle the entire patient communication flow for cosmetic sequences so your team stays focused on what generates the revenue. Instead of your front desk managing 15 touchpoints for a full mouth case, the system handles confirmations, pre-appointment prep reminders, and post-visit follow-ups automatically. One practice saw their front desk teams reclaim 15+ hours a week on reminder calls alone while their cosmetic patient satisfaction scores actually improved because nothing falls through the cracks anymore.', 'Every cosmetic case that gets delayed because of a missed confirmation call or scheduling mix-up costs you more than just that appointment slot. At your case values, one rescheduled veneer sequence can mean $8,000 pushed to next month, and your reputation with premium patients depends on execution feeling effortless. Most practices your size are losing 2-3 high-value cases monthly to coordination gaps they don\'t even see. The system goes live in under a week with no IT setup required. Would you be open to seeing how this works for cosmetic treatment sequences specifically?', 'Noticed Healthy Smile Dental Arts is doing impressive numbers with just three people. Most cosmetic practices that size hit coordination bottlenecks where manual appointment management starts limiting the premium patient experience. Are you seeing any challenges with multi-visit case coordination as you scale?', 'cost of manual coordination', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://drgrecymartinez.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Healthy Smile Dental Arts', '4.4M', '3', '', '', 'New York', 'United States', 'CSV (company, industry, employees, specialty, state, country, revenue, contact title) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Website Scrape (https://drgrecymartinez.com) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 2 Research Summary + CSV (specialty, employees) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (contact name, title) + Agent 2 Research Summary + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'CSV (company, website, specialty) + Agent 2 Summary + Agent 3 Top Pain + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'Agent 5 Personalisation Insight + Agent 3 Top Pain + CSV (company, contact, specialty) + Apollo.io Enrichment → Claude AI (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)', 'http://www.linkedin.com/company/healthy-smile-dental-arts', '+1 212-491-6940', 'healthysmile@drgrecymartinez.com', '', 'http://www.linkedin.com/in/grecymartinez', 'drgrecymartinez.com', 'hospital & health care', 'cosmetic dental, full mouth rehabilitation, implants, laser dentistry, invisalign, hospitals & health care, hospital & health care, cosmetic dentists, dentists, general dentistry, health & medical, orthodontists', 'Discover a new level of dental artistry at Healthy Smile Dental Arts, where exceptional care meets modern technology. Under the skilled eye of Dr. Grecy Martinez, with her 30 years of experience, you\'ll experience dentistry like never before. Specializing in cosmetic and full-scale treatments like veneers, Invisalign, implants, teeth whitening and full mouth reconstruction, your smile will leave you beaming with confidence. Located in the heart of New York, this newly designed and expanded haven', 'New York', '1993', '', 'Owner, CEO and Dentist', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
